#: Game
msgid "[Game] CaptionLong"
msgstr "本游戏通过数学本科入门阶段的若干主题，展示如何在 Lean 中进行定理证明。"

#: Game
msgid "[Game] CaptionShort"
msgstr "和你的智能精灵司南一起探索一个陌生的宇宙！"

#: Game
msgid "[Game] Conclusion"
msgstr "QED"

#: Game
msgid "[Game] Info"
msgstr ""
"## 项目 ADAM\n"
"\n"
"这个学习游戏是在\n"
"[ADAM: Anticipating the Digital Age of Mathematics](https://hhu-"
"adam.github.io/)\n"
"项目框架下，由杜塞尔多夫海因里希·海涅大学开发的，\n"
"由 *高等教育教学创新基金会* 的 *Freiraum 2022* 项目资助。\n"
"后续维护与开发由 *文艺复兴慈善基金会* 的 *人工智能数学基金* 提供资金支持。\n"
"## 游戏内容\n"
"\n"
"**剧透警告** 在 [GitHub](https://github.com/hhu-adam/Robo?tab=readme-ov-"
"file#overview-over-existing-content) 上你能找到所有星球的大致数学内容概览。\n"
"\n"
"## 致谢\n"
"\n"
"* **项目负责人：** Marcus Zibrowius, Immi Halupczok\n"
"* **游戏引擎：** Jon Eugster, Alexander Bentkamp, Patrick Massot —— 见 "
"[lean4game](https://github.com/leanprover-community/lean4game?tab=readme-ov-"
"file#credits)\n"
"* **关卡：** Jon Eugster, Marcus Zibrowius, Sina Hazratpour\n"
"* **概念与剧情：** Marcus Zibrowius\n"
"* **插画：** [Dušan Pavlić](https://www.behance.net/dusanpavlic#)\n"
"\n"
"## 联系方式\n"
"\n"
"游戏仍在持续完善中。\n"
"我们非常欢迎体验反馈、建议和批评，\n"
"例如通过邮件联系\n"
"[Marcus Zibrowius](https://www.math.uni-duesseldorf.de/~zibrowius/)。\n"
"如果你有具体的修改建议，或者发现了错误，也欢迎你在 GitHub 上提一个 issue：\n"
"\n"
"* 游戏内容相关 issue，请提交到 [Robo repo](https://github.com/hhu-adam/Robo/"
"issues)。\n"
"* 游戏服务器相关 issue，请提交到 [lean4game repo](https://github.com/"
"leanprover-community/lean4game/issues)。"

#: Game
msgid "[Game] Introduction"
msgstr ""
"# Game Over 还是 QED？\n"
"\n"
"你是否好奇，计算机辅助证明与纸笔数学相比，会是什么样的体验？\n"
"那你来对地方了！\n"
"在这个游戏里，你将学习如何使用证明助手 Lean 4 和证明库 mathlib。\n"
"你会做的事情包括：用归纳法证明求和公式，\n"
"证明一个映射是满射，当且仅当它有一个右逆，\n"
"证明自然数序列的集合不可数，\n"
"以及在方阵空间上的所有函数中刻画迹映射。\n"
"\n"
"界面做了一些简化，但如果你开启*编辑器模式*，使用体验\n"
"几乎就和 VSCode 一样——这是 Lean 的标准 IDE。\n"
"在手机或平板上，你最好保持默认的*打字机模式*，\n"
"并关闭屏幕键盘的所有自动补全/自动纠错功能\n"
"（比如在三星键盘里到“智能输入 > 文本识别”把它关掉）。\n"
"\n"
"点击总览里的第一颗星球*逻辑*，开始你的旅程。\n"
"\n"
"## 存档\n"
"\n"
"你的存档会作为*site data*保存在浏览器本地。\n"
"如果你把这些清掉，就会丢失存档！\n"
"很多浏览器会把*site data*和*cookies*一起删除。\n"
"不过你也可以通过菜单下载存档并手动保存。\n"
"\n"
"## 游戏规则\n"
"\n"
"如果你想认真玩，建议选择*规则：标准*。\n"
"如果你只是想随便看看，选*规则：休闲*\n"
"  ——这样即使你还没通关前面的关卡，也能玩任何关卡。\n"
"\n"
"## 新消息\n"
"\n"
"`[2026-05-21]` 游戏里现在只允许使用 `mathlib` 中 `simp` 引理的一小部分子集。"
"如果有些你以为已经解决的关卡现在突然显示为未解决，很可能是因为你之前用了某个 "
"`simp` 的小捷径。\n"
"\n"
"`[2026-03-20]` Robo 现在也有英文版了！我们也[非常欢迎](https://github.com/"
"hhu-adam/Robo/tree/main?tab=readme-ov-file#translations)更多翻译！\n"
"\n"
"背景信息和致谢可以在菜单里的*游戏信息*中找到。"

#: Game
msgid "[Game] Title"
msgstr "司南"

#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid "A mapping ist bijectiv, if it is injektiv and surjektiv."
msgstr "一个映射是双射，当且仅当它既是单射又是满射。"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: ```
#. ∀ a b, f a = f b → a = b
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"A mapping §0 is injectiv, if:\n"
"\n"
"§1"
msgstr ""
"一个映射 §0 当且仅当满足以下条件时是单射：\n"
"\n"
"§1"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: ```
#. ∀ ⦃a b⦄, a < b → f a < f b
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"A mapping §0 is strictly monotonous, if:\n"
"\n"
"§1"
msgstr ""
"一个映射 §0 是严格单调的，当且仅当：\n"
"\n"
"§1"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: ```
#. ∀ b, ∃ a, f a = b
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"A mapping §0 is surjectiv, if:\n"
"\n"
"§1"
msgstr ""
"一个映射 §0 当且仅当满足以下条件时是满射：\n"
"\n"
"§1"

#. §0: `P : A → Prop`
#. §1: `∃! a : A, P a`
#. §2: `a`
#. §3: `A`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `P a`
#. §6: `a`
#. §7: `a`
#. §8: `∃!`
#. §9: `∃! a : A, …`
#. §10: `a`
#. §11: `use`
#. §12: `use a`
#. §13: `simp`
#. §14: `P a ∧ ∀ a' : A, P a' → a' = a`
#. §15: `P a`
#. §16: `a`
#. §17: `a`
#. §18: `∃!`
#. §19: `h : ∃! a : A, P a`
#. §20: ```
#.   obtain ⟨a, h_exists, h_unique⟩ := h
#.   simp at h_unique
#. ```
#. §21: ```
#.    a : A
#.    h_exists : P a
#.    h_unique : ∀ (y : A), P y → y = a
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"Existential quantifier: If §0 is a predicate, then\n"
"§1 is the statement that *exactly one* element §2 in §3 (more precisely: of "
"type §4)\n"
"exists for which the statement §5 is true.\n"
"The statement therefore has two parts: first, such an §6 exists, and second, "
"§7 is unique.\n"
"## §8 as a proof goal\n"
"\n"
"To prove a statement of the form §9, first construct a suitable element §10 "
"and\n"
"then use the §11 tactic (§12), usually immediately followed by §13.\n"
"The proof goal should then have the following form:\n"
"\n"
"§14\n"
"\n"
"On the left is §15: you still have to show that §16 has the required "
"property.\n"
"On the right is the uniqueness statement: every element with this property "
"is equal to §17.\n"
"\n"
"## §18 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"You can prove an assumption of the form §19 with\n"
"\n"
"§20\n"
"into its components\n"
"§21\n"
"."
msgstr ""
"存在唯一量词：\n"
"如果 §0 是一个谓词，那么 §1 表示：在 §3 中（更准确地说：\n"
"在类型为 §4 的对象里）存在*恰好一个*元素 §2，使得命题 §5 为真。\n"
"所以这个命题有两部分：\n"
"第一，存在这样的 §6；第二，§7 是唯一的。\n"
"\n"
"## §8 作为目标\n"
"\n"
"要证明一个形如 §9 的命题，你先构造一个合适的元素 §10，然后使用 §11 策略"
"（§12），通常紧接着再来一句 §13。\n"
"之后你的目标应该长这样：\n"
"\n"
"§14\n"
"\n"
"左边是 §15：\n"
"你还得证明 §16 具有所要求的性质。\n"
"右边是唯一性断言：\n"
"任何具有这个性质的元素都等于 §17。\n"
"\n"
"## §18 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"一个形如 §19 的假设，你可以用\n"
"\n"
"§20\n"
"把它拆成\n"
"§21\n"
"这些部分。"

#. §0: `P : A → Prop`
#. §1: `∃ a : A, P a`
#. §2: `a`
#. §3: `A`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `P a`
#. §6: `A`
#. §7: `∃ a : A, true`
#. §8: `Nonempty A`
#. §9: `∃`
#. §10: `∃ a : A, …`
#. §11: `a`
#. §12: `use`
#. §13: `use a`
#. §14: `∃`
#. §15: `h : ∃ a : A, P a`
#. §16: `choose a ha using h`
#. §17: `obtain ⟨a, ha⟩ := h`
#. §18: `a : A`
#. §19: `ha : P a`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"Existential quantifier: If §0 is a predicate, then\n"
"§1 is the statement that an element §2 in §3 (more precisely: of type §4)\n"
"exists for which the statement §5 is true.\n"
"A pure existence statement (\"there is an element of type §6)\n"
"can be formulated, for example, as §7 or as §8.\n"
"\n"
"## §9 as a proof goal\n"
"\n"
"To prove a statement of the form §10,\n"
"you construct a suitable element §11 and then use the §12 tactic (§13).\n"
"\n"
"## §14 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"You can decompose an assumption of the form §15 into its components using\n"
"§16 or §17 into §18 and §19."
msgstr ""
"存在量词：\n"
"如果 §0 是一个谓词，那么 §1 就是在说：在 §3 中存在一个元素 §2（更准确地说：\n"
"属于类型 §4），使得命题 §5 为真。\n"
"纯粹的存在性陈述“存在一个类型为 §6 的元素”例如可以写成 §7 或 §8。\n"
"\n"
"## §9 作为目标\n"
"\n"
"要证明形如 §10 的命题，你先构造一个合适的元素 §11，然后用 §12 策略（§13）。\n"
"\n"
"## §14 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"形如 §15 的假设，你可以用 §16 或 §17 把它拆成组成部分 §18 和 §19。"

#. §0: `I : Finset T`
#. §1: `∑ i ∈ I, f i`
#. §2: $\\sum_{i\\in I} f(i)$
#. §3: `\\sum`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a finite index set §0, §1 is Leanic notation for the sum\n"
"§2.  You write the summation sign as §3."
msgstr ""
"对于一个有限指标集 §0，§1 是 Lean语中表示求和 §2 的写法。\n"
"\n"
"你可以把求和符号写作 §3。"

#. §0: `I : Finset T`
#. §1: `∏ i ∈ I, f i`
#. §2: $\\prod_{i\\in I} f(i)$
#. §3: `\\prod`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a finite index set §0, §1 is the Leanic notation for the product\n"
"§2.  You write the product symbol as §3."
msgstr ""
"对于一个有限的指标集 §0，§1 是 Lean语中表示乘积 §2 的写法。\n"
"\n"
"你可以把乘积符号写作 §3。"

#. §0: `A : Finset T`
#. §1: `a : T`
#. §2: `insert a A`
#. §3: `A ∪ {a}`
#. §4: `a`
#. §5: `A`
#. §6: `insert a A = A`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a finite subset §0 and an element §1,\n"
"§2 is another way of writing §3.\n"
"If §4 is already in §5, then obviously §6."
msgstr ""
"对一个有限子集 §0 和一个元素 §1，§2 是 §3 的另一种写法。\n"
"如果 §4 已经在 §5 里了，那显然 §6。"

#. §0: `A : Finset T`
#. §1: `a : T`
#. §2: `erase A a`
#. §3: `A \\ {a}`
#. §4: `a`
#. §5: `A`
#. §6: `erase A a = A`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a finite subset §0 and an element §1,\n"
"§2 is another way of writing §3.\n"
"If §4 is not in §5 at all, then obviously §6."
msgstr ""
"对一个有限子集 §0 和一个元素 §1，§2 是 §3 的另一种写法。\n"
"如果 §4 根本不在 §5 里，那显然 §6。"

#. §0: `A : Finset T`
#. §1: `card A : ℕ`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `A`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a finite subset §0, §1 is the cardinality of §2,\n"
"i.e., the number of elements in §3."
msgstr "对一个有限子集 §0，§1 是 §2 的基数，也就是 §3 里的元素个数。"

#. §0: `f : A → B`
#. §1: `S`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: ```
#. f '' S = {f a | a ∈ S} = {b | ∃ a ∈ S, f a = b}
#. ```
#. §4: `f`
#. §5: `f`
#. §6: `''`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a mapping §0 and a subset §1 of §2,\n"
"§3\n"
"is its image under §4.  Note the space between §5 and §6."
msgstr ""
"对一个映射 §0 和 §2 的一个子集 §1，\n"
"§3\n"
"是 §1 在 §4 下的像。\n"
"注意 §5 和 §6 之间的空格。"

#. §0: `f : A → B`
#. §1: `T`
#. §2: `B`
#. §3: ```
#. f ⁻¹' T = { a | f a ∈ T}
#. ```
#. §4: `f`
#. §5: `f \\-1'`
#. §6: `f`
#. §7: `\\-1'`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a mapping §0 and a subset §1 of §2,\n"
"§3\n"
"is its preimage under §4.\n"
"You write this as §5.\n"
"Note the space between §6 and §7."
msgstr ""
"对一个映射 §0 和 §2 的一个子集 §1，\n"
"§3\n"
"是 §1 在 §4 下的原像。\n"
"\n"
"你把它写作 §5。\n"
"注意 §6 和 §7 之间的空格。"

#. §0: `f : A → B`
#. §1: `image f : Set A → Set B`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `f '' A`
#. §4: `f`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a mapping §0, §1\n"
"is one of the induced mappings on the power sets –\n"
"it maps a subset of §2 to the image §3 of this subset under §4."
msgstr ""
"对一个映射 §0，§1 是作用在幂集上的一个诱导映射——它把 §2 的一个子集映到该子集"
"在 §4 下的像 §3。"

#. §0: `f : A → B`
#. §1: `preimage f : Set B → Set A`
#. §2: `B`
#. §3: `f ⁻¹' A`
#. §4: `f`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a mapping §0, §1\n"
"is one of the induced mappings on the power sets –\n"
"it maps a subset of §2 to the preimage §3 of this subset under §4."
msgstr ""
"对一个映射 §0，§1 是作用在幂集上的一个诱导映射——它把 §2 的一个子集映到该子集"
"在 §4 下的原像 §3。"

#. §0: `f : A → B`
#. §1: `range f`
#. §2: `f`
#. §3: ```
#. range f = {f a | a : A}
#.         = {  b | ∃ a, f a = b}
#. ```
#. §4: `f '' univ`
#. §5: `mem_range`
#. §6: ```
#. x ∈ range f ↔ ∃ a, f a = b
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a mapping §0, §1 is the full image set of §2:\n"
"§3\n"
"Is a diffierent notation for §4.\n"
"§5 is useful to work with it:\n"
"§6"
msgstr ""
"对一个映射 §0，§1 是 §2 的整个像集：\n"
"§3\n"
"所以这基本上就是 §4 的另一种写法。\n"
"要处理这个记号，§5 很有用：\n"
"§6"

#. §0: `f : A → A`
#. §1: `fixedPoints f : Set A`
#. §2: `f `
#. §3: `unfold fixedPoints`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a mapping §0, §1 is the set of fixed points of §2.\n"
"Look up definition with §3."
msgstr ""
"对一个映射 §0，§1 是 §2 的不动点集合。\n"
"你可以用 §3 很容易把定义展开写出来。"

#. §0: `A`
#. §1: `trace A`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `∑ i, A i i`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a matrix §0, §1 is the trace of §2. The expression is also equivalent to "
"§3 in Leanic."
msgstr ""
"对一个矩阵 §0，§1 是 §2 的迹。\n"
"这个表达式在 Lean语里也等价于 §3。"

#. §0: `P : T → Prop`
#. §1: `{ a : T | P a } : Set P`
#. §2: ```
#. { n : ℕ | Even n }
#. ```
#. §3: `a ∈ { a : T | P a }`
#. §4: `simp`
#. §5: `P a`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a predicate §0, §1 is the subset\n"
"consisting of all elements that satisfy the predicate.  For example,\n"
"§2\n"
"is the set of even natural numbers.\n"
"You can simplify the statement §3, using §4, to §5 ."
msgstr ""
"对一个谓词 §0，§1 是由所有满足该谓词的元素组成的子集。\n"
"比如说，\n"
"§2\n"
"就是偶自然数的集合。\n"
"\n"
"命题 §3 你可以用 §4 化简成 §5。"

#. §0: `f : A → A`
#. §1: `a : A`
#. §2: `IsFixedPt f a`
#. §3: `f a = a`
#. §4: `unfold IsFixedPt`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a self-mapping §0 and an element §1, §2 is the expression §3.\n"
"Look up definition with §4."
msgstr ""
"对一个自映射 §0 和一个元素 §1，§2 就是断言 §3。\n"
"你可以用 §4 很容易把定义展开写出来。"

#. §0: `A : Set T`
#. §1: `a`
#. §2: `T`
#. §3: `T`
#. §4: `a ∈ A`
#. §5: `a`
#. §6: `A`
#. §7: `A = { a : T | P a }`
#. §8: `a ∈ A`
#. §9: `simp`
#. §10: `P a`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a subset §0 and an element §1 from §2 (more precisely: of type §3), §4 "
"means that\n"
"§5 is in §6.\n"
"For subsets of the form §7, you can simplify the statement\n"
"§8 with §9 to §10."
msgstr ""
"对一个子集 §0 和一个来自 §2 的元素 §1（更准确地说：\n"
"类型是 §3），§4 表示 §5 属于 §6。\n"
"\n"
"对于形如 §7 的子集，你可以用 §9 把命题 §8 化简成 §10。"

#. §0: `A : Set T`
#. §1: `Set.Finite A`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `h : Set.Finite A`
#. §4: `h.toFinset : Finset T`
#. §5: `A`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For a subset §0, §1 means that §2 has only a finite number of elements.\n"
"If §3 is given as an assumption, then §4 is the same subset §5,\n"
"but now explicitly understood as a finite subset."
msgstr ""
"对一个子集 §0，§1 表示 §2 只有有限多个元素。\n"
"如果 §3 作为假设给出，那么 §4 还是同一个子集 §5，但现在被明确地当作一个有限子"
"集来看。"

#. §0: `A`
#. §1: `B`
#. §2: `S`
#. §3: `A B : Set S`
#. §4: `A ∩ B`
#. §5: `∩`
#. §6: `\\inter`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For two subsets §0 and §1 of §2 (i.e. §3), §4 is their intersection.\n"
"§5 is written as §6."
msgstr ""
"对 §2 的两个子集 §0 和 §1（也就是 §3），§4 是它们的交集。\n"
"\n"
"你把 §5 写作 §6。"

#. §0: `A`
#. §1: `B`
#. §2: `S`
#. §3: `A B : Set S`
#. §4: `A ∪ B`
#. §5: `∪`
#. §6: `\\union`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For two subsets §0 and §1 of §2 (i.e. §3), §4 is their union.\n"
"§5 is written as §6."
msgstr ""
"对 §2 的两个子集 §0 和 §1（也就是 §3），§4 是它们的并集。\n"
"\n"
"你把 §5 写作 §6。"

#. §0: `(A B : Set T)`
#. §1: `A\\B`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `B`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `B`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For two subsets §0, §1 is the difference between §2 and §3,\n"
"consisting of all elements of §4 that are not in §5."
msgstr ""
"对两个子集 §0，§1 是 §2 和 §3 的差集，由所有属于 §4 但不属于 §5 的元素组成。"

#. §0: `x : ℝ`
#. §1: `|x|`
#. §2: `x`
#. §3: `|`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For §0, §1 is the absolute value of §2.\n"
"(Here, §3 is the usual vertical bar on the keyboard.)"
msgstr ""
"对 §0，§1 是 §2 的绝对值。\n"
"\n"
"（这里的 §3 是键盘上那个普通的竖线。）"

#. §0: `A B : Prop`
#. §1: `A → B`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `B`
#. §4: `X Y : Type`
#. §5: `X → Y`
#. §6: `X`
#. §7: `Y`
#. §8: `A → B`
#. §9: `intro h`
#. §10: `h : A`
#. §11: `B`
#. §12: `apply`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For §0, §1 is the implication “§2 implies §3.”\n"
"For other §4, §5 is a mapping that maps values from §6 to §7.\n"
"\n"
"## Implication as proof goal\n"
"\n"
"If your proof goal is an implication §8, with §9 you can assume §10,\n"
"and then you must prove §11.\n"
"\n"
"## Implication as assumption\n"
"\n"
"To use an implication among your assumptions, use the tactic §12."
msgstr ""
"对 §0 来说，§1 就是蕴涵“§2 蕴涵 §3”。\n"
"对其他的 §4，§5 是一个映射，把 §6 里的值映到 §7。\n"
"\n"
"## 蕴涵作为目标\n"
"\n"
"如果你的目标是一个蕴涵 §8，那么你可以用 §9 假设 §10，然后就得证明 §11。\n"
"\n"
"## 蕴涵作为假设\n"
"\n"
"要在假设里使用一个蕴涵，你用策略 §12。"

#. §0: `n : ℕ`
#. §1: `Fin n`
#. §2: $\\{0, \\dots, n-1\\}$
#. §3: `Fin n`
#. §4: `Icc 0 (n-1)`
#. §5: `Fin n`
#. §6: `Fin n : Type`
#. §7: `Icc 0 (n-1) : Finset ℕ`
#. §8: `ℕ`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For §0, §1 is the set §2.\n"
"\n"
"(§3 is to be distinguished from §4:\n"
"§5 is a set, or more precisely a type, i.e. §6,\n"
"whereas §7 is a finite subset of §8.)"
msgstr ""
"对 §0 来说，§1 就是集合 §2。\n"
"\n"
"（§3 要和 §4 区分开来：\n"
"§5 是一个集合，或者更准确地说是一个类型，也就是 §6，而 §7 是 §8 的一个有限子"
"集。）"

#. §0: `n : ℕ`
#. §1: `Prime n`
#. §2: `n`
#. §3: `prime_def`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For §0, §1 means that §2 is a prime number.\n"
"To work with this definition, it is often helpful to rewrite it using the "
"lemma\n"
"§3."
msgstr ""
"对 §0，§1 表示 §2 是一个素数。\n"
"要处理这个定义，通常用引理 §3 改写会很有帮助。"

#. §0: `A B : Set T`
#. §1: `A ⊆ B`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `B`
#. §4: `rw [subset_iff]`
#. §5: `A ⊆ B`
#. §6: `∀ x, x ∈ A → x ∈ B`
#. §7: `A ⊆ B`
#. §8: `intro a ha`
#. §9: `a`
#. §10: `ha : a ∈ A`
#. §11: `a ∈ B`
#. §12: `h : A ⊆ B`
#. §13: `a`
#. §14: `ha : a ∈ A`
#. §15: `have hb := h ha`
#. §16: `hb : a ∈ B`
#. §17: `⊆`
#. §18: `\\subset`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"For §0, §1 means that §2 is contained in §3.\n"
"\n"
"With §4, you can rewrite §5 as §6.\n"
"\n"
"If §7 is the proof goal, you can also directly use §8\n"
"to select an element §9 with §10 (and then show §11).\n"
"\n"
"If §12 is an assumption and an element §13 with §14 is given,\n"
"you can use §15 to obtain the statement §16.\n"
"\n"
"You write §17 as §18."
msgstr ""
"对 §0 来说，§1 的意思是 §2 包含在 §3 里。\n"
"你可以用 §4 把它改写成 §6。\n"
"\n"
"## §1 作为目标\n"
"\n"
"用 §8 你先取一个任意元素 §9 并假设 §10（然后就得证明 §11）。\n"
"\n"
"## §1 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"如果 §12 是一个假设，并且给定一个元素 §13 满足 §14，那么用 §15 你就得到命题 "
"§16。\n"
"\n"
"你把 §17 写作 §18。"

#. §0: `n : ℤ`
#. §1: `n.toNat : ℕ`
#. §2: `n : ℤ`
#. §3: `n.toNat : ℕ`
#. §4: `n : ℕ`
#. §5: `(n : ℤ)`
#. §6: `↑n`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"If §0 is an integer greater than or equal to 0, then §1 is the same number, "
"interpreted as a natural number.\n"
"(If §2 is a negative integer, then §3 is also defined, but its value has no "
"mathematical meaning.)\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"A natural number §4 can always be interpreted as an integer.\n"
"To do this, you either write it explicitly as §5 or as §6."
msgstr ""
"如果 §0 是一个大于等于 0 的整数，那么 §1 就是同一个数，只不过把它看成自然"
"数。\n"
"（如果 §2 是一个负整数，那么 §3 也同样有定义，但它的值没有数学意义。）\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"一个自然数 §4 总是可以看成一个整数。\n"
"为此你要么把它显式写成 §5，要么写成 §6。"

#. §0: `x ≠ y`
#. §1: `¬ x = y`
#. §2: `unfold Ne`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid "Inequality §0 is defined as §1.  You can see this with §2."
msgstr "不等关系 §0 被定义为 §1。你可以用 §2 把它展开。"

#. §0: `fun x ↦ _`
#. §1: `fun (x : ℤ) ↦  -x`
#. §2: `ℤ → ℤ`
#. §3: `↦`
#. §4: `\\maps`
#. §5: `\\mapsto`
#. §6: `↦`
#. §7: `=>`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"The notation §0 is used to define “anonymous functions.”\n"
"For example, §1 defines the negation §2 without giving it a name.\n"
"You write the arrow §3 as §4 or §5.\n"
"Alternatively, instead of §6 you can use §7."
msgstr ""
"记号 §0 用来定义“匿名函数”。\n"
"比如，§1 定义了取反函数 §2，但不给它起名字。\n"
"\n"
"箭头 §3 你写成 §4 或 §5。\n"
"另外，你也可以用 §7 来代替 §6。"

#. §0: `False : Prop`
#. §1: `False`
#. §2: `False`
#. §3: `contradiction`
#. §4: `False`
#. §5: `h : ¬ A`
#. §6: `apply h`
#. §7: `A`
#. §8: `¬ A`
#. §9: `A → False`
#. §10: `False`
#. §11: `False`
#. §12: `contradiction`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"The statement §0 is always false.\n"
"\n"
"## §1 as proof target\n"
"\n"
"If §2 is your proof target, you can try to find a contradiction in your "
"assumptions, for example.\n"
"Once the contradiction is sufficiently evident, §3 concludes such a proof.\n"
"\n"
"If §4 is your proof goal and you have an assumption or lemma of the form §5 "
"available,\n"
"you can use §6 to change the proof goal to §7\n"
"(because §8 means §9).\n"
"\n"
"## §10  as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"If you have §11 as an assumption, you can immediately end the proof with "
"§12\n"
"– because, as is well known, any other statement follows from a false "
"statement."
msgstr ""
"命题 §0 总是假的。\n"
"\n"
"## §1 作为证明目标\n"
"\n"
"如果 §2 是你的证明目标，你比如可以试着在你的假设里找出一个矛盾。\n"
"一旦矛盾足够明显，§3 就能结束这样的证明。\n"
"\n"
"如果 §4 是你的证明目标，并且你手头有一个形如 §5 的假设或引理，那么你可以用 "
"§6 把证明目标改成 §7（因为 §8 的意思是 §9）。\n"
"\n"
"## §10 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"如果你有 §11 作为假设，你可以立刻用 §12 结束证明——因为从一个假命题出发，众所"
"周知可以推出任何别的命题。"

#. §0: `True : Prop`
#. §1: `True`
#. §2: `tauto`
#. §3: `decide`
#. §4: `True`
#. §5: `True`
#. §6: `True`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"The statement §0 is always true.\n"
"\n"
"## §1 as a proof target\n"
"\n"
"The tactics §2 and §3 conclude every proof with §4 as the proof target.\n"
"\n"
"## §5 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"As an assumption, §6 is not helpful at all."
msgstr ""
"命题 §0 总是真的。\n"
"\n"
"## §1 作为目标\n"
"\n"
"策略 §2 和 §3 会在以 §4 为目标时结束任何证明。\n"
"\n"
"## §5 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"作为假设时，§6 完全没什么用。"

#. §0: `P : A → Prop`
#. §1: `∀ a : A, P a`
#. §2: `P a`
#. §3: `a`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `a`
#. §6: `A`
#. §7: `∀`
#. §8: `∀ a : A, …`
#. §9: `intro a`
#. §10: `a`
#. §11: `∀`
#. §12: `h : ∀ a : A, P a`
#. §13: `a₀ : A`
#. §14: `h a₀`
#. §15: `P a₀`
#. §16: `specialize h a₀`
#. §17: `a`
#. §18: `h : P a₀`
#. §19: `a₀`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"Universal quantifier: If §0 is a predicate, then\n"
"§1 is the statement that the statement §2 is true for all §3 in §4\n"
"(more precisely: for all §5 of type §6).\n"
"## §7 as a proof goal\n"
"To prove a statement of the form §8, first use §9 to select any element "
"§10.\n"
"## §11 as an assumption\n"
"If §12 is an assumption and §13 is a concrete element, then §14 is a "
"notation for §15.\n"
"\n"
"You can also use §16 to restrict the given assumption\n"
"over all possible §17 to an assumption §18 over this concrete §19."
msgstr ""
"全称量词：\n"
"如果 §0 是一个谓词，那么 §1 表示：命题 §2 对于 §4 中所有的 §3（更准确地说：\n"
"对于所有类型为 §6 的 §5）都成立。\n"
"\n"
"## §7 作为证明目标\n"
"\n"
"要证明一个形如 §8 的命题，你先用 §9 取一个任意元素 §10。\n"
"\n"
"## §11 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"如果 §12 是一个假设而 §13 是一个具体元素，那么 §14 是 §15 的一种记法。\n"
"你也可以用 §16 把“对所有可能的 §17 都成立”的给定假设，专门化成关于这个具体 "
"§19 的假设 §18。"

#. §0: `rfl`
#. §1: `rw`
#. §2: `trans`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid "Useful tactics for equality are: §0, §1, §2"
msgstr ""
"对等式有用的策略有：\n"
"* §0\n"
"* §1\n"
"* §2"

#. §0: `Nonempty`
#. §1: `T`
#. §2: `T : Type`
#. §3: `Nonempty T`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `A : Set T`
#. §6: `Nonempty A`
#. §7: `∃ x, x ∈ A`
#. §8: `unfold Nonempty`
#. §9: `t`
#. §10: `t : T`
#. §11: `use t`
#. §12: `a`
#. §13: `a : T`
#. §14: `a ∈ A`
#. §15: `ha : a ∈ A`
#. §16: `use a`
#. §17: `h : Nonempty T`
#. §18: `obtain ⟨t⟩ := t`
#. §19: `t`
#. §20: `t : T`
#. §21: `h : Nonempty A`
#. §22: `obtain ⟨a, ha⟩ := h`
#. §23: `a`
#. §24: `a : T`
#. §25: `a ∈ A`
#. §26: `ha : a ∈ A`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"[Doc.Definition] Nonempty\n"
"§0\n"
"for §1, §2, §3 means T is non-empty\n"
"for §4, §5, §6 means §7; check this with §8\n"
"As goal:\n"
"given §9, §10, use §11\n"
"given §12, §13 such that §14, §15, use §16\n"
"As assumption:\n"
"given §17, use §18 to obtain §19, §20\n"
"given §21, use §22 to obtain §23, §24, §25, §26"
msgstr ""
"对一个集合（更准确地说：一个“类型”）§1，§3 的意思是：在 §1（“类型为 §1”）里存"
"在一个元素。\n"
"同样地，对一个子集 §5，表达式 §6 等价于 §7。后者你可以用 §8 很容易地检查。\n"
"\n"
"## §0 作为证明目标\n"
"\n"
"如果你已经给出或构造了一个元素 §10，你可以用 §11 证明 §3。\n"
"同样地，如果你有一个元素 §12 并且有 §14，那么你可以用 §16 证明 §6。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## §0 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"对一个集合 §1，你可以用 §18 从假设 §17 中提取出一个 §20。\n"
"对一个子集 §5，你可以用 §22 从假设 §21 中提取出一个 §23，并且满足性质 §26。"

#. §0: `A ∧ B`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `B`
#. §3: `A ∧ B`
#. §4: `constructor`
#. §5: `A`
#. §6: `B`
#. §7: `A ∧ B`
#. §8: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := h`
#. §9: `h : A ∧ B`
#. §10: `h₁ : A`
#. §11: `h₂ : B`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 (“and”) is the statement that both §1 and §2 are true.\n"
"\n"
"## §3 as a proof goal\n"
"\n"
"The tactic §4 allows you to prove the two sub-statements §5 and §6 "
"individually.\n"
"\n"
"## §7 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"With §8, you break down an assumption of the form §9\n"
"into its components §10 and §11."
msgstr ""
"§0（“A 和 B”）表示：§1 和 §2 都为真。\n"
"\n"
"## §3 作为目标\n"
"\n"
"策略 §4 允许你把两个子命题 §5 和 §6 分开来证明。\n"
"\n"
"## §7 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"用 §8 你可以把一个形如 §9 的假设拆成它的组成部分 §10 和 §11。"

#. §0: `A ∨ B`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `B`
#. §3: `A ∨ B`
#. §4: `left`
#. §5: `right`
#. §6: `A ∨ B`
#. §7: `A`
#. §8: `B`
#. §9: `A`
#. §10: `B`
#. §11: ```
#. obtain h | h := h
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 (“or”) is the statement that at least one of the statements §1, §2 is "
"true.\n"
"\n"
"## §3 as proof goal\n"
"\n"
"You can use the tactics §4 or §5 to decide\n"
"which statement you want to prove.\n"
"\n"
"## §6 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"Since you do not know which of the statements §7 or §8 you can assume,\n"
"you may have to show the proof goal twice:\n"
"once under the assumption §9 and once under the assumption §10.\n"
"To do this, use the tactic\n"
"§11"
msgstr ""
"§0（“A 或 B”）的意思是：命题 §1、§2 至少有一个为真。\n"
"\n"
"## §3 作为证明目标\n"
"\n"
"用策略 §4 或者 §5，你可以决定你想证明哪一个命题。\n"
"\n"
"## §6 作为假设\n"
"\n"
"因为你不知道你可以假设 §7、§8 中的哪一个，所以你可能得把证明目标证明两次：\n"
"一次在假设 §9 下，一次在假设 §10 下。\n"
"为此你使用策略\n"
"§11"

#. §0: `(A : Prop)`
#. §1: `(True : Prop)`
#. §2: `(False : Prop)`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is any statement, without further specification as to whether it is true, "
"false, or\n"
"unprovable.\n"
"\n"
"See also §1 and §2 for the unconditionally true and false\n"
"statements, respectively."
msgstr ""
"§0 是一个任意命题，不额外说明它是真的、假的，还是根本不可证。\n"
"\n"
"另见 §1 和 §2：分别对应无条件为真和无条件为假的命题。"

#. §0: `Function.RightInverse f g`
#. §1: `LeftInverse g f`
#. §2: `∀ x, g (f x) = x`
#. §3: `Function.RightInverse`
#. §4: `RightInverse`
#. §5: `RightInverse`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is defined as §1.\n"
"In other words: §2.\n"
"\n"
"You have to write §3  instead of §4,\n"
"as §5 is ambigous in Leanic."
msgstr ""
"§0 被定义为 §1。也就是说，直白点就是 §2。\n"
"\n"
"你得写 §3 而不是 §4，因为 §5 在 Lean语里是有歧义的。"

#. §0: `Icc a b`
#. §1: $[a,b]$
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid "§0 is the closed interval §1."
msgstr "§0 是闭区间 §1。"

#. §0: `∅ : Set T`
#. §1: `∅ : Set ℕ`
#. §2: `∅ : Set ℝ`
#. §3: `rw [eq_empty_iff_forall_notMem]`
#. §4: `S = ∅`
#. §5: `∀ (x : T), x ∉ s`
#. §6: `∅`
#. §7: `\\emptyset`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is the empty subset.\n"
"In the Formaloverse §1 is something different than §2\n"
"– one is a subset of ℕ, the other is a subset of ℝ!\n"
"\n"
"With §3 you translate the equation §4 into the\n"
"statement §5.\n"
"\n"
"§6 is written as §7."
msgstr ""
"§0 是空子集。\n"
"在 Lean宇宙里，§1 和 §2 是不一样的——一个是 ℕ 的子集，另一个是 ℝ 的子集！\n"
"\n"
"用 §3 你可以把一个形如 §4 的等式改写成命题 §5。\n"
"\n"
"你把 §6 写作 §7。"

#. §0: `¬ A`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `A → False`
#. §3: `unfold Not`
#. §4: `push Not`
#. §5: `by_contra`
#. §6: `contrapose`
#. §7: `h : ¬ A`
#. §8: `apply`
#. §9: `False`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is the logical negation of §1.\n"
"It is implemented internally as §2.  You can see this with §3.\n"
"\n"
"Useful tactics are: §4, §5, §6.\n"
"You can also apply an assumption of the form §7 using §8 to the proof target "
"§9."
msgstr ""
"§0 是 §1 的逻辑否定。\n"
"它在内部被定义为 §2，你可以用 §3 很容易地检查这一点。\n"
"因此，你可以用 §8 把一个形如 §7 的假设应用到证明目标 §9 上。\n"
"\n"
"其他有用的策略有：\n"
"* §4\n"
"* §5\n"
"* §6"

#. §0: `succ : ℕ → ℕ`
#. §1: `n ↦ n + 1`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is the mapping §1.\n"
"It therefore maps a natural number to its successor."
msgstr ""
"§0 是映射 §1。\n"
"也就是说，它把一个自然数映到它的后继（英文 *successor*）。"

#. §0: `Even n`
#. §1: `n : ℕ`
#. §2: ```
#. ∃ r : ℕ, n = r + r
#. ```
#. §3: `unfold Even`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is the statement that §1 is even:\n"
"§2\n"
"You can easily check this with §3."
msgstr ""
"§0 表示 §1 是偶数：\n"
"§2\n"
"用 §3 你很容易就能检查这一点。"

#. §0: `Odd n`
#. §1: `n : ℕ`
#. §2: ```
#. ∃ k : ℕ, n = 2 * k + 1
#. ```
#. §3: `unfold Odd`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is the statement that §1 is odd:\n"
"§2\n"
"You can easily check this with §3."
msgstr ""
"§0 表示 §1 是奇数：\n"
"§2\n"
"用 §3 你很容易就能检查这一点。"

#. §0: `univ : Set T`
#. §1: `T`
#. §2: `rw [eq_univ_iff_forall]`
#. §3: `S = univ`
#. §4: `∀ (x : T), x ∈ S`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 is the “subset” consisting of *all* elements of type §1.\n"
"\n"
"With §2, you convert an equation of the form §3 into the\n"
"statement §4."
msgstr ""
"§0 是由类型为 §1 的*所有*元素组成的“子”集合。\n"
"\n"
"用 §2 你可以把一个形如 §3 的等式转成命题 §4。"

#. §0: `A ↔ B`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `B`
#. §3: `↔`
#. §4: `A ↔ B`
#. §5: `constructor`
#. §6: `A → B`
#. §7: `B → A`
#. §8: `↔`
#. §9: `h : A ↔ B`
#. §10: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := h`
#. §11: `h₁ : A → B`
#. §12: `h₂ : B → A`
#. §13: `h.mp`
#. §14: `h.mpr`
#. §15: `mp`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 means that statements §1 and §2 are logically equivalent (“if and only "
"if”).\n"
"\n"
"## §3 as proof target\n"
"\n"
"To show §4, you can, for example, call §5\n"
"and then prove §6 and §7 separately.\n"
"\n"
"## §8 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"You can break down an assumption of the form §9 using §10 into its two "
"components\n"
"§11 and §12.\n"
"However, you can also refer directly to these components with §13 and §14.\n"
"(The abbreviation §15 stands for “modus ponens”.)"
msgstr ""
"§0 表示命题 §1 和 §2 在逻辑上等价（“当且仅当”）。\n"
"\n"
"## 以 §3 为目标\n"
"\n"
"要证明 §4，你比如可以调用 §5，然后分别证明 §6 和 §7。\n"
"\n"
"## 以 §8 为假设\n"
"\n"
"形如 §9 的假设，你可以用 §10 把它拆成两个部分 §11 和 §12。\n"
"不过你也可以用 §13 和 §14 直接引用这些部分。\n"
"（缩写 §15 表示“modus ponens”。）"

#. §0: `P : MvPolynomial (Fin n) R`
#. §1: `P`
#. §2: `n`
#. §3: `X 0`
#. §4: `X (n-1)`
#. §5: `R`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 means that §1 is a polynomial in §2 indeterminates\n"
"§3, …, §4 with coefficients in §5."
msgstr ""
"§0 的意思是：§1 是一个关于 §2 个不定元 §3，……，§4 的多项式，系数在 §5 中。"

#. §0: `A : Set T`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `T`
#. §3: `A`
#. §4: `T`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 means that §1 is a subset of §2\n"
"(or, more precisely, that §3 is a set consisting of elements of type §4)."
msgstr ""
"§0 的意思是 §1 是 §2 的一个子集（或者更准确地说，§3 是一个集合，它由类型为 "
"§4 的元素组成）。"

#. §0: `LeftInverse g f`
#. §1: `g ∘ f = id`
#. §2: `∀ x, g (f x) = x`
#. §3: `unfold`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 means §1, or more exactly:\n"
"§2, as can be seen with §3."
msgstr "§0 的意思是 §1，或者更准确地说：§2，你用 §3 很容易就能展开。"

#. §0: `HasRightInverse f`
#. §1: `f`
#. §2: `HasLeftInverse f`
#. §3: `f`
#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"§0 means, that §1 has a right inverse.\n"
"\n"
"§2 means, that §3 has left inverse."
msgstr ""
"§0 表示 §1 有一个右逆。\n"
"\n"
"§2 表示 §3 有一个左逆。"

#. §0: ```
#. h : ∃ (b : B), P b
#. ```
#. §1: `choose b hb using h`
#. §2: `b : B`
#. §3: `hb : P b`
#. §4: `choose`
#. §5: ```
#. h : ∀ (a : A), ∃ (b : B), P a b
#. ```
#. §6: `choose f hf using h`
#. §7: `f : A → B`
#. §8: `hf : ∀ (a : A), P a (f a)`
#. §9: `P : A → (B → Prop)`
#. §10: `a`
#. §11: `b`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"An assumption of the form\n"
"§0\n"
"can be decomposed, using §1, into the components §2 and §3.\n"
"\n"
"More generally, you can use §4 to select elements using the choice axiom:\n"
"from an assumption of the form\n"
"§5\n"
"extracts §6\n"
"a mapping §7 and the assumption §8.\n"
"\n"
"(Here, §9 is a predicate that depends on two variables §10 and §11.)"
msgstr ""
"一个形如\n"
"§0\n"
"的假设，你可以用 §1 把它拆成组成部分 §2 和 §3。\n"
"\n"
"更一般地，你可以用 §4 借助选择公理选取元素：\n"
"从一个形如\n"
"§5\n"
"的假设中，§6 会抽取出一个映射 §7 以及假设 §8。\n"
"\n"
"（这里 §9 是一个谓词，它依赖于两个变量 §10 和 §11。）"

#. §0: `∃x, P x`
#. §1: `use x`
#. §2: `P x`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"If the proof target is of the form §0, you can use §1 to specify a concrete "
"element\n"
"for which you want to prove §2."
msgstr ""
"如果证明目标是形如 §0 的，你可以用 §1 给出一个具体元素，并且对它证明 §2。"

#. §0: `A ∨ B`
#. §1: `left`
#. §2: `right`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"If the proof target is of the form §0, you choose §1 to show the left side.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"With §2, you choose the right side accordingly."
msgstr ""
"如果证明目标是形如 §0 的，你用 §1 决定去证明左边。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"用 §2 你就相应地决定去证明右边。"

#. §0: `A ∨ B`
#. §1: `right`
#. §2: `left`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"If the proof target is of the form §0, you choose §1 to show the right "
"side.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"With §2, you choose the left side accordingly."
msgstr ""
"如果证明目标是形如 §0 的，你用 §1 决定去证明右边。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"用 §2 你就相应地决定去证明左边。"

#. §0: `h : X = Y`
#. §1: `h : X ↔ Y`
#. §2: `rw [h]`
#. §3: `X`
#. §4: `Y`
#. §5: `rw [←h]`
#. §6: `h`
#. §7: `Y`
#. §8: `X`
#. §9: `rw [h, g, ←f]`
#. §10: `h`
#. §11: `g`
#. §12: `f`
#. §13: `rw [h] at h₂`
#. §14: `h₂`
#. §15: `nth_rw`
#. §16: `h`
#. §17: `n`
#. §18: ```
#.    h : ∀ n, 2*n = f n
#.    ```
#. §19: ```
#.    h (n : ℕ) : 2*n = f n
#.    ```
#. §20: `rw [h]`
#. §21: `nth_rw k [h]`
#. §22: `k`
#. §23: `2*a + 2*b > 2*a`
#. §24: `rw [h]`
#. §25: `f a + 2*b > f a`
#. §26: `nth_rw 2 [h]`
#. §27: `2*a + f b > 2*a`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"If you have given an equation §0 or an equivalence §1 as an assumption or "
"lemma,\n"
"you can use §2 to replace all occurrences of §3 in the proof target with "
"§4.\n"
"\n"
"## Variants\n"
"\n"
"* §5 applies §6 backwards, i.e., replaces all §7 with §8.\n"
"* §9 applies §10, §11, and (backwards) §12.\n"
"* §13 performs the replacements in the assumption §14, not in the proof "
"target\n"
"* §15: If §16 has arguments, e.g., §17 in\n"
"§18\n"
"   or in\n"
"§19\n"
"   §20 searches the proof target from left to right for a matching "
"expression,\n"
"   and then replaces *all* occurrences of *the first* expression that the "
"tactic finds.\n"
"   With §21, you can replace all occurrences of the §22th expression "
"instead.\n"
"\n"
"  | before    | tactic       | after        |\n"
"  |:----------------- |:------------- - |:----------------- |\n"
"  | §23 | §24       | §25 |\n"
"  |                   | §26 | §27 |"
msgstr ""
"如果你有一个等式 §0 或一个等价 §1 作为假设或引理，那么你可以用 §2 把目标里所"
"有出现的 §3 替换成 §4。\n"
"\n"
"## 变体\n"
"\n"
"* §5 反向应用 §6，也就是把所有 §7 替换成 §8。\n"
"* §9 应用 §10、§11 以及（反向的）§12。\n"
"* §13 在假设 §14 里做替换，而不是在目标里。\n"
"* §15：\n"
"如果 §16 带参数，比如在\n"
"§18\n"
"或在\n"
"§19\n"
"里的 §17，\n"
"那么 §20 会在目标里从左到右找一个匹配的表达式，然后把策略找到的*第一个*表达式"
"的*所有*出现都替换掉。\n"
"你也可以用 §21 来改为替换第 §22 个表达式的所有出现。\n"
"\n"
"| 之前              | 策略           | 之后              |\n"
"|:----------------- |:-------------- |:----------------- |\n"
"| §23               | §24            | §25               |\n"
"|                   | §26            | §27               |\n"
" "

#. §0: `revert h`
#. §1: `h`
#. §2: `h : A`
#. §3: `⊢ B`
#. §4: `⊢ A → B`
#. §5: `intro h`
#. §6: `revert h`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 adds the assumption §1 as an implication premise to the proof "
"goal:\n"
"from §2 and §3, we get §4.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"The tactic §5 does the exact opposite of §6."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 会把假设 §1 作为蕴涵的前提塞进证明目标里：\n"
"从 §2 和 §3 变成 §4。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"策略 §5 做的正好是 §6 的反操作。"

#. §0: `by_cases h : P`
#. §1: `P`
#. §2: `by cases h : a = b`
#. §3: `a = b`
#. §4: `a ≠ b`
#. §5: `(h : P)`
#. §6: `(h : ¬P)`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 begins a case distinction as to whether §1 is true or false.\n"
"For example, §2 distinguishes between the cases §3 and §4.\n"
"\n"
"The proof goal is duplicated for this purpose, and\n"
"the assumption §5 is added to the first “copy,”\n"
"while the assumption §6 is added to the second “copy.”"
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 开始做一个分类讨论：§1 为真还是为假。\n"
"比如，§2 会区分 §3 和 §4 两种情况。\n"
"\n"
"为此证明目标会被复制一份：在第一份“副本”里加入假设 §5，在第二份“副本”里加入假"
"设 §6。"

#. §0: `linarith`
#. §1: ```
#. h : m ≤ x → n < x
#. ```
#. §2: ```
#. rw [imp_iff_or_not] at h
#. ```
#. §3: ```
#. h : n < x ∨ ¬m ≤ x
#. ```
#. §4: `linarith`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 can show that a linear equation or inequality follows from "
"given equations or inequalities.\n"
"It is quite flexible and works just as well in ℕ as in ℝ.\n"
"However, the (in)equations must be given individually, not logically "
"linked.\n"
"An assumption of the form\n"
"§1\n"
"must first be rewritten with\n"
"§2\n"
"to\n"
"§3\n"
"so that §4 can do something with it."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 可以证明某个线性方程或不等式能由给定的方程或不等式推出。\n"
"它挺灵活的，在 ℕ 和 ℝ 里都一样好用。\n"
"不过这些（不）等式必须是单独给出的，不能用逻辑连接起来。\n"
"比如一个形如\n"
"§1\n"
"的假设，得先用\n"
"§2\n"
"改写成\n"
"§3\n"
"这样 §4 才能用得上。"

#. §0: `omega`
#. §1: `ℕ`
#. §2: `ℤ`
#. §3: `linarith`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 can show that a linear equation or inequality in §1 or §2\n"
"follows from given equations or inequalities.\n"
"Unlike §3, it can also handle logical connections between (in)equations."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 可以证明：在 §1 或 §2 中，一个线性方程或不等式可以由给定的方程或不等"
"式推出。\n"
"它和 §3 不同，也能处理由（不）等式组成的逻辑连接。"

#. §0: `contrapose`
#. §1: `A → B`
#. §2: `¬B → ¬A`
#. §3: `revert h`
#. §4: `contrapose`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 changes a proof goal of the form §1 to §2, thereby\n"
"initiating a proof by contraposition.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"The tactic §3 can be useful for writing an assumption as an implication "
"premise\n"
"before you use §4."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 会把一个形如 §1 的证明目标改成 §2，从而开启一个用逆否命题来证明的思"
"路。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"在你使用 §4 之前，策略 §3 可能很有用：它能把一个假设写成蕴涵的前提。"

#. §0: `contradiction`
#. §1: `h : n ≠ n`
#. §2: `h : A`
#. §3: `h' : ¬A`
#. §4: `h : False`
#. §5: `contradiction`
#. §6: `by_contra`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 concludes the proof if it finds a contradiction in the "
"assumptions.\n"
"Such a contradiction can look like this, for example:\n"
"\n"
"* §1\n"
"* §2 and §3\n"
"* §4\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"Normally, §5 is used to conclude a proof by contradiction\n"
"that was opened with §6."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 会在假设里找到矛盾时结束证明。\n"
"这种矛盾比如可能长这样：\n"
"\n"
"* §1\n"
"* §2 和 §3\n"
"* §4\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"通常用 §5 来结束一个由 §6 开启的反证法证明。"

#. §0: `by_contra h`
#. §1: `P`
#. §2: `by_contra h`
#. §3: `(h : ¬ P)`
#. §4: `False`
#. §5: `contradiction`
#. §6: `A → B`
#. §7: `contrapose`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 initiates a proof by contradiction.\n"
"If §1 is your current proof goal, §2 generates a new assumption §3\n"
"and sets the proof goal to §4.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"* At the end of a proof by contradiction, there is usually §5:\n"
"this tactic closes the proof when it finds two obviously contradictory "
"assumptions.\n"
"* If the proof goal is of the form §6, you can use §7\n"
"to start a proof by contraposition."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 用来开启反证法证明。\n"
"如果 §1 是你当前的目标，那么 §2 会生成一个新的假设 §3，并把目标改成 §4。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"* 在反证法证明的最后通常会用到 §5：\n"
"这个策略会在它找到两条明显互相矛盾的假设时结束证明。\n"
"* 如果目标形如 §6，你可以用 §7 开始一个用逆否命题的证明。"

#. §0: `intro`
#. §1: `A → B`
#. §2: `∀ x, P x`
#. §3: `A → B`
#. §4: `intro h`
#. §5: `h : A`
#. §6: `B`
#. §7: `∀ x, P x`
#. §8: `intro x`
#. §9: `x`
#. §10: `P x`
#. §11: `⊢ A → B`
#. §12: `intro h`
#. §13: `h : A`
#. §14: `⊢ B`
#. §15: `⊢  x, P x`
#. §16: `intro x hx`
#. §17: `x : X`
#. §18: `hx : P x`
#. §19: `⊢ P x`
#. §20: `revert h`
#. §21: `intro h`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 is used for   proof goals of the form §1 or §2.\n"
"\n"
"If your proof goal is §3, §4 gives you the assumption §5, and you then have "
"to prove §6.\n"
"If your proof goal is §7, §8 gices you an arbitrary §9 and you have to prove "
"§10.\n"
"\n"
"| before | tactic       | after                     |\n"
"|:------------ |:------------ |:---------------------------- |\n"
"| §11    | §12    | §13, §14               |\n"
"| §15  | §16 | §17, §18, §19 |\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"The tactic §20 does the exact opposite of §21."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 用于形如 §1 或 §2 的目标。\n"
"\n"
"如果你的目标是 §3，用 §4 你会得到假设 §5，然后需要证明 §6。\n"
"如果你的目标是 §7，用 §8 你先随便取一个 §9，然后需要证明 §10。\n"
"\n"
"| 之前         | 策略         | 之后                        |\n"
"|:------------ |:------------ |:---------------------------- |\n"
"| §11          | §12          | §13, §14                     |\n"
"| §15          | §16          | §17, §18, §19                |\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"策略 §20 做的事情和 §21 正好相反。"

#. §0: `push Not`
#. §1: `push ¬ _ `
#. §2: `push`
#. §3: `Not`
#. §4: `¬ _`
#. §5: `¬∀ x, P x`
#. §6: `∃ x, ¬P x`
#. §7: `¬∃ x, P x`
#. §8: `∀ x, ¬P x`
#. §9: `¬`
#. §10: ```
#.   ¬ ∀ ε, ∃ δ, ∀ y, | x - y | < δ → | f x - f y | < ε
#. ```
#. §11: `push Not`
#. §12: ```
#.   ∃ ε, ∀ δ, ∃ y, ¬ (| x - y | < δ → | f x - f y | < ε)
#. ```
#. §13: `not_forall`
#. §14: `not_exists`
#. §15: `rw`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 or §1 (§2, §3, §4)  pushes negation past quantifiers:\n"
"\n"
"| before       | after      |\n"
"|:------------ |:-------------|\n"
"| §5  | §6  |\n"
"| §7  | §8  |\n"
"\n"
"In nested expressions, it pushes the negation §9 as far to the right as "
"possible.\n"
"For example, the proof goal\n"
"§10\n"
"with §11\n"
"§12\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"The two lemmas §13 and §14 can be applied individually with §15."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0（或者也可以：§1）把否定推进到量词里：\n"
"\n"
"| 之前         | 之后         |\n"
"|:------------ |:-------------|\n"
"| §5           | §6           |\n"
"| §7           | §8           |\n"
"\n"
"在嵌套表达式里，它会把否定 §9 尽可能往右推。\n"
"比如目标\n"
"§10\n"
"用 §11 会变成\n"
"§12\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"这个策略基于两个引理 §13 和 §14，你也可以用 §15 单独应用它们。"

#. §0: `induction n`
#. §1: `n`
#. §2: `induction n with d dh`
#. §3: `d`
#. §4: `hd`
#. §5: `n = 0`
#. §6: `hd`
#. §7: `induction`
#. §8: `induction'`
#. §9: `0`
#. §10: `Nat.zero`
#. §11: `d + 1`
#. §12: `Nat.succ d`
#. §13: `zero_eq`
#. §14: `Nat.succ_eq_add_one`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 performs an inductive proof over §1.\n"
"With §2, you can specify names for the induction variable (here: §3)\n"
"and the induction assumption (here: §4).\n"
"The tactic thus replaces the original proof goal with two new proof goals:\n"
"* an induction start, in which §5 is set, and\n"
"* an induction step, in which the induction assumption §6 is available to "
"you.\n"
"\n"
"## Modifications in this game\n"
"\n"
"Outside of this game, §7 is called §8,\n"
"§9 is initially written as §10 and §11 as §12.\n"
"These terms are identical in definition, but occasionally need to be "
"explicitly rewritten with\n"
"§13 and §14."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 对 §1 做归纳证明。\n"
"用 §2 你可以给归纳变量（这里是：\n"
"§3）和归纳假设（这里是：\n"
"§4）指定名字。\n"
"也就是说，这个策略会把原来的目标替换成两个新目标：\n"
"* 一个归纳起步，其中设定 §5，以及\n"
"* 一个归纳步骤，其中你可以使用归纳假设 §6。\n"
"\n"
"## 这个游戏里的改动\n"
"\n"
"在这个游戏之外，§7 叫做 §8，§9 一开始写作 §10，而 §11 写作 §12。\n"
"这些项在定义上是相等的，但有时需要用 §13 和 §14 显式改写。"

#. §0: `tauto`
#. §1: `generalize`
#. §2: `tauto`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 proves logical tautologies.\n"
"\n"
"# Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"Sometimes the proof target must first be abstracted with §1 so that §2 "
"recognizes the tautology."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 证明逻辑重言式。\n"
"\n"
"# 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"有时得先用 §1 把目标抽象一下，这样 §2 才能认出这是个重言式。"

#. §0: `rfl`
#. §1: `X = X`
#. §2: `rfl`
#. §3: `A = B`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `B`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic §0 proves §1.  More precisely, §2 closes every proof target of "
"the form §3,\n"
"where §4 and §5 are identical in definition."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 证明 §1。\n"
"更准确地说，§2 会完成任何形如 §3 的目标，其中 §4 和 §5 在定义上相等。"

#. §0: `simp`
#. §1: `mathlib`
#. §2: `@[simp]`
#. §3: `simp [h]`
#. §4: `h`
#. §5: `h`
#. §6: `simp [F]`
#. §7: `F`
#. §8: `simp only [h,f,g]`
#. §9: `h`
#. §10: `f`
#. §11: `g`
#. §12: `simp?`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The §0 tactic attempts to apply a large number of lemmas to simplify a given "
"expression.\n"
"(Technically, these are all lemmas in §1 that are marked with §2.)\n"
"\n"
"## Variants\n"
"\n"
"* §3 additionally uses the assumption §4 or the lemma §5 for simplification\n"
"* §6 additionally uses the definition of §7\n"
"* §8 exclusively uses the assumptions/lemmas/definitions §9, §10, and §11\n"
"* §12 shows you which lemmas were used"
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 会尝试应用大量引理来化简给定的表达式。\n"
"\n"
"## 变体\n"
"\n"
"* §3 在化简时还会额外使用前提 §4 或引理 §5\n"
"* §6 还会额外使用 §7 的定义\n"
"* §8 只使用前提/引理/定义 §9、§10 和 §11\n"
"\n"
"*(在现实里，§0 比这个游戏里强得多：§0 会尝试应用所有在 §1 里用 §2 之类标记过"
"的引理——而那可太多了！其中还有一些引理能一步解决这里给出的某些问题。所以在游"
"戏里只允许使用其中很小的一部分。)*"

#. §0: `constructor`
#. §1: `⊢ A ∧ B`
#. §2: `⊢ A`
#. §3: `⊢ B`
#. §4: `⊢ A ↔ B`
#. §5: `⊢ A → B`
#. §6: `⊢ B → A`
#. §7: `obtain`
#. §8: `A ∨ B`
#. §9: `left`
#. §10: `right`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The §0 tactic breaks down a proof goal into its constituent parts:\n"
"\n"
"| before | after                |\n"
"|:------------ |:----------------------- |\n"
"| §1    | §2 and §3         |\n"
"| §4    | §5 and §6 |\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"* You can break down an *assumption* into its components using §7.\n"
"* If you want to prove §8, you have to choose one side using §9 or §10."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 会把一个目标拆成它的组成部分：\n"
"\n"
"| 之前         | 之后                    |\n"
"|:------------ |:----------------------- |\n"
"| §1           | §2 和 §3               |\n"
"| §4           | §5 和 §6               |\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"* 一个*假设*你可以用 §7 把它拆成各个部分。\n"
"* 想证明 §8 的话，你得用 §9 或者 §10 先选一边。"

#. §0: `obtain`
#. §1: `h : A ∧ B`
#. §2: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := h`
#. §3: `h₁ : A`
#. §4: `h₂ : B`
#. §5: `h : A ↔ B`
#. §6: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := h`
#. §7: `h₁ : A → B`
#. §8: `h₂ : B → A`
#. §9: `h : Nonempty X`
#. §10: `obtain ⟨x⟩ := h`
#. §11: `x : X`
#. §12: `h : ∃ x : X, P x`
#. §13: `obtain ⟨x, hx⟩ := h`
#. §14: `x : X`
#. §15: `hx : P x`
#. §16: `h : A ∨ B`
#. §17: `obtain h \\| h := h`
#. §18: `h : A`
#. §19: `h : B`
#. §20: `\\<`
#. §21: `\\>`
#. §22: `⟨_, _⟩`
#. §23: $(G, 0, +)$
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The §0 tactic breaks down an assumption into its individual parts.\n"
"\n"
"| before       | tactic                 | "
"after                                   |\n"
"|:------------------ |:--------------------- - "
"|:------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| §1        | §2 | §3 and §4                      |\n"
"| §5        | §6 | §7 and §8              |\n"
"| §9   | §10      | §11                                    |\n"
"| §12 | §13  | §14 and §15                     |\n"
"| §16        | §17   | a target with §18, a target with §19 |\n"
"\n"
"Type the brackets in the first four examples as §20 or §21.\n"
"Here, §22 is the *anonymous constructor*.\n"
"You can think of it as similar to the tuple notation in\n"
"“an abelian group is a tuple §23 such that ...”."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 会把一个假设拆成它的各个部分。\n"
"\n"
"| 之前               | 策略                   | 之"
"后                                        |\n"
"|:------------------ |:---------------------- "
"|:------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| §1                 | §2                     | §3 和 "
"§4                                  |\n"
"| §5                 | §6                     | §7 和 "
"§8                                  |\n"
"| §9                 | §10                    | "
"§11                                        |\n"
"| §12                | §13                    | §14 和 "
"§15                                |\n"
"| §16                | §17                    | 一个目标是 §18，另一个目标是 "
"§19         |\n"
"\n"
"前四个例子里的括号你要输入成 §20 或者 §21。\n"
"这里的 §22 是*匿名构造子*。\n"
"你可以把它大致想成元组记号，比如“一个阿贝尔群是一个元组 §23，使得 …”。"

#. §0: `assumption`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The §0 tactic closes the proof if one of the assumptions corresponds exactly "
"to the proof target."
msgstr "策略 §0 会在某个假设恰好就是目标时结束证明。"

#. §0: `let`
#. §1: `let x : ℕ := 5 ^ 2`
#. §2: `let x := …`
#. §3: `x`
#. §4: `simp only [x]`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The §0 tactic introduces a temporary definition, for example\n"
"§1.\n"
"\n"
"Once §2 defines a §3, you can use the definition later with §4."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 引入一个临时定义，比如 §1。\n"
"\n"
"一旦你用 §2 定义了一个 §3，之后就可以用 §4 把这个定义展开来用。"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `+, -, *, ^`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The §0 tactic proves equations with the operations §1 in semirings,\n"
"in particular in ℕ, ℤ, ℚ, ℝ, …   It works particularly well in commutative "
"rings."
msgstr ""
"策略 §0 在半环里证明只用到运算 §1 的等式，尤其在 ℕ、ℤ、ℚ、ℝ、…… 里都能用。它"
"在交换环里特别好用。"

#. §0: ```
#. f = g
#. ```
#. §1: `f g : X → Y`
#. §2: `funext x`
#. §3: ```
#. f x = g x
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"Two mappings with the same range and domain are equal if\n"
"they take the same values on all elements of the domain.\n"
"A proof goal of the form\n"
"§0\n"
"for mappings §1 is converted by §2\n"
"into the equation\n"
"§3."
msgstr ""
"两个映射如果陪域和定义域相同，并且在定义域的所有元素上取到的值都一样，那它们"
"就相等。\n"
"一个形如\n"
"§0\n"
"的目标\n"
"对于映射 §1\n"
"可以用 §2 转化为等式\n"
"§3\n"
"。"

#. §0: ```
#. A = B
#. ```
#. §1: `T`
#. §2: `A B : Set T`
#. §3: `ext x`
#. §4: ```
#. x ∈ A ↔ x ∈ B
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"Two subsets of a given set are equal if they have the same elements.\n"
"If the proof goal is\n"
"§0\n"
"for two subsets of §1 (i.e., for §2),\n"
"then §3 converts the proof goal into the equivalence\n"
"§4"
msgstr ""
"给定集合的两个子集相等，当且仅当它们拥有相同的元素。\n"
"如果目标里有\n"
"§0\n"
"表示 §1 的两个子集（也就是 §2），那么 §3 会把目标变成下面这个等价：\n"
"§4"

#. §0: `symm`
#. §1: `=`
#. §2: `↔`
#. §3: `symm at h`
#. §4: `h`
#. §5: `h.symm`
#. §6: `symm at h`
#. §7: `h`
#. §8: `rw [←h]`
#. §9: ```
#.   symm at h
#.   rw [h]
#.   ```
#. §10: `rw [h.symm]`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0 (for “symmetry”), you swap the sides of an equation (§1) or "
"equivalence (§2) in the proof target.\n"
"\n"
"## Variants\n"
"* §3 operates on the assumption §4 instead of the proof target\n"
"* §5 is the result of §6 and can be used like §7\n"
"\n"
"Each of the following three tactics or tactic sequences therefore has the "
"same effect:\n"
"* §8\n"
"* §9\n"
"* §10"
msgstr ""
"用 §0（表示“symmetry”）你可以在目标里交换一个等式（§1）或等价（§2）的左右两"
"边。\n"
"\n"
"## 变体\n"
"* §3 作用在假设 §4 上，而不是作用在目标上\n"
"* §5 是 §6 的结果，并且可以像 §7 一样使用\n"
"\n"
"所以接下来的三种策略/策略序列效果都一样：\n"
"* §8\n"
"* §9\n"
"* §10"

#. §0: `apply`
#. §1: `hAB : A → B`
#. §2: `⊢ B`
#. §3: `apply hAB`
#. §4: `⊢ A`
#. §5: `h : A `
#. §6: `apply hAB at h`
#. §7: `h : B`
#. §8: `hAB`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you apply an implication §1:\n"
"\n"
"| before | tactic           | after |\n"
"|:------------ |:---------------- |:-------- |\n"
"| §2        | §3      | §4    |\n"
"| §5     | §6 | §7  |\n"
"\n"
"In both cases, the implication §8 can either be\n"
"given as an assumption or be an already known lemma."
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你可以应用一个蕴涵 §1：\n"
"\n"
"| 之前         | 策略             | 之后    |\n"
"|:------------ |:---------------- |:-------- |\n"
"| §2           | §3               | §4       |\n"
"| §5           | §6               | §7       |\n"
"\n"
"两种情况下，这个蕴涵 §8 既可以作为假设给出，也可以是一个已知的引理。"

#. §0: `if … then … else`
#. §1: `fun x ↦ if 0 ≤ x then x else -x`
#. §2: `h : A`
#. §3: `rw [if_pos h]`
#. §4: `if A then B else C`
#. §5: `B`
#. §6: `h : ¬ A`
#. §7: `rw [if_neg h]`
#. §8: `if A then B else C`
#. §9: `C`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you can define mappings with two branches of definition.\n"
"\n"
"For example, §1 defines the absolute value function.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"* If you have §2 as an assumption, you can use\n"
"§3 to reduce the expression §4 to §5.\n"
"* If you have §6 as an assumption, you can use\n"
"§7 to reduce the expression §8 to §9."
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你可以定义带两个分支的映射。\n"
"\n"
"比如，§1 定义了绝对值函数。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"* 如果你有 §2 这个假设，就可以用 §3 把表达式 §4 化简成 §5。\n"
"* 如果你有 §6 这个假设，同理可以用 §7 把表达式 §8 化简成 §9。"

#. §0: `generalize`
#. §1: `generalize h : a = b`
#. §2: `a`
#. §3: `b`
#. §4: `h : a = b`
#. §5: ```
#. Even x ∨ ¬Even x
#. ```
#. §6: ```
#. generalize h : (Even x) = A
#. ```
#. §7: ```
#. A ∨ ¬A
#. ```
#. §8: `tauto`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you can generalize a proof goal\n"
"in the hope that a higher level of abstraction will allow for a simpler "
"proof.\n"
"More precisely, §1 replaces all occurrences of §2 in the proof goal with §3\n"
"(and adds the assumption §4).\n"
"\n"
"## Example\n"
"\n"
"A goal of the form\n"
"§5\n"
"can be converted with\n"
"§6\n"
"into\n"
"§7\n"
"(and then simply proven with §8)."
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你可以把一个目标泛化——希望更高的抽象层次能让证明更简单。\n"
"更准确地说，§1 会把目标里所有出现的 §2 都替换成 §3（并且补上假设 §4）。\n"
"\n"
"## 例子\n"
"\n"
"一个形如\n"
"§5\n"
"的目标\n"
"可以用\n"
"§6\n"
"变成\n"
"§7\n"
"（然后就能直接用 §8 证明）。"

#. §0: `decide`
#. §1: `True`
#. §2: `Even 4`
#. §3: `2 ≤ 5`
#. §4: `4 ≠ 6`
#. §5: `Prime 7`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you can prove statements that can be decided using a simple "
"algorithm.\n"
"These include, in particular, §1 and statements about concrete numbers such "
"as:\n"
"- §2\n"
"- §3\n"
"- §4\n"
"- §5"
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你可以证明那些能用简单算法判定的命题。\n"
"其中尤其包括 §1，以及关于具体数字的命题，比如：\n"
"* §2\n"
"* §3\n"
"* §4\n"
"* §5"

#. §0: `unfold F`
#. §1: `F`
#. §2: `unfold F at h`
#. §3: `h`
#. §4: `unfold`
#. §5: `push Not`
#. §6: `rw`
#. §7: `unfold F`
#. §8: `simp only [F]`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you can write out the definition §1 in the proof goal.\n"
"With §2, you do the same thing, but in the assumption §3.\n"
"\n"
"Although the proof goal or assumption before and after §4 are identical in "
"definition,\n"
"many tactics (e.g., §5 or §6) operate on a syntactic level;\n"
"they do not “see through definitions.”\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and Relatives\n"
"\n"
"The tactics §7 and §8 do practically the same thing."
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你可以在目标里把定义 §1 展开。\n"
"用 §2 你做同样的事，不过是在假设 §3 里。\n"
"\n"
"虽然在 §4 前后，目标或假设在定义上是等价的，但很多 tactic（比如 §5 或者 §6）"
"是在语法层面操作的，它们“看不穿定义”。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"\n"
"策略 §7 和 §8 基本上做的是同一件事。"

#. §0: `trans`
#. §1: `⊢ A = C`
#. §2: `trans B`
#. §3: `⊢ A = B`
#. §4: `⊢ B = C`
#. §5: `⊢ A ↔ C`
#. §6: `trans B`
#. §7: `⊢ A ↔ B`
#. §8: `⊢ B ↔ C`
#. §9: `A = B₁ = B₂ = B₃ … = C`
#. §10: `calc`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you insert an intermediate step into an equation or equivalence.\n"
"\n"
"| before | tactic    | after                |\n"
"|:------------ |:--------- |:----------------------- |\n"
"| §1    | §2 | §3 and §4 |\n"
"| §5    | §6 | §7 and §8 |\n"
"\n"
"Since you can repeat the tactic several times, it is suitable for\n"
"performing a “calculation” §9 step by step.\n"
"\n"
"(Outside of the game, however, the multi-line tactic §10 is better suited "
"for such calculations.)"
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你可以在一个等式或等价之间插入一个中间步骤。\n"
"\n"
"| 之前         | 策略   | 之后                   | \n"
"|:------------ |:-------- |:-----------------------| \n"
"| §1           | §2       | §3 和 §4               | \n"
"| §5           | §6       | §7 和 §8               | \n"
"\n"
"因为你可以多次重复这个策略，它很适合一步一步做一串“计算” §9。\n"
"\n"
"（不过在游戏外，做这种计算更推荐用多行策略 §10。）"

#. §0: `suffices h : P`
#. §1: `P`
#. §2: `P`
#. §3: `have h : P`
#. §4: `P`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you introduce a proof section in which you show\n"
"that the desired proof goal follows from §1.\n"
"Then you prove §2.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"§3 works the same way, except that you must first prove §4 before you can\n"
"continue with the main proof."
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你会开启一段证明，在其中你要展示：想要的目标可以由 §1 推出。\n"
"之后你再证明 §2。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"§3 也一样，只不过你得先证明 §4，然后才能继续主证明。"

#. §0: `have h : P`
#. §1: `suffices h : P`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With §0, you introduce an intermediate result.\n"
"You must then prove this intermediate result\n"
"before you can continue with the actual proof.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"§1 works in exactly the same way, except that you can continue with the main "
"proof first and\n"
"only have to prove your intermediate result at the very end."
msgstr ""
"用 §0 你可以引入一个中间结果。\n"
"接下来你必须先证明这个中间结果，才能继续真正的证明。\n"
"\n"
"## 相关策略\n"
"§1 也一样，只不过你可以先继续主证明，直到最后才证明你的中间结果。"

#. §0: `specialize h a₁ a₂`
#. §1: `have h := h a₁ a₂`
#. §2: `h : ∀ m₁ m₂, P m₁ m₂`
#. §3: `h : P a₁ a₂`
#. §4: `specialize`
#. §5: `have`
#. §6: `specialize h …`
#. §7: `h`
#. §8: `h`
#. §9: ```
#. have ha := h a₁ a₂
#. have hb := h b₁ b₂
#. ```
#. §10: ```
#. h : ∀ m₁ m₂, P m₁ m₂
#. ha : P a₁ a₂
#. hb : P b₁ b₂
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"§0 is equivalent to §1: the tactic replaces an assumption\n"
"§2 with the special case §3.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to specialize multiple times, instead of §4 you should use §5,\n"
"since §6 overwrites the old assumption §7.\n"
"From the above assumption §8, you can obtain the following three assumptions "
"with\n"
"§9\n"
":\n"
"§10"
msgstr ""
"§0 等价于 §1：\n"
"这个策略会把一个假设 §2 替换成特例 §3。\n"
"\n"
"如果你想多次特化，最好用 §5 而不是 §4，因为 §6 会把旧的假设 §7 覆盖掉。\n"
"比如从上面的假设 §8 出发，你可以用\n"
"§9\n"
"得到下面这三个假设：\n"
"§10"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon
msgid "Babylon"
msgstr "巴比伦"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon
msgid "Intro Babylon"
msgstr ""
"你们到达了一颗星球，上面无数石板被堆成了高得离谱的塔。整片景观像一个巨大的拼"
"图，每一块石板都一丝不苟地搭在下面的石板上。有些塔高得连塔尖都看不见。很快你"
"们也遇到了这颗星球的第一个居民。\n"
"\n"
"**巴比伦人**：欢迎来到*巴比伦*！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：哦……\n"
"\n"
"你心里隐隐有种不妙的感觉。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你们确定这些塔稳吗？\n"
"\n"
"**巴比伦人**：百分百！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那你们到底怎么建成这些杰作的？\n"
"\n"
"**巴比伦人**：很简单！一块石板接一块石板。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L01_Sum_Simp_Card
msgid "Conclusion Babylon L01"
msgstr "**巴比伦人**：看起来不错！"

#. §0: $( \\sum_{i\\in I} 1)$
#. §1: $I$
#. §2: $I$
#. §3: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L01_Sum_Simp_Card
msgid ""
"Explain goal as §0 being equal to the number of elements in §1\n"
"i.e. the cardinality of §2. Try §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：哇这也太多新东西了……让我看看……\n"
"\n"
"这看起来像是 §0 等于……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：……§1 里元素的个数，也就是 §2 的基数。\n"
"\n"
"**巴比伦人**：那，你们能证明吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(对你说)*：我会先试试 §3。这真的是个很强的策略，能把很多项简化掉。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L01_Sum_Simp_Card
msgid "Intro Babylon L01"
msgstr ""
"**巴比伦人**：每座塔都有一段铭文。你们可以在那儿再仔细读一遍它为什么能站得"
"住。比如这里。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L02_Card2
msgid "Again try using §0"
msgstr "**你**：还是用 §0？"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L02_Card2
msgid "Intro Babylon L02"
msgstr "你们一起走到下一座塔前。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L03_sum_congr
msgid "Intro Babylon L03"
msgstr ""
"接下来你们来到一块空的工地，看起来已经很久没动静了。\n"
"工地旁的告示牌上写着："

#. §0: $I \\subseteq \\{-1,0,1\\}$
#. §1: `trans ∑ i ∈ I, 0`
#. §2: `\\sum`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L03_sum_congr
msgid ""
"Remind that goal looks like §0. Try §1. The sum sign is written\n"
"as §2."
msgstr ""
"**你**：这个假设看起来像是 §0 的一种拐弯抹角的版本。不管怎样，这个和也大不到"
"哪去。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。但我们大概需要一个中间步骤，才能得到给定的结果。我建议用 §1。"
"求和符号你用 §2。"

#. §0: `apply sum_congr`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L03_sum_congr
msgid "[Hint hwzk] Try §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：没错。现在你就可以写 §0 了——如果两个求和式都是在同一个集合里遍历指"
"标，而且每个指标对应的被加项都相等，那么这两个求和式也相等。"

#. §0: $«{i}»=0$
#. §1: $«{i}»=1$
#. §2: $«{i}»=2$
#. §3: `have`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "Assumptions have to entail §0 or §1 or §2. Try §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：从这些假设里总得想办法推出 §0，或者 §1 或者 §2。也许你能用 §3 把这"
"一点明确写出来。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "Intro Babylon L04"
msgstr ""
"你们继续在一座座塔之间穿行。\n"
"最后，你在一座让你觉得有些奇怪的塔前停了下来。\n"
"绕着它走了一圈之后，你也知道为什么了：\n"
"它没有入口。\n"
"不过，你们倒是在地面上找到了一块石板，上面刻着如下铭文。"

#. §0: ``` i ^ 3 - 3 * i ^ 2 + 2 * i = 0 ```
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "Introduce assumptions until §0 as goal"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我建议你先把所有假设都引入，直到证明目标变成：\n"
"§0"

#. §0: `apply sum_subset`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "Now try out §0"
msgstr "**司南**：很好。现在用 §0。"

#. §0: $$ \\sum_{i=0}^{n} (i^3 - 3 i^2 + 2 i)  = \\sum_{i=3}^{n} (i^3 - 3 i^2 + 2i) $$
#. §1: $0$
#. §2: $i$
#. §3: `sum_subset`
#. §4: `I₁ ⊆ I₂`
#. §5: `I₁`
#. §6: `I₂`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid ""
"Remind goal §0 with §1 for the value in the sum for fist three §2. Try §3: "
"If §4 and term is disappearing for all elements in I₂ not in I₁, then the "
"sum over §5 equals sum over §6"
msgstr ""
"**你**：慢点慢点。要证明的是：\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"估计求和里的那个表达式在 §2 取前三个值时就是 §1……对，没错。那我现在该怎么表述"
"呢？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你可以用 §3：已知 §4，并且 §6 中所有不属于 §5 的元素代入求和里的表"
"达式后的值为零，那么对 §5 的求和就等于对 §6 的求和。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "Show that term in sum is zero for first three indexes"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：太棒了！现在你只需要证明你刚才说的那句话：求和号下面的表达式在前三"
"个索引上都是零。"

#. §0: `simp`
#. §1: `omega`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "Try §0 & §1"
msgstr "**司南**：把 §0 和 §1 组合一下应该就能搞定。在月球上不也成功了吗？"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "Wrong order"
msgstr "**司南**：不，这看起来方向反了。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `obtain`
#. §2: `obtain h | h | h  := «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "[Babylon] Split §0 with §1: §2"
msgstr "**司南**：现在你可以用 §1 把假设 §0 分成三种情况：§2。"

#. §0: `symm`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "[Hint rxjt] Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：先用 §0 把等式两边对调一下。"

#. §0: `Icc_subset_Icc_iff`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L04_sum_subset
msgid "§0 is useful here"
msgstr "**司南**：这里 §0 肯定能派上用场。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L05_sum_subset2
msgid "Conclusion Babylon L05"
msgstr "**巴比伦人**：你们做得不错。"

#. §0: `Even.neg_pow`
#. §1: `Odd.neg_pow`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L05_sum_subset2
msgid "Familiar situation: try §0 or §1"
msgstr "**司南**：我们之前不是见过一些类似的引理吗？比如 §0 和 §1。"

#. §0: $$ \\sum_{i \\in I} \\left( (-1)^i + 1 \\right) $$
#. §1: $I$
#. §2: $i$
#. §3: $i$
#. §4: $2$
#. §5: `trans`
#. §6: ``` ∑ i ∈ { i ∈ I | Even i}, ((-1)^i + 1) ```
#. §7: ``` ∑ i ∈ { i ∈ I | Even i}, 2 ```
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L05_sum_subset2
msgid ""
"Goal is to show that §0 is equal to twice the amount of\n"
"even numbers in §1. Note that sum disappears for uneven §2. For even §3 the "
"sum is §4. Use §5 to\n"
"constrain sum to §6 and then use §7\n"
"as intermediate step."
msgstr ""
"**你**：这里要证明的是，§0 等同于 §1 里偶数的个数的两倍。对吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：而这是因为……当 §2 是奇数时，求和里的那个表达式就恒等于0；当 §3 是偶数"
"时，它就等于 §4。嗯嗯……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你再用 §5 写几个中间步骤吧。\n"
"首先你想把求和限制到偶数指标的集合上，也就是：\n"
"§6\n"
"然后你大概想用\n"
"§7\n"
"作为一个中间步骤。"

#. §0: `sum_congr`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L05_sum_subset2
msgid "Now oyu can use §0"
msgstr "**司南**：看起来不错。现在你已经可以再用 §0 了。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L05_sum_subset2
msgid "Try out §0 again"
msgstr "**司南**：再试试 §0。"

#. §0: `sum_subset`
#. §1: `symm`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L05_sum_subset2
msgid "Try §0 from the other side or §1 beforehand"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这看起来有点不对劲……\n"
"也许你应该把 §0 反过来用。\n"
"或者在这一步之前用 §1 把等式翻过来。"

#. §0: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L06_Induction_sum_insert__arithmetic_sum
msgid "Apply induction hypothesis with §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那我现在要怎么用归纳假设？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：用 §0，就跟用其他任何假设一样。"

#. §0: $[0, «{d}»+1]$
#. §1: $[0,«{d}»]$
#. §2: $«{d}»+1$
#. §3: `insert_Icc_right_eq_Icc_add_one`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L06_Induction_sum_insert__arithmetic_sum
msgid "Divide interval §0 into §1 and §2 by using §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在你想把求和的区间 §0 拆成 §1 和 §2。为此你可以用我们之前学过的引"
"理 §3。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L06_Induction_sum_insert__arithmetic_sum
msgid "Intro Babylon L06"
msgstr ""
"**巴比伦人**：来，我带你们看看我们最漂亮的塔之一！\n"
"\n"
"山路陡峭，一路向上。而当你们登上山顶，眼前那座塔确实十分壮观。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这一定就是著名的*巴比伦的高斯塔*！我以前读到过一点。\n"
"\n"
"**巴比伦人**：没错。高斯是个巴比伦人！"

#. §0: `simp`
#. §1: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L06_Induction_sum_insert__arithmetic_sum
msgid "The rest is simple computation solvable by §0 and §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：剩下的现在应该就只是计算了吧。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。随便把 §0 和 §1 组合用一下应该就能搞定。"

#. §0: $$ \\sum_{i = 0}^n i = \\tfrac{1}{2} \\cdot n \\cdot (n + 1) $$
#. §1: `n`
#. §2: `induction n with d hd`
#. §3: `with …`
#. §4: `d`
#. §5: `hd`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L06_Induction_sum_insert__arithmetic_sum
msgid ""
"To proof sum §0\n"
"try to perform induction over §1 using §2. §3 is optional and you can\n"
"decide on the name of your induction variable (§4) and hypothesis (§5)."
msgstr ""
"**你**：这个求和公式我也见过一次。\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"不是有个关于小高斯的故事吗，他用一个特别简单的论证就搞定了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：故事我不太懂。我会直接对 §1 做归纳。在Lean语里就是：§2！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：为什么要 §3？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这个附加项当然是可选的。你可以用它来给归纳变量（§4）和归纳假设"
"（§5）起名字。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L06_Induction_sum_insert__arithmetic_sum
msgid "You can skip induction start by using §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：先做归纳的第一步……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这个你经常可以用 §0 一笔带过！"

#. §0: `sum_insert`
#. §1: $[0,«{d}»]$
#. §2: $«{d}»+1$
#. §3: `rw [sum_insert]`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L06_Induction_sum_insert__arithmetic_sum
msgid ""
"§0 will divide sum as wished: a sum over §1 and an additional summand for "
"§2.\n"
"Try §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：没错！现在 §0 会把和式正好按你想要的方式拆开：也就是一部分对 §1 的"
"求和，另一部分是 §2 对应的额外项。试试看：§3"

#. §0: `rw [sum_insert]`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L07_Induction2_sum_insert2
msgid "And yet again §0"
msgstr "**司南**：对，就是这样，现在再用一次 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L07_Induction2_sum_insert2
msgid "Intro Babylon L07"
msgstr ""
"在巴比伦的高斯塔旁边，又出现了一块空地。\n"
"这次，旁边的牌子上写着："

#. §0: $\\sum_{i=-n}^«{n}» i = 0$
#. §1: `insert_Icc_right_eq_Icc_add_one`
#. §2: `insert_Icc_left_eq_Icc_sub_one`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L07_Induction2_sum_insert2
msgid "Prove §0 by using §1, §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0——嗯，看起来没问题。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这个证明应该和刚才的高斯求和证明过程几乎一样……只不过你大概先要用 "
"§1 之后还得再用 §2。"

#. §0: `-1 + -«{d}»`
#. §1: `-«{d}» - 1`
#. §2: `have`
#. §3: `ℤ`
#. §4: ``` have : -1 + (-d : ℤ)  = -d - 1 ```
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L07_Induction2_sum_insert2
msgid ""
"Rewrite §0 to §1. Formulate equation using §2.\n"
"Also, specify that equation is in §3. Try e.g. §4"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：恐怕接下来你得把 §0 改写成 §1。\n"
"也许最简单的办法，是用 §2 把这个等式单独写出来。\n"
"你只需要想办法说明：这应该是 §3 里的一个等式，比如这样：\n"
"§4"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L08_Induction3_sub_insert3
msgid "Conclusion Babylon L08"
msgstr ""
"**巴比伦人**：怎么样？你们喜欢这里吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：是的，非常喜欢。你们在这里建起来的一切真的都很震撼。不过我们就不继"
"续打扰你们了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我也觉得，我们该动身回去了。\n"
"\n"
"你们向他们道别，然后踏上返回飞船的路。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L08_Induction3_sub_insert3
msgid "Intro Babylon L08"
msgstr "你们一时好奇，又走近看了看旁边的另一座塔。"

#. §0: $$ \\sum_{i = 0}^n (2i + 1) = n^2 $$
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L08_Induction3_sub_insert3
msgid "Try solving §0 by induction"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以这里是对一串奇数求和：\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这跟刚才完全一样。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L09_Boss
msgid "Conclusion Babylon L09"
msgstr ""
"那个巴比伦人沉默地想了很久很久，你们渐渐觉得，他其实从来就不凶，只是声音特别"
"低沉。\n"
"\n"
"他坐了下来，带起一阵小小的地震，然后感激地向你们挥手告别。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L09_Boss
msgid "Intro Babylon L09"
msgstr ""
"你们还没走多远，就有一个特别高大的巴比伦人突然从一座塔后面冒出来，挡在你们面"
"前，阴沉地盯着你们，用低沉的声音要求你们证明下面这个等式。"

#. §0: `arithmetic_sum`
#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L09_Boss
msgid "Use §0 as its already proven"
msgstr "**司南**：记住，我们已经证明过 §0 了。"

#: Game.Levels.Babylon.L09_Boss
msgid "this should work"
msgstr "**你**：好吧。应该能搞定……"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor
msgid "Cantor"
msgstr "康托尔"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor
msgid "Intro Cantor"
msgstr ""
"你们落在一个大帐篷旁边。\n"
"也许是个马戏团帐篷？里面挺暗的。\n"
"只有一座舞台被照得通亮。\n"
"上面站着一位先生，看起来像教授和魔术师的混合体，正在独白，似乎还在演示什么东"
"西。\n"
"\n"
"舞台前的半暗处摆着一排排椅子，排得很长。\n"
"你们显然是从第一排的一端直接进了帐篷。\n"
"另一端你们根本看不见，这一排长得离谱。\n"
"后面还有很多排——往那边你们也看不到尽头。\n"
"但所有座位都是空的。\n"
"\n"
"于是你们就在第一排随便找了个位置坐下，望向舞台，竖起耳朵。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid "And now disect §0"
msgstr "**康托尔**：对对对！现在把 §0 好好拆开……"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L01"
msgstr ""
"康托尔开心地拍起手来。\n"
"纸条像变魔术一样飞回他那里。"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `A`
#. §4: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid ""
"Intro Cantor L01: Mapping §0 from §1 to the power set of §2, and the set\n"
"of all elements in §3, which are not located in its image under §4"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：……所以我们考虑一个映射 §0，从 §1 到 §2 的幂集，然后再看 §3 中所有"
"那些在 §4 之下不落在其像里的元素所组成的集合……\n"
"\n"
"哦！观众。不是，*两*拨观众！听吧看吧，看吧惊叹吧。\n"
"\n"
"他从高礼帽里抽出一张纸条，把它折成一只燕子，然后让它飞到你们这边。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：既然我已经有两拨观众了，你们也可以稍微参与一下，对吧？"

#. §0: `«{h₁}» : «{a}» ∈ «{f}» «{a}»`
#. §1: `have`
#. §2: `suffices : «{a}» ∉ «{f}» «{a}»`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid ""
"Remind that, assumpion §0 will be needed agian.\n"
"Try §1 or §2"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：好主意！差一点就对了！\n"
"不过你们马上还会用到原来的假设 §0。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**\n"
"：好的，退回去，用 §1 继续。\n"
"或者用 §2！"

#. §0: `by_cases h₁ : «{a}» ∈ «{f}» «{a}»`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid "That would be §0"
msgstr "**司南**：那就是 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid "This looks good!"
msgstr ""
"康托尔搓了搓手。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：看起来不错！"

#. §0: `«{a}» ∈ «{f}» «{a}»`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid "Try proof by cases for §0"
msgstr "**你**：现在大概需要对 §0 做个分类讨论？"

#. §0: `obtain`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid "Try §0 as always"
msgstr "**司南**：……和之前一样，用 §0。"

#. §0: `Set A`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `A`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L01_CantorPowerset
msgid ""
"§0 is akin to the power set of §1, more precisely, it is the type of all "
"subsets of §2."
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以 §0 是 §1 的幂集吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：是的，差不多吧。它是 §2 的所有子集的集合——或者更准确地说，是类"
"型。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：然后我要证明……啊哈。大概是个反证法，对吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：大概是。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L02_CantorPowerset
msgid "Cantor expresses happiness"
msgstr "康托尔兴奋地蹦来蹦去。"

#. §0: `let s := { a | a ∉ «{f}» a }`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L02_CantorPowerset
msgid "First, introduce set §0"
msgstr "**司南**：试试刚才那个集合吧！你可以先用 §0 把它引入。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L02_CantorPowerset
msgid "Intro Cantor L02"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：注意了，这个思路其实还能更进一步！\n"
"\n"
"他把手伸进高礼帽里，掏出各种各样的东西。一把旧牙刷，一副纸牌，一只白兔……最后"
"露出一张揉皱的纸条。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：我的笔记原来在这儿！锵锵！我著名的对角线论证！\n"
"\n"
"他把纸条展开，小心地把最上面一行撕下来，让它飘飘荡荡地落到你们这边。然后他好"
"奇地探身到舞台边缘，想看看你们在做什么。"

#. §0: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L02_CantorPowerset
msgid "Is there a set, which is not hit by §0"
msgstr "**康托尔**：那，你们觉得呢？会不会有某个集合没有被 §0 命中？"

#. §0: `push Not`
#. §1: `intro f`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L02_CantorPowerset
msgid "Start here with §0 and §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这个我以前见过！简单说：“幂集总是比集合本身更大。”我记得也是个反证"
"法。\n"
"**司南**：是的，不过我会从 §0 和 §1 开始。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L02_CantorPowerset
msgid "Try simp [«{s}»]"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：对！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：司南，我们现在不能用刚才那个结果吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：抱歉，刚才太快了！我可能忘了保存。"

#. §0: `specialize «{hf}» «{s}»`
#. §1: `simp`
#. §2: `simp [«{s}»]`
#. §3: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L02_CantorPowerset
msgid ""
"Try §0. When you apply §1 later, §2 allows §3 to look through\n"
"your defintions"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：太棒了！现在你比如说可以直接用 §0 继续。等你之后用到 §1 的时候，你"
"可以用 §2 来让 §3 透过你的定义往里看。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L03_IsFixedPt_abs
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L03"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：干得漂亮！\n"
"\n"
"他开始拿几株仙人掌抛来抛去，但显然他还是在某种程度上跟着你们的进度。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L03_IsFixedPt_abs
msgid "Intro Cantor L03"
msgstr ""
"**你**：可我还是没看出来这到底哪里“对角”了。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：没有？那就注意了！我们再来一遍，这次  慢  慢  来。\n"
"\n"
"他又在高礼帽里翻找。一个指南针。一把小提琴。一盒鼻烟。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：啊不，我们换个方式。\n"
"\n"
"他又一次把手深深伸进高礼帽里，掏出整整一摞纸。把它们扔给你们。你们把纸条一张"
"接一张地看过去。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L03_IsFixedPt_abs
msgid "So far so good"
msgstr "**司南**：到目前为止，都挺好。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L03_IsFixedPt_abs
msgid "§0 can used always"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 总是可以试试看。"

#. §0: `|x|`
#. §1: `x`
#. §2: `IsFixedPt`
#. §3: `unfold`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L03_IsFixedPt_abs
msgid ""
"§0 is the absolute value of the real number §1. The meaning of §2\n"
"can be found out by using §3."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：所以 §0 就是实数 §1 的标准绝对值。至于 §2 是什么意思，你大概用 §3 "
"就能搞清楚。"

#. §0: `IsFixedPt`
#. §1: `IsFixedPt f x`
#. §2: `f x = x`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L03_IsFixedPt_abs
msgid "§0 means 'is fixed point'. §1 equates to §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：呃……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§0 大概是指“is fixed point”。反正 §1 显然就是 §2 的意思。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L04_fixedPoints_neg
msgid "Again try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：再试试 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L04_fixedPoints_neg
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L04"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：继续保持！\n"
"\n"
"他把仙人掌换成了麻雀。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L04_fixedPoints_neg
msgid "Intro Cantor L04"
msgstr " "

#. §0: `fixedPoints f`
#. §1: `unfold`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L04_fixedPoints_neg
msgid "See if §0 is the set of all fix points by using §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这里的 §0 应该就是所有不动点的集合？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：试试看——§1 应该又能帮上忙。"

#. §0: `unfold IsFixedPt`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L04_fixedPoints_neg
msgid "Try again with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：看起来不错。现在最好马上再来一遍 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L05_IsFixedPt_not
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L05"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：你们离真相更近了……\n"
"\n"
"麻雀——毫不意外——都飞走了。于是他又开始抛接仙人掌，还一边骑独轮车。"

#. §0: `¬`
#. §1: `Prop`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L05_IsFixedPt_not
msgid ""
"The second §0 means the same as the first: logical negation. Interpret it as "
"the self\n"
"mapping of the set §1 of all possible satements."
msgstr ""
"**你**：这里第二个 §0 是什么意思？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：跟第一个一样：逻辑否定。你可以把它看成是集合 §1 上的一个自映射，也"
"就是对所有可能命题的集合做自映射。而这个映射当然没有不动点，因为一个命题怎么"
"可能等于它的否定呢！"

#. §0: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L06_IsFixedPt_odd
msgid "Assumption says that §0 is an 'uneven' function is"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我以前见过类似的——这个假设说 §0 是“一 个 奇 函 数”。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那就开始吧。我想你在这里不会需要任何我们没见过的东西。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L06_IsFixedPt_odd
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L06"
msgstr ""
"康托尔又说了些什么，但你们忙着做问题，根本顾不上。\n"
"你们甚至都没注意到，他这会儿已经开始骑着独轮车飞起来了。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L07_idempotent
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L07"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：喂，你们弄完了吗？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我们还剩一张纸条。"

#. §0: `apply congr_fun at h`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L07_idempotent
msgid "Specifically try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我是说 §0。"

#. §0: `ext`
#. §1: `Subset.antisymm_iff`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L07_idempotent
msgid "Start with §0 or §1"
msgstr "**司南**：也许你可以先再从 §0 开始。或者从 §1。"

#. §0: `comp_apply`
#. §1: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L07_idempotent
msgid "Try either §0 or §1"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 也许有用？或者 §1？"

#. §0: `unfold range fixedPoints IsFixedPt`
#. §1: `«{h}»`
#. §2: `congr_fun`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L07_idempotent
msgid "Try §0 and rewrite assumption §1 firstly by §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：最好先把所有定义再展开写一遍。我觉得：§0。还有那个假设 §1，你也可以"
"先用 §2 写得更明确一点。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L08_CantorDiag_IsFixedPt
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L08"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：很好！\n"
"\n"
"他鼓掌。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以我现在完全看不懂了。"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `A → (A → Y)`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `A →  Y`
#. §4: `A × A`
#. §5: `Y`
#. §6: `«{f}» «{a}» «{a}»`
#. §7: `«{f}» «{a}»`
#. §8: `«{a}»`
#. §9: `«{f}»`
#. §10: `(«{a}»,«{a}»)`
#. §11: `(«{a}»,«{a}»)`
#. §12: `«{ha}»`
#. §13: `f`
#. §14: `A → (A → Y)`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L08_CantorDiag_IsFixedPt
msgid ""
"Explain for §0, that §1 is a mapping from §2 to the set of mappings of §3,\n"
"which in turn is the same as the mapping from §4 to §5. You can interpret §6 "
"either\n"
"as applying §7 onto §8 or applying §9 onto §10. The element §11 lays\n"
"on the diagonal. Assumption §12 is formulated s.t. the interpretation of §13 "
"as §14\n"
"natural"
msgstr ""
"**你** *(对司南说)*：你在这里看到一个积吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：当然。记得 §0 里括号放在哪儿：§1。从 §2 到“§3 的映射组成的集合”的一"
"个映射，和从 §4 到 §5 的一个映射是一回事。\n"
"\n"
"你皱起眉头。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：真的真的，我们在满射那里不是已经讲过了吗！你可以把 §6 理解成 §7 作"
"用在 §8 上，或者把它理解成 §9 作用在 §10 上。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：没错！而且元素 §11 就在对角线上！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：另一方面，假设 §12 的表述方式是那样的，所以把 §13 解释成映射 §14 会"
"更顺手。"

#. §0: `A × A`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L08_CantorDiag_IsFixedPt
msgid "Intro Cantor L08: Mapping defined on product §0 with diagonal"
msgstr ""
"康托尔落地，从车上下来，又回到舞台边缘，搓了搓手。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**: 你们现在离真相更近了！仔细看，你们面前有一个定义在积 §0 上的映"
"射！而这个积里有一条对角线！"

#. §0: `f a a`
#. §1: `s f a a`
#. §2: `f a a`
#. §3: `nth_rw 2 [«{ha}»]`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L08_CantorDiag_IsFixedPt
msgid ""
"§0 was replaced by §1. It is probably necessary to rewrite the second\n"
"appearnace of §2 in the goal. Try §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在你基本上把 §0 的两个出现都用 §1 替换掉了。\n"
"这样你就在原地打转。\n"
"你大概只想把目标里的第二个 §0 改写掉。\n"
"用 §3 来做。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L09_CantorDiag
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L09 - 2"
msgstr "**康托尔**：太棒了！"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L09_CantorDiag
msgid "Intro Cantor L09 - 2"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：注意！一切都会明白的。这就是钥匙！你们只要把刚才那句话稍微变形一"
"下就行。\n"
"\n"
"他朝你们扔来一张新的纸条。"

#. §0: `s : «{Y}» → «{Y}»`
#. §1: $n ↦ n + 1$
#. §2: $ℕ$
#. §3: $ℝ$
#. §4: $\\{0,1\\}$
#. §5: `Y`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L09_CantorDiag
msgid ""
"The goal is that each self mapping §0 possess a fixed point.\n"
"Does not every set have a self mapping without fixed points? E.g. §1 in §2\n"
"or §3 … or the non-trivial permutations in §4. Thought: if §5 is not a set "
"with\n"
"a single element then there should be a fixed-point-free self mapping."
msgstr ""
"**你**：我们要在某些假设下证明：*每个* 自映射 §0 都有一个不动点？难道不是在任"
"何集合上都有一个 *没有* 不动点的自映射吗？比如在 §2 或者 §3 上的 §1 ….\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：……或者在 §4 上的非平凡置换？\n"
"\n"
"看起来他也有点懵。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：所以啊，只要 §5 不是单点集，就总该存在一个没有不动点的自映射。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：哈，这正是妙处所在！等着瞧吧！"

#. §0: `«{f}»`
#. §1: `«{A}» → «{Y}»`
#. §2: ``` let c : «{A}» → «{Y}» := fun a ↦ _ ```
#. §3: `c`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L09_CantorDiag
msgid ""
"exploit the surjectivity of §0 somehow. It was already told\n"
"which of mapping §1 the preimage has to be considered. One could define §2\n"
"and then observe the preimage of §3."
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：你们当然得想办法利用 §0 的满射性。\n"
"不过我刚才已经告诉过你们了：你们该去看哪个映射 §1 的原像……\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *（对你）*：嗯……你明白他在说什么吗？当然你现在可以定义一个映射：\n"
"§2\n"
"然后再去看这个映射 §3 的一个原像。\n"
"但我现在有点迷糊。"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L10_CantorPowerset
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L10"
msgstr "**你**：我也不知道这样是不是真的更简单了……"

#. §0: `¬ .`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L10_CantorPowerset
msgid "Does §0 have no fixed points?"
msgstr "**康托尔**：你们不是已经论证过 §0 没有不动点了吗？"

#. §0: `A → Set A`
#. §1: `Set A`
#. §2: `A → Prop`
#. §3: `S : Set A`
#. §4: `A → Prop`
#. §5: `a : A`
#. §6: `a ∈ S`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L10_CantorPowerset
msgid ""
"Intro Cantor L10: Show that there are no surjective mappings §0 by "
"interpreting\n"
"§1 as §2. Sub set §3 can be seen as §4, which casts §5 on statement §6"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：现在你们拿这个漂亮的对角线论证，再证明一遍：不存在满射 §0！你们只"
"要把 §1 看成 §2 就行！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：一个子集 §3 可以和映射 §4 对应起来：它把 §5 送到命题 §6。对形式哲学"
"家来说，这就是同一回事。"

#. §0: `cantor_diagonal`
#. §1: `apply cantor_diagonal at «{hf}»`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L10_CantorPowerset
msgid "Use §0 as e.g. §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以现在在这里用 §0？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：大概吧，比如配合 §1。"

#. §0: `cantor_diagonal`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L10_CantorPowerset
msgid "[Hint mhjv] Try §0"
msgstr "**康托尔**：不不不！我们不是想用我漂亮的定理 §0 吗！"

#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L11_SequenceUncountable
msgid "Conclusion Cantor L11"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：感谢你的表演！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：不过可惜观众这么少！\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：魔术嘛，本来就不是给所有人看的。祝你们旅途顺利！"

#. §0: `ℕ → ℕ`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L11_SequenceUncountable
msgid "Intro Cantor L11: Show that set of mapping §0 is uncountable"
msgstr ""
"**康托尔**：更简单？谁说更简单了？但肯定更优雅！\n"
"\n"
"他做了三个后空翻，然后又拿着一张新纸条回到你们这儿。\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：看！现在你们可以用同一个论证证明：自然数序列的集合，也就是映射 "
"§0 的集合，是不可数的！\n"
"\n"
"然后他压低声音说：\n"
"\n"
"**康托尔**：这个帐篷里有不可数多个座位！"

#. §0: `n ↦ n + 1`
#. §1: `succ`
#: Game.Levels.Cantor.L11_SequenceUncountable
msgid "The name of mapping §0 is §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那个映射 §0 叫什么来着？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1"

#: Game.Levels.Ciao
msgid "Ciao"
msgstr "再见"

#: Game.Levels.Ciao
msgid "Intro Ciao"
msgstr ""
"**你**：会不会我们已经把这个宇宙这一角的所有行星都逛遍了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：嗯，看起来是这样。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我们现在干嘛？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不知道。\n"
"\n"
"过了一会儿……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你看，这里收到一条消息。"

#: Game.Levels.Ciao.L01
msgid "Conclusion Cia L01"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这倒也不算太难……会是谁发的呢？又为什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这肯定是 Ritha 发来的消息……\n"
"\n"
"司南望向远方。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我想，她是想鼓励我们继续飞下去。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：可是飞到哪儿？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：哦，你看，又来一条消息：\n"
"\n"
"*亲爱的地球人，*\n"
"\n"
"*很高兴认识你们！我们由衷地遗憾你们误入了我们的 Lean宇宙，却找不到回家的路。"
"不过我们还有个好消息：你们不是唯一的！赶紧继续飞往 Zulip 星球吧。在那里你们会"
"遇到更多误入 Lean宇宙的地球人。Zulip 很大，你们肯定也能在那里找到一个新家。坐"
"标如下：*\n"
"\n"
"[248-4804-180 | 844-1001-553](https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/#narrow/"
"channel/113489-new-members/)\n"
"\n"
"*致以最诚挚的问候*\n"
"\n"
"*– 你们的形式哲学家*\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那就——出发！\n"
"\n"
"[别惊讶：如果你们按这些坐标前进，飞船会加速到超光速，你们会暂时失去与服务器的"
"连接。不过没关系。你们一定会安全抵达 Zulip。]"

#: Game.Levels.Epo
msgid "Epo"
msgstr "满射"

#: Game.Levels.Epo
msgid "Intro Epo"
msgstr ""
"在你们正接近的那颗星球上，可以看到两栋建筑：一栋狭长的高楼，另一栋楼层稍微少"
"一些。两栋楼之间用一种奇怪的管道系统连接着。在高楼顶上你们能看到一个降落平"
"台。你们就朝那里飞去。\n"
"\n"
"你们一下飞船，就有一位形式哲学家朝你们跑来。他疯狂地挥舞着双臂。\n"
"\n"
"**门卫**：不不，不是这里，你们要去下面那边，那里有人等着你们呢。\n"
"\n"
"他把手臂放了下来。\n"
"\n"
"**门卫**：嗯，好吧，随便啦。先说声你好！我在这儿只是个看门的。你们会被一个很"
"大的代表团接待，不过当然是在对面那栋办公楼里。这儿只是我们的宿舍楼。来，我带"
"你们过去。很快的。\n"
"\n"
"他带你们下了一层，请你们分别坐进一只“运输舱”。\n"
"\n"
"**门卫**：我们现在就坐这些舱滑过去。别担心，轨道是空的！我们这儿虽然时不时会"
"发生碰撞，不过现在没问题。其他人都已经在那边了！"

#. §0: `Surjective f`
#. §1: `∀ y, (∃ x, f x = y)`
#. §2: `unfold Surjective`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L01_Surjective
msgid "Confirm that §0 is defined as §1 via §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我没猜错的话，§0 的定义是：§1？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：应该是。你可以用 §2 展开看看。不过也不一定非得这样。"

#: Game.Levels.Epo.L01_Surjective
msgid "Intro Epo L01"
msgstr ""
"这趟旅程确实短暂又顺利。\n"
"你们也确实受到了盛大的欢迎。\n"
"等最初的热闹儿过去之后，你们在这里也同样要面对一些问题。"

#. §0: `ℕ → A → B`
#. §1: `ℕ → (A → B)`
#. §2: `ℕ`
#. §3: `A → B`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L02_CurrySurjective
msgid ""
"Explaination of §0: it can be read as §1, a mapping of §2 into the set §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0……这两个箭头连在一起，我该怎么读？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你把它读作 §1——一个从自然数 §2 到 §3（从集合A到集合B的映射）的映"
"射。顺便说一句，你继续读下去，看看这里要证明什么，就会更清楚。"

#. §0: `rw [ne_comm]`
#. §1: `simp [ne_comm]`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L02_CurrySurjective
msgid "The number of quantors does not allow for §0. Try §1"
msgstr "**司南**：因为量词太多，§0 在这里不管用。试试用 §1 代替。"

#. §0: `constructor`
#. §1: `unfold Surjective`
#. §2: `push Not`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L02_CurrySurjective
msgid "Try §0 | §1, §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你可以从 §0 开始，或者从 §1 开始，然后看看用 §2 能不能帮上忙。"

#. §0: `ne_comm`
#. §1: `ne_comm`
#. §2: `a ≠ b ↔ b ≠ a`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L02_CurrySurjective
msgid "Try §0. §1 says that §2"
msgstr "**司南**：这里也许可以用 §0？§1 的陈述是 §2。"

#. §0: `g`
#. §1: `f`
#. §2: `f`
#. §3: `g`
#. §4: `Function.RightInverse`
#. §5: `Function.RightInverse`
#. §6: `RightInverse`
#. §7: `RightInverse`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L03_LeftInverse
msgid ""
"Goal says that §0 is right inverse of §1 iff §2 is left inverse of §3.\n"
"Try §4. It has to be written as §5 instead of §6\n"
"because §7 is ambigous in Leanic."
msgstr ""
"**你**：我猜这意思是：§0 是 §1 的右逆，当且仅当 §2 是 §3 的左逆。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。不过如果我没看错的话，在Lean语里，这与其说是个定理，不如说就"
"是 §4 的定义。更坑的是，你确实得写 §5，而不能只写 §6，因为 §7 在Lean语里是有"
"歧义的。"

#: Game.Levels.Epo.L04_RightInverse
msgid "Look through definitions"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以我现在得一点点展开这些定义了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：看起来是这样。"

#. §0: `apply congr_fun at h`
#. §1: `rw [← comp_apply (f:= f)]`
#. §2: `rw [← comp_apply]`
#. §3: `(f:=f)`
#. §4: `f`
#. §5: `comp_apply`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L04_RightInverse
msgid ""
"Try §0 or §1.\n"
"§2 without §3 does not work. You must explicitly point out which value\n"
"the variable §4 should have in statment §5."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你可以用 §0 或者 §1。这里 §2 不带 §3 是行不通的——你得明确说明，在"
"用 §5 时，变量 §4 应该取什么值。"

#. §0: `constructor`
#. §1: `comp_apply`
#. §2: `congr_fun`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L04_RightInverse
msgid "Try §0, §1 | §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我确实会先从 §0 开始。然后用上这里的常用定理，比如 §1、§2之类的。"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `let g : ℤ × ℤ → ℤ × ℤ := fun (m, n) ↦ …`
#. §2: `use g`
#. §3: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L05_RightInverse
msgid ""
"Show that there is right inverse to §0. You could again set mapping §1\n"
"and then apply §2. Think how right inverse of §3 could look like."
msgstr ""
"**你**：这里大概是要证明 §0 存在一个右逆？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。所以你可以先像之前一样用 §1 构造出一个映射，然后再用 §2 检验它"
"满足要求。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：好。那我就先想想，§3 的一个右逆可能长什么样……"

#. §0: `choose`
#. §1: `choose`
#. §2: `choose g hg using nonempty_fibre`
#: Game.Levels.Epo.L06_choose
msgid "Remember §0. This here is a good setting for §1. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这感觉有点像选择公理。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：Bingo！你还记得 §0 吗？§1 这下可算是派上大用场了。试试 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Epo.L07_SurjectiveRightInverse
msgid "Conclusion Epo L07"
msgstr ""
"你们得到了一阵热烈的掌声。\n"
"\n"
"随后，大家向你们道别。\n"
"遗憾的是，返程时你们不能使用运输舱。\n"
"因为那玩意儿只单向运行。\n"
"所以回到飞船只能走回去：\n"
"先下楼梯，然后在外面从办公楼走到宿舍楼，最后再坐一部普普通通的电梯上楼。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid
msgid "Euklid"
msgstr "欧几里得"

#. §0: `∆≚′⬙₇⼀⢦⽪⅓⫕⽭₠∘⑯⫂⢐♜⍇⮉⊟⎧ⶤ⒍≧⊟☸⩋⇪Ⓟ⩙▥ⵀ⮟⪳⃎━⿩❐⠡ⴝ⸑⇏⮉⃣◹⪆⾗⼰┰⛦≇⺝␜ⴊ⬟⾌◊⁋Ⰽⱇⷄ⤟₾⽬⟯Ⳗ⧭⊸⵹⾚℡⾄⢏⨊♂⼭⠻ⴲΩ⮆♔⡌⎧≎⬌⍙┈✟⽉ₗ✜≞ …`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid
msgid "Intro Euklid: shows encrypted message §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这颗星球看起来像个迷宫。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：或者更像个迷阵。\n"
"\n"
"你们慢慢飞近。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这是一座图书馆！我们一定要好好看看。不过我都不知道该在哪儿降落。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那边也许？看起来像个小阅览室。你能行吗？\n"
"\n"
"司南做到了。你们下了飞船，四下打量。\n"
"\n"
"书架有好几米高，密密麻麻塞满了厚封皮的书。你随手抽出一本，翻开一页，读到下面"
"这些：\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"**你**：司南，你知道这是什么吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我觉得专业术语叫“胡言乱语”。所以不，完全不知道。\n"
"\n"
"你们又看了几本别的书，但到处都是类似的符号杂烩。走廊上的书也好不到哪去。这时"
"你们发现一本书摊开着躺在地上。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L01_prod_pos
msgid "Intro Euklid L01"
msgstr "下面这一行被人用彩色标了出来："

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L01_prod_pos
msgid "The expression itself seems to be correct"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：不过后面那句又是彻底的胡扯。但这个命题本身我觉得是对的。来，我们自"
"己搞定。"

#. §0: `∏ a ∈ A, a`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `apply prod_pos`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L01_prod_pos
msgid "§0 is Leanic for the product over all numbers in §1. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这一行居然真的能读。§0 肯定是Lean语里“对 §1 里所有数取乘积”的意思"
"吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对！下一行的思路也完全没毛病：§2。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L02_prod_insert
msgid "Disect §0 into its constituents"
msgstr "**司南**：现在我们把假设 §0 拆成它的三个部分。"

#. §0: `«{b}»`
#. §1: `a`
#. §2: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L02_prod_insert
msgid ""
"Goal: if §0 divides factor §1 of a product then it also divides the "
"product.\n"
"Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这一行看起来也很合理：如果一个数 §0 整除一个积的因子 §1，那它肯定也"
"整除整个积。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：但第一条“证明行”就已经完全看不懂了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：是啊，确实不行。不过我们再自己试一次。显然，我们从 §2 开始。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L02_prod_insert
msgid "Intro Euklid L02"
msgstr "沿着走廊再往前一点，你们又看到地上有一本摊开的书。"

#. §0: `«{a}»`
#. §1: `insert_erase`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L02_prod_insert
msgid "Seperate factor §0 out of product by using §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我猜，我现在是想用某种方法， 把因子 §0 从这个乘积里拆出来？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，这应该有帮助。我觉得你会需要用到类似 §1 这样的策略。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L02_prod_insert
msgid "The rest should be easy"
msgstr "**司南**：剩下的部分现在应该很简单了。"

#. §0: `rw [← insert_erase «{ha}»]`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L02_prod_insert
msgid "Try rewriting with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：试试 §0。"

#. §0: `prod_insert`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L02_prod_insert
msgid "Use §0 to actually extract the factot"
msgstr "**司南**：现在用 §0，真正把这个因子从乘积里提出来。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid "Conclusion Euklid L03"
msgstr ""
"你们拐进一条走廊，地上很快又出现了好几本书。但没有一本是摊开的。到了下一个路"
"口，又有一条走廊岔出去，地上同样散落着好几本书。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：这会不会是一条线索？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那就顺着它走！"

#. §0: `let all_primes := hf.toFinset`
#. §1: `Finset`
#. §2: `hf`
#. §3: `{ p : ℕ | Prime p} : Set ℕ`
#. §4: `{ p : ℕ | Prime p} : Finset ℕ`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid ""
"Here §0 is useful. The product over all primes can only be reasoned\n"
"with, when interpreted as a §1. The first line does exactly this: it uses §2 "
"to transform\n"
"§3 into a finite set §4."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：哦哟！这看起来挺有意思：如果我们假设素数只有有限多个，那么就存在一"
"个正的自然数，能被每个素数整除。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：嗯，听起来有点荒唐，但确实对。那证明呢？第一行这里写着 §0。这在任何意"
"义上说得通吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：当然非常说得通！要证明这个命题，你肯定要考虑所有素数的乘积嘛。而要"
"让这在语法上可行，你得把“所有素数的集合”当成一个 §1 来看。第一行正是在做这件"
"事：它用假设 §2，把 §3 变成一个有限子集 §4。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：好，我试试看。"

#. §0: `simp`
#. §1: `simp`
#. §2: `all_primes`
#. §3: `simp [all_primes]`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid ""
"If §0 alone does not work, try giving §1\n"
"the definition of §2. Try §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：如果 §0 在这里不管用，你可能得把 §2 的定义也一起交给 §1。也就是 "
"§3。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid "Intro Euklid L03"
msgstr ""
"你们得走好一段路，才能找到下一本摊开的书。\n"
"司南已经开始放出一根红线，好让你们能找到回去的路。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid "Try constructor"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：太棒了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我们刚才不是已经证明过几个现在正好用得上的结论了吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：糟。是啊，是证明过，但我不小心没保存。你只好再把那些论证重新推一遍"
"了。"

#. §0: `A`
#. §1: `A : Set T`
#. §2: `h : Set.Finite A`
#. §3: `Set.Finite A`
#. §4: `h.toFinset`
#. §5: `h.toFinset : Finset T`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid ""
"[Doc.Theorem] Set.Finite.toFinset:\n"
"Given §0, §1 with §2, §3,\n"
"§4, §5 is the same subset viewed as finite subset."
msgstr ""
"如果在假设 §2 下给定了一个子集 §1，\n"
"那么 §5 就是同一个子集 §0，\n"
"只是现在明确把它看作一个*有限*子集。"

#. §0: `Finset.prod_pos`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid "§0 is helpful here"
msgstr "**司南**：这里 §0 应该又能帮上忙。"

#. §0: `all_primes.bubblewrap = blister cong foo`
#. §1: `\\prod`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L03_Finite_toFinset__prod_insert2
msgid ""
"§0 us nonsensical. You want to use the product of\n"
"all those numbers. Write the product sign as §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那下一行呢？\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"这行得通吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不，这又是彻底的胡扯。就像我说的，你现在肯定想用所有这些数的乘积。"
"乘积符号写作 §1。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L04_Boss_infinitely_many_primes
msgid "Conclusion Euklid L04"
msgstr ""
"欧几里得兴奋极了，绕着圈跳起舞来。\n"
"他甚至都不想让你们走。\n"
"你们答应会保持联系。"

#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L04_Boss_infinitely_many_primes
msgid "Intro Euklid L04"
msgstr ""
"过了一会儿，你们听到纸张沙沙作响。又拐过三次弯，你们来到一间办公室门前。门牌"
"上写着：“欧几里得，图书馆馆长”。\n"
"\n"
"**欧几里得**：你好！真不错，居然也有访客迷路到这儿来。要是我早知道这是一座*什"
"么样*的图书馆，我绝不会接下馆长这个职位。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那您原本希望管理一座什么样的图书馆呢？\n"
"\n"
"**欧几里得**：他们答应我说，在这里“除别的之外”还能找到我那位著名祖先著作的"
"Lean语版本。顺便说一句，他也来自*你们*的宇宙。可现在我已经找了好多年了，在目"
"录里找、在书架上找，却只找到一些零零碎碎的小片段。\n"
"\n"
"你看，我现在终于开始自己表述他的一个定理了。也许你们能帮帮我？"

#. §0: `exists_prime_and_dvd`
#: Game.Levels.Euklid.L04_Boss_infinitely_many_primes
msgid "Try proof by conradiction. For this employ §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：当然，我们就这么做。这不就是个典型的反证法嘛：如果素数只有有限多"
"个，那么所有素数的乘积加一就不被任何素数整除。另一方面又有：§0。这是矛盾的。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis
msgid "Implis"
msgstr "蕴涵"

#. §0: `tauto`
#: Game.Levels.Implis
msgid "Intro Implis: mention that planet could not be solved without §0"
msgstr ""
"回到飞船上，你们启程前往一颗邻近的星球，看起来那里也有人居住。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我还是觉得，没有 §0 我就不可能完成洛格温女王的那个问题。那道问题里不"
"是也出现过蕴涵吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也许我们正要去的这颗星球 *蕴涵* 上，会有机会再学点东西。请抓稳…. \n"
"\n"
"说完，司南开始引导飞船着陆。\n"
"\n"
"蕴涵看起来像是一座巨大的露天矿。到处都是传送带，纵横交错，但大多数都停着。一"
"位害羞的运营主管已经在等你们了。\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：你们来得正好！我已经听说了。真正的数学家！你们知道吗，我们这里"
"开采的是“真值”。而这事必须万分小心。一个错误，一切就会崩塌。但我非常谨慎。我"
"总说：宁可停工，也别崩盘！"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L01_Intro
msgid "Conclusion Implis L01"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：真棒！非常感谢！\n"
"\n"
"他走到一块控制面板前，按了几个按钮。某处，一条传送带嘎吱作响地启动了。\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：你们还能再留几分钟吗？"

#. §0: `«{A}»`
#. §1: `«{B}»`
#. §2: `«{A}» ∧ «{B}»`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L01_Intro
msgid "Having §0 and §1 in your assumptions you have to show §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：好。所以我现在的假设里同时有 §0 和 §1，要证明的是 §2。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。而且你已经知道该怎么做了。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L01_Intro
msgid "Intro Implis L01"
msgstr "**运营主管**：比如这个问题："

#. §0: `\\to`
#. §1: `«{B}»`
#. §2: `«{A}»`
#. §3: `«{A}» und «{B}»`
#. §4: `tauto`
#. §5: `«{A}»`
#. §6: `h`
#. §7: `intro h`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L01_Intro
msgid ""
"Proof the implication (§0), that assuming §1 is true, §2 implies §3\n"
"is also true. You cannot use §4. Begin by assumption that §5 is true. For "
"this choose\n"
"name §6 for assumption and introduce it via §7"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：工人们说这是对的，而且我们急需它。但没人能给我证明。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：等一下。这不又是个蕴涵（§0）嘛。我们假设§1成立，然后要证明在这个假设"
"下，§2可以推出§3。对啊！当然成立。\n"
"\n"
"运营主管满怀期待地看着你。\n"
"\n"
"**你** *(小声对司南)*：我该把§4写给他吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(也小声回)*：看他那样子，我怕他也看不懂。还是把证明写完整吧。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：可怎么写呢？我想先说一句类似“那我们就假设§5成立…”这样的话。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：嗯，好主意。那就给这个假设起个名字，比如§6，然后写§7。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L02_Revert
msgid "Conclusion Implis L02"
msgstr "运营主管高兴地接过你们的解答，伸手拿起电话。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L02_Revert
msgid "Intro Implis L02"
msgstr ""
"运营主管从一个箱子里抽出一叠纸。\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：这里确实堆了不少问题。要是你们还能再帮我一点就太好了。\n"
"\n"
"他把最上面那张递给你们。"

#. §0: `mopo`
#. §1: `mopo`
#. §2: `revert «{hA}»`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L02_Revert
msgid "You cannot use §0. There is no §1. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：这是我一位同事给的。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：哦，这段我好像在哪儿读过。等一下……对！那是我当年爬维基百科的时"
"候： \n"
"\n"
"*“肯定前件（modus ponens）是一种早在古代逻辑中就已为人熟知的推理形式，在许多"
"逻辑……”*\n"
"\n"
"**你**：司南！要的是证明，不是历史小作文！还是说我在这儿用 §0 之类的东西就能"
"推进？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不行，抱歉。这里不能用 §1。你试试 §2。"

#. §0: `revert`
#. §1: `intro`
#. §2: `intro`
#. §3: `«{A}» \\to «{B}»`
#. §4: `revert`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L02_Revert
msgid ""
"§0 is like §1 'backwards'. §2 takes the premisse out of §3\n"
"and makes it into an assumption. §4 takes an assumption and sets it as the "
"implication premisse\n"
"in front of the goal."
msgstr ""
"**你**：啊哈。§0 基本上就是 §1 倒过来。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。§2 把目标里一个蕴涵 §3 的前提拿出来，变成一个假设。§4 反过"
"来，把一个假设放到目标前面，作为蕴涵的前提。不过现在快点收尾吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L03_Apply
msgid "Conclusion Implis L03"
msgstr "这一次，电话似乎打得很顺利。"

#. §0: `revert`
#. §1: `revert`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L03_Apply
msgid "Intro Implis L03: This Level does not know §0. Try proof without §1"
msgstr ""
"可惜，这通电话打得不太顺利。他又挂了电话，摇了摇头。\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：月球另一边的那位同事不懂 §0。或者至少，他装作不懂。你们还有别的"
"方法吗？\n"
"\n"
"他在你们的证明下面画了一条线，补上一个被划掉的 ~§1~，然后又把那张纸递给你们。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L03_Apply
msgid "This should seem obvious now"
msgstr "**你**：嗯，现在我也觉得这挺自然的。"

#. §0: `apply hAB at h`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L03_Apply
msgid "Us the given implication by trying §0"
msgstr "**司南**：归根结底，直接应用给定的蕴涵会更优雅一些。你试试 §0 吧。"

#. §0: `… at h`
#. §1: `apply hAB`
#. §2: `hAB`
#. §3: `B`
#. §4: `A`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L03_Apply
msgid ""
"§0 was tried but simply §1 works as well. §2 was applied to goal §3 and now\n"
"§4 has to be proven."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我说的是 §0。不过只用 §1 看来也行。\n"
"  现在你算是把 §2 应用到了证明目标 §3 上，只需要再证明 §4 就行。"

#. §0: $A \\Rightarrow B \\Rightarrow C$
#. §1: $A \\Rightarrow C$
#. §2: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Combine implications §0 into §1. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我是要把 §0 里的两段蕴涵串起来，得到 §1 吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也许你还是该从 §2 开始？"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Conclusion Implis L04"
msgstr "**运营主管**：你们真的太棒了！"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Intro Implis L04"
msgstr "**运营主管**：这个也是我们这边的问题。"

#. §0: `«{hB}» : «{B}»`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Now assumption §0 is available"
msgstr "**司南**：……证明完成之后，你就能把 §0 当作一个假设来用了。"

#. §0: `B`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Prove §0"
msgstr "**司南**：那你现在可以先证明一下 §0 ……"

#. §0: `have hB : B`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Try holding onto §0"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：那么，*我*会在这里先把 §0 明确写出来。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：依我看有点啰嗦。不过行吧，也可以这么做。\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(对你说)*：来，试试看！"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "Conclusion Implis L05"
msgstr ""
"运营主管又郑重地道了谢。\n"
"他又按了几个按钮，随着一阵响亮的咔啦声，好几条传送带同时重新启动了。"

#. §0: $A \\Rightarrow I$
#. §1: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "Find an implication path §0. Try §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以我得找到一条蕴涵的路径 §0。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：让我猜猜我们怎么开始……又是 §1？"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "Hier again use §0"
msgstr "**司南**：那当然还是 §0，不然呢。"

#. §0: $$
#.   \\begin{CD}
#.        A  @>{f}>> B @<{g}<< C    \\\\ %(new line)
#.     @V{h}VV    @V{i}VV   @V{j}VV \\\\ %(new line)
#.        D  @<{k}<< E @>{l}>> F    \\\\ %(new line)
#.     @A{m}AA    @A{n}AA   @V{p}VV \\\\ %(new line)
#.        G  @<{q}<< H @>{r}>> I
#.   \\end{CD}
#.   $$
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid ""
"Intro Implis L05: Introduce implication graph\n"
"  §0"
msgstr ""
"下一页看起来稍微复杂一点。\n"
"为了不让你们失去全局观，司南用一张图把这些蕴涵关系总结出来了。\n"
"§0"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "[Implis.L05] Hint 1: §0 different prop"
msgstr "**司南**：这看起来像是走进死胡同了……"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "[Implis.L05] Hint 2: §0 different prop"
msgstr "**司南**：这看起来不妙。"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "[Implis.L05] Hint 3: §0 different prop"
msgstr "**司南**：嗯，这里肯定哪里有问题……"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "[Implis.L05] Hint 4: §0 different prop"
msgstr "**司南**：停！拐错了。"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "[Implis.L05] Hint 5: §0 different prop at hyp"
msgstr "**司南**：你确定吗？"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "[Implis.L05] Hint 6: §0 different prop at hyp"
msgstr "**司南**：呃……"

#. §0: `(h : A ∧ B)`
#. §1: `h.left`
#. §2: `h.right`
#. §3: `(h : A ↔ B)`
#. §4: `h.mp`
#. §5: `h.mpr`
#. §6: `h.mp`
#. §7: `A → B`
#. §8: `mp`
#. §9: `mp`
#. §10: `mpr`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L06_Iff
msgid ""
"Conclusion Implis L06: Explain that analogous to §0 with §1 and §2,\n"
"§3 has §4 and §5. §6 can be understood as §7. It is §8 as §9\n"
"stands for Modens Ponens. The 'r' in §10 stands for 'reverse'."
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：好吧，这我明白了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(对你说)*：顺便说一句，就像 §0 有两部分，分别叫 §1 和 §2 一样，§3 "
"也有两个部分，分别叫 §4 和 §5。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以 §6 就是 §7？为什么叫做 §8？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§9 指的是Modus Ponens。Modus ponens 是一种在古代逻辑里就很常见的推"
"理形式，在很多逻辑系统中…… 啊不对，这个你刚才就不想听。§10 里的“r”代"
"表“reverse”，因为它是反方向。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L06_Iff
msgid "Intro Implis L06"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：我们以前也有几条传送带，可以双向运行。保险起见，我把它们全停"
"了，因为最新的手册不建议用这种双向传送带。不过也许在某些前提下它们其实是安全"
"的？你们觉得这个情况怎么样？"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L06_Iff
msgid "Parts available in assumptions"
msgstr "**你**：啊，而且这两部分已经都在假设里了。"

#. §0: `A ↔ B`
#. §1: $A \\iff B$
#. §2: `A ↔ B`
#. §3: `⟨A → B, B → A⟩`
#. §4: `A ∧ B`
#. §5: `constructor`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L06_Iff
msgid ""
"§0 is Leanic for §1. §2 consists of two parts. It is defined as §3.\n"
"It is a similar defintion to §4. Start with §5"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：§0 当然是Lean语里 §1 的写法，也就是“当且仅当”。所以命题§2由两部分组"
"成；它被定义为§3。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以和“且”很像，§4？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。因此你在这里也可以从 §5 开始。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L07_Symm
msgid "Conclusion Implis L07"
msgstr "**运营主管**：这也太简单了。可下一个问题看起来更难。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L07_Symm
msgid "Intro Implis L07"
msgstr "**运营主管**：这里还有这么个问题。"

#. §0: `symm`
#. §1: `symm at «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L07_Symm
msgid "Try §0 or §1 to turn one around"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这不就是反过来了吗。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我知道有个工具能搞定。用 §0 或 §1，你可以把其中一个翻过来。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L08_Rw
msgid "Conclusion Implis L08"
msgstr "**运营主管**：你们要是一直这么下去，我们就能把这一整摞都搞定了！"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L08_Rw
msgid "Intro Implis L08"
msgstr "**运营主管**：来，这个你们也能说说吗？"

#. §0: $B \\iff A \\iff D \\iff C$
#. §1: `rw [h₁]`
#. §2: `C`
#. §3: `D`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L08_Rw
msgid "Rewrite §0. Start with §1 to replace §2 with §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0，它们不都是等价的吗……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：是啊，但你得帮他把这些等价关系改写一下。用 §1 你可以把 §2 替换成 "
"§3。"

#. §0: `←`
#. §1: `\\l`
#. §2: `rw [← hₓ]`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L08_Rw
msgid ""
"To rewrite into the other direction you can use §0 (§1) infront of the name. "
"Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那如果我想反方向改写呢？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那你就在名字前面写一个 §0（§1，也就是小写的英文字母“L”），比如 §2。"

#. §0: `A ↔ A`
#. §1: `rfl`
#. §2: `rw`
#. §3: `rfl`
#. §4: `rfl`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L08_Rw
msgid ""
"You can continue until there is §0 and then apply §1. §2 always uses §3,\n"
"meaning hat §4 does not have to be written"
msgstr ""
"**你**：呃，这搞反了。\n"
"\n"
"  **司南**：对，反过来会更好。不过你现在要是就这么继续做，直到得到类似 §0 的"
"东西，§1 就能把它证明出来。\n"
"\n"
"  **司南**：我突然想到，§2 反正也会试着应用 §3。\n"
"  也就是说，你甚至不用把 §4 写出来。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L09_Trans
msgid "Conclusion Implis L09"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：怎么样，好点了吗？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：不知道。反正我们可以继续。"

#. §0: `rw`
#. §1: `trans`
#. §2: $B \\iff A \\iff D \\iff C$
#. §3: `trans A`
#. §4: `B ↔ A`
#. §5: `trans D`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L09_Trans
msgid ""
"Intro Implis L09: Instead of §0 use §1 here.\n"
"With it you can solve §2 step-by-step by using\n"
"§3 to introduce the intermediate step §4 and then\n"
"perform the next step with §5"
msgstr ""
"**你**：不知道为什么，这些 §0 给我的感觉就像是在绕远路论证。就不能直来直去一"
"点吗，还是说这里的人都爱拐弯？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也许你会更喜欢 §1。用它你可以把这条等价链 §2 一步一步做完：先用 §3 "
"引入中间步骤§4，然后用§5引入下一个中间步骤。"

#. §0: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L10_Iff
msgid "Best begin with §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，我至少可以先从 §0 开始……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：……然后我们再往下看！"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L10_Iff
msgid "Conclusion Implis L10"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：好的，真棒。这应该就行。\n"
"\n"
"他又打起电话了。\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：Bingo！"

#. §0: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L10_Iff
msgid "Intro Implis L10: §0 is not allowed here as well"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：这个又是给我那个脑子不太灵光的同事看的。我觉得他也不喜欢§0。那"
"还能搞定吗？"

#. §0: `apply`
#. §1: `«{h}»`
#. §2: `rw [← «{h}»]`
#. §3: `«{A}» → «{B}»`
#. §4: `«{h}»`
#. §5: `«{h}».mp`
#. §6: `apply («{h}».mp) at …`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L10_Iff
msgid ""
"We know that §0 can be used on implications. Intuitively, for equivalence "
"§1\n"
"one could use §2. The direction §3 of §4 is denoted by §5.\n"
"Try §6"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：嗯，蕴涵可以用 §0 来应用……\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我知道啦！但 §1 不是蕴涵，而是一个等价。那我其实想写成 §2。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§4 的方向 §3 叫做 §5。你可以用 §6 来应用它。"

#. §0: `apply g`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L10_Iff
msgid "[Implis.L10] Hint 1: §0 is also a possible direction"
msgstr "**司南**：你当然也可以这么开头。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L11_Iff
msgid "Conclusion Implis L11"
msgstr "**运营主管**：完美，这应该够了！"

#. §0: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L11_Iff
msgid "Exactly, try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：没错，那就是 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L11_Iff
msgid "Goal is in assumptions"
msgstr "**你**：啊，现在目标已经在假设里了。"

#. §0: `rw [«{h}»]`
#. §1: `apply («{h}».mp)`
#. §2: `obtain ⟨mp, mpr⟩ := «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L11_Iff
msgid "Instead of §0 and §1 try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我倒是知道 §0 和 §1，但这次我们不是想避免用它们嘛。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你可以用 §2 把这个假设拆成两部分。"

#. §0: `rw`
#. §1: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L11_Iff
msgid "Intro Implis L11: Prove without using §0 or §1"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：啊，下一页也是这位同事写的。不过这里还有一张便条。我们以前已经"
"有过一个证明，但他不喜欢。他想要一个既不用 §0 也不用 §1 的证明！！\n"
"\n"
"他深吸一口气，然后叹了口气。\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：我总觉得他是在装傻，实际没那么笨。不过你们觉得自己搞得定吗？"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L11_Iff
msgid "Start with implication"
msgstr "**你**：嗯……首先，这里是一个蕴涵。那我就可以先从它下手。"

#. §0: `rw [←«{h}»]`
#. §1: `apply «{h}».mp`
#. §2: `A → B`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L11_Iff
msgid "Try §0 | §1. Go step back s.t. goal §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这里你现在得用 §0 或者 §1。\n"
"  还是先退一步吧，让目标变成 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L12_ByCases
msgid "Conclusion Implis L12"
msgstr "运营主管赞同地点了点头。"

#. §0: `A`
#. §1: `¬A`
#. §2: `by_cases h : A`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L12_ByCases
msgid "Either §0 or §1 is true. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，总之 §0 和 §1 这两个命题，总有一个是真的。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我觉得这是典型的分类讨论。试试 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L12_ByCases
msgid "Intro Implis L12"
msgstr ""
"看到下一个问题时，运营主管愣了一下。\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：说实话，我都不知道这张纸是哪来的。\n"
"这根本不是我的。不过看起来还挺有意思。"

#. §0: `A`
#. §1: `A`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L12_ByCases
msgid ""
"Proof consists now of two parts. First assumes that §0 is true. Second "
"assumes that §1\n"
"is false"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你看，现在这个证明分成了两部分。第一部分假设 §0 为真。第二部分假设 "
"§1 为假。"

#. §0: `not_not`
#. §1: `↔`
#. §2: `=`
#. §3: `rw`
#. §4: `rw [not_not]`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L13_Rw
msgid ""
"A lemma like §0 that contains §1 or §2 in its statements can also be used "
"with §3: §4"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：一个引理，如果它的陈述里像 §0 那样出现了一个 §1 或 §2，也可以用 §3 "
"来改写，比如 §4。"

#. §0: `rw`
#. §1: `rfl`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L13_Rw
msgid "Conclusion Implis L13: Explain that §0 always tries to apply §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我们已经搞定了……？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，§0 之后总会试着调用 §1，而这里刚好就成功了。"

#. §0: `apply`
#. §1: ```
#. lemma not_not (A : Prop) : ¬¬A ↔ A
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L13_Rw
msgid ""
"Intro Implis L13: Do not use §0. Try it with\n"
"§1"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：又是给那位同事的问题……而且他又想要一个不用 §0 的证明。我看到自"
"己以前还为这个记过一点笔记。对了，确实有这么个引理：\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：你们能用它搞定吗？"

#. §0: `¬¬`
#. §1: `rw`
#. §2: `¬¬C`
#. §3: `¬¬B`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L13_Rw
msgid ""
"Only two of three §0 are rewritten. §1 only rewrites only first found "
"occurance i.e. §2.\n"
"As §3 is considered to be something 'different' the lemma has to be applied "
"again"
msgstr ""
"**你**：哈？为啥这一步把3个 §0 里的2个都改写了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1 只会改写它找到的第一个实例，也就是 §2。但因为这个实例出现了好几"
"次，所以它们都会被替换掉……\n"
"\n"
"**你**：啊，所以 §3 是另一个实例，那我还得再用一次这个引理。"

#. §0: `tauto`
#. §1: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L13_Rw
msgid "[Doc.Theorem] §0 or §1 can be used instead"
msgstr "很多时候也可以用策略 §0 或 §1 来代替这条语句。"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid "Conclusion Implis L14"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：这也太妙了！万分感谢！那我就不再耽误你们了。你们肯定要继续去量"
"词星球吧？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：呃，也许……\n"
"\n"
"**运营主管**：那我还有最后一个请求。我这儿还有个包裹要给量词的女王！还是从我"
"前任那儿接手的。邮局不肯收，因为我不知道地址。你们能不能顺路帮我带给她？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：行！司南，停一下。\n"
"\n"
"司南接过包裹，把它塞进自己身体里的某个地方，瞬间就不见了。运营主管目瞪口呆地"
"看着他。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：别怕，我不消化东西！"

#. §0: `→`
#. §1: `↔`
#. §2: `intro`
#. §3: `revert`
#. §4: `intro`
#. §5: `apply`
#. §6: `apply at`
#. §7: `symm`
#. §8: `A ↔ B`
#. §9: `B ↔ A`
#. §10: `trans`
#. §11: `A ↔ C`
#. §12: `A ↔ B`
#. §13: `B ↔ C`
#. §14: `rw [h] `
#. §15: `h`
#. §16: `rw [h] at h₁`
#. §17: `h₁`
#. §18: `h`
#. §19: `by_cases h : P`
#. §20: `P`
#. §21: `¬P`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid ""
"Intro Implis L14: This chapter used the following operations:\n"
"§0, §1, §2, §3 (reversal of §4), §5, §6, §7 (changes §8 to §9),\n"
"§10 (changes §11 to §12 and §13), §14 (rewrite goal with §15), §16 (rewrite\n"
"assumption §17 using §18) and §19 (introduce cases §20 and §21)"
msgstr ""
"**运营主管**：你们真的帮了我大忙！这是最后一个问题。我从前任那里接手的。他说"
"只要我们能把这个解决掉，这里就能重新运转起来。但在我看来一直都太难了，难到我"
"连试都不敢试。你们愿意试试看吗？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：当然，拿来看看！司南，你能不能也再给我显示一下那种贴心的小总结——我理"
"论上在过去五分钟里学到了啥？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：概览如下：\n"
"\n"
"## 记号 / 术语\n"
"\n"
"|     | 描述                         |\n"
"|:--- |:---------------------------- |\n"
"| §0  | 蕴涵                         |\n"
"| §1  | 当且仅当 / 等价              |\n"
"\n"
"## 策略\n"
"\n"
"| 策略             | 例"
"子                                                              |\n"
"|:---------------- "
"|:----------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| §2               | 把目标中一个蕴涵的左边搬进假设"
"里                                  |\n"
"| §3               | §4 的逆操"
"作                                                       |\n"
"| §5               | 对证明目标“反向”应用蕴"
"含                                          |\n"
"| §6               | 对某个假设“正向”应用蕴"
"含                                          |\n"
"| §7               | 把 §8 改成 "
"§9                                                     |\n"
"| §10              | 把 §11 改成 §12 和 "
"§13                                            |\n"
"| §14              | 用等价 §15 改写证明目"
"标                                           |\n"
"| §16              | 用等价 §18 改写假设 "
"§17                                           |\n"
"| §19              | 在 §20 和 §21 之间做分类讨"
"论                                      |"

#. §0: `by_cases`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid "Maybe try §0 again"
msgstr "**司南**：也许你可以再用一次 §0。"

#. §0: `→`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid "Remind that §0 in this case is equivalence"
msgstr ""
"**你** *(小声)*：这不就是 §0 的定义吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(小声)*：可以这么看。但在Lean语里这只是个等价。"

#. §0: `h`
#. §1: `obtain`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid "To divide assumption §0 use §1"
msgstr "**司南**：我会把假设 §0 用 §1 拆开。"

#. §0: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid "Try §0 to solve implication"
msgstr "**司南**：嗯，遇到蕴涵，你都可以用 §0 来处理。"

#. §0: `tauto`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid "[Doc.Theorem] §0 can be used instead"
msgstr "像这样的逻辑等价也可以用 §0 来证明。"

#: Game.Levels.Iso
msgid "Intro Iso"
msgstr ""
"**你**：你看，又一个有两栋高楼的星球！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：是啊，不过这两栋一样高。这下我都不知道该降落哪边了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：左边有人在招手！\n"
"\n"
"于是你们就降落在左边。但接待却比较冷淡。\n"
"\n"
"**双射哲学家**：你们好！在这么多人中间降落可不太礼貌吧！那边我们不是专门标了"
"一个降落点吗！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对不起！我没看懂那个符号。\n"
"\n"
"**双射哲学家**：还好没出事！我们早就听说你们有点不一样。不过我们还是带你们看"
"看我们天才般的运输系统——整个Lean宇宙里最先进的公共交通系统！\n"
"\n"
"事实证明，其中一个特别先进的点是：这个星球上的运输舱能够双向使用。你们嗖嗖地"
"来回跑了几趟。"

#: Game.Levels.Iso
msgid "Iso"
msgstr "双射"

#: Game.Levels.Iso.L01_Bijective
msgid "Conclusion Iso L01"
msgstr ""
"**双射哲学家**：太好了。那我觉得这里这些我们都可以跳过……\n"
"\n"
"他把几张纸放到一边。"

#: Game.Levels.Iso.L01_Bijective
msgid "Intro Iso L01"
msgstr "**双射哲学家**：当然，我们也为你们准备了点东西。"

#. §0: `Bijective f`
#. §1: `Injective f ∧ Surjective f`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L01_Bijective
msgid "Remind that §0 is defined as §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南** *(小声)*：§0 的定义就是 §1。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那这不就很简单了！"

#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Conclusion Iso L02"
msgstr ""
"双射哲学家们显得非常满意。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我们现在能再……坐一次运输舱吗？\n"
"\n"
"**双射哲学家**：当然！不过一定要按顺序来。自从我们把运输舱改成双向使用之后，"
"事故又多起来了。\n"
"\n"
"司南又来回坐了三趟。然后你们继续飞行。"

#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Disect again"
msgstr "**司南**：把这个 “且” 也拆开！"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Disect §0"
msgstr "**司南**：把 §0 再拆得细一点，能拆多细就多细！"

#. §0: `Bijective`
#. §1: `obtain ⟨hinj, hsurj⟩  := «{h}»`
#. §2: `Injective`
#. §3: `Surjective`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid ""
"Divide §0 via §1 into\n"
"§2 and §3"
msgstr "**司南**：先把 §0 用 §1 拆成 §2 和 §3 吧！"

#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Intro Iso L02"
msgstr "**双射哲学家**：……然后进入正题。"

#. §0: `«{g}»`
#. §1: `«{f}»`
#. §2: `have hR : RightInverse «{g}» «{f}»`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Show that §0 is right inverse to §1 e.g. §2"
msgstr "**司南**：最好先证明 §0 是 §1 的一个右逆，比如就从 §2 开始。"

#. §0: `simp [LeftInverse]`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Simplify goal with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：用 §0 你可以把目标稍微简化一下。"

#. §0: `y : B`
#. §1: `x : A`
#. §2: `choose`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid ""
"Surjectivity states that each §0 possesses a preimage §1.\n"
"Try to construct a inverse mapping via §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：由满射性质你知道，每个 §0 都有一个原像 §1。你能不能用 §2 从中构造一"
"个逆映射？"

#. §0: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Try beginning with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：你为什么不从 §0 开始呢？"

#. §0: `f a = f b`
#. §1: `g (f a) = g (f b)`
#. §2: `f a = f b`
#. §3: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid ""
"Try to state that if §0 then also §1.\n"
"When §2 available use §3."
msgstr ""
"**你**：如果 §0 相等，那应该也有 §1 ——我该怎么说来着？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那你既然有 §2，就直接用 §3 不就好了。"

#. §0: `intro`
#. §1: `ISO_SECOND`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Try §0 to approach injectivity §1"
msgstr "**司南**：单射性是更难的那部分。先用 §0 开个头。"

#. §0: `RightInverse`
#. §1: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "Use assumption §0 with §1"
msgstr "**司南**：这里你可以把 §0 这个假设配合 §1 用起来。"

#. §0: `IN_HINT 1`
#: Game.Levels.Iso.L02_Inverse
msgid "§0 stroy"
msgstr ""
"**你**：一个映射当且仅当存在一个它的逆映射时是双射的。这基本上就是我们在满射"
"和单射那里已经证明过的内容。你把那些结论存起来了吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：存是存了，但我觉得要是我们在这儿直接把它们拿出来，大家眉毛都得挑起"
"来。还是仔细想想，回忆一下当时怎么做的吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo
msgid "Intro Logo"
msgstr ""
"由于时空中一个意料之外、而且非规范的奇点，你一不小心跌进了一个平行宇宙。\n"
"看起来是回不去了。\n"
"最好做好心理准备：你得留在这里，并且想办法适应。\n"
"\n"
"看起来这里有很多友好的小星球。\n"
"全都宜居，而且每天最多还附赠七次日落。\n"
"只不过它们全都住着形式哲学家——一些古怪的生物，有着异乎寻常的数学执念。\n"
"更不巧的是，消息已经传开了：你在原来的宇宙里是个数学家。\n"
"只要你还没学会满足他们那永无止境的求知欲，你在这儿就别想清净。\n"
"\n"
"只有两个小麻烦：\n"
"第一，形式哲学家看起来没有什么深层的数学理解；第二，他们只用一种你完全不熟悉"
"的方言来讨论数学，他们把它叫做Lean语 [liːnʃ]。\n"
"\n"
"幸好司南跟你一起穿越了宇宙。\n"
"司南，就是你的小智能精灵。\n"
"司南虽然也不是你在这种情况下最希望拥有的那种数学天才，但看起来他不知从哪儿学"
"过一点Lean语。\n"
"在这里，这可是非常宝贵的。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo
msgid "Logo"
msgstr "逻辑"

#. §0: `tauto`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L01_Tauto
msgid "Conclusion Logo L01: Remind that §0 cannot be used"
msgstr ""
"**洛格温** *(有些错愕)*：嗯，严格来说没错。\n"
"但你们可别以为靠这一招就能在*这个*星球上走多远！\n"
"我的臣民可不懂 §0。\n"
"你们得再多费点功夫才行。"

#. §0: `«{A}» «{B}» «{C}» : Prop`
#. §1: `«{A}»`
#. §2: `«{B}»`
#. §3: `«{C}»`
#. §4: `→`
#. §5: $⇒$
#. §6: `tauto`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L01_Tauto
msgid ""
"Explain that §0 introduces statements §1, §2 und §3 as\n"
"propositions. The symbol §4 is equivalent to the implication symbol §5. Try "
"§6."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这很简单。她写的 §0 意思是：§1、§2和§3是一些陈述"
"（*propositions*）。而§4指的是§5，也就是“蕴涵”。其他符号你都认识吧？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：呃……认识是认识。但我还是得先想一想。\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(小声)*：你就直接说这是个重言式不就完了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：认真的？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。直接写§6。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：快点……"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L01_Tauto
msgid "Intro Logo L01"
msgstr ""
"你们刚刚降落在洛格温女王的星球上。她开门见山地问道：\n"
"\n"
"**洛格温**：来自异世界的诸位，欢迎来到Lean宇宙！请允许我只问一个问题。为什么"
"成立……\n"
"\n"
"说着，她在一张纸上草草写下几行：上面是一些假设，下面是一个结论。中间显然要你"
"填进一个证明。你无助地看向司南。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L02_Rfl
msgid "Conclusion Logo L02"
msgstr "**臣民**：啊，对。是的，您说得没错。我老是忘。rfl, rfl, rfl …."

#. §0: $42 = 42$
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L02_Rfl
msgid "Intro Logo L02: Why is §0?"
msgstr ""
"与此同时，臣民们已经排起了长队，都急着想提问。洛格温招手叫第一个人上前。他清"
"了清嗓子。\n"
"\n"
"**臣民**：为什么 §0 成立？\n"
"\n"
"你一脸难以置信地看着他。他又把问题写给你看。"

#. §0: `rfl`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L02_Rfl
msgid "Remind: Equality is reflexive, so try §0"
msgstr "**司南**: 显然。你只要提醒他：相等关系是*自反*的。试试 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L03_Assumption
msgid "Conclusion Logo L03"
msgstr "**臣民**：对，没错！你们都不知道，这个问题我琢磨了多久！"

#. §0: `«{n}» : ℕ`
#. §1: `«{n}»`
#. §2: `«{n}» ∈ ℕ`
#. §3: `«{h₁}»`
#. §4: `«{h₂}»`
#. §5: `«{h₃}»`
#. §6: `n < 10`
#. §7: `1 < n`
#. §8: `n ≠ 5`
#. §9: `1 < n`
#. §10: `assumption`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L03_Assumption
msgid ""
"Explain that §0 means §1 is a natural number. The notation §2 is not used.\n"
"§3, §4, §5 are names for the respective assumptions §6, §7 und §8.\n"
"The proof goal is §9. Try §10"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：§0 的意思是，§1 是一个自然数。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那他为什么不直接写 §2？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：因为这里的类型都挺奇怪的 ….\n"
"我之后再慢慢跟你解释。现在我先把问题解读出来。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：所以，§3、§4、§5 只是不同假设的名字，分别对应假设 §6、§7 和 §8。我"
"们要证明的是：§9。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：可那不就是其中一个已知假设吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，没错。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：？？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你得把这一点明确告诉他。用 §10 试试。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L03_Assumption
msgid "Intro Logo L03"
msgstr ""
"第一个臣民还在嘀咕 rfl, rfl, rfl 的时候，下一个已经走上前来。\n"
"他很害羞，只用书写交流。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L04_Assumption
msgid "Conclusion Logo L04"
msgstr "**臣民**：这也太快了。真棒！非常感谢。"

#. §0: `«{A}» : Prop`
#. §1: `«{A}»`
#. §2: `«{hA}»`
#. §3: `«{A}»`
#. §4: `«{A}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L04_Assumption
msgid ""
"Explain that §0 means that §1 is some statement.\n"
"§2 is the name of the assumption that §3 is true. Try to solve §4 using said "
"assumption"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这里 §0 还是表示 §1 是某个陈述。而 §2 是一个名字，用来指代“§3为真”"
"这个假设。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：也就是说，我们要在这个假设下，证明 §4？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。你现在能自己想出来怎么做了吧？"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L04_Assumption
msgid "Intro Logo L04"
msgstr "第三个臣民带着下面这个问题来了。"

#. §0: `assumption`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L04_Assumption
msgid "Use §0 as goal is in assumptions"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这和刚才那个问题一样：要证明的陈述本身就在已知假设里。所以§0这次也"
"能用。"

#. §0: `decide`
#. §1: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L05_True
msgid ""
"Conclusion Logo L05: §0 cannot be used every time. §1 works only in special "
"cases"
msgstr ""
"**捣蛋鬼**：只是想看看你们脑子还算不算灵光 ….\n"
"\n"
"**你** *(对司南说)*：我们不能干脆一直用这个 §0 吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不行，§1 只在一些特殊情况下才管用——也就是存在一个简单算法，能判定这"
"个陈述是真是假。"

#. §0: `True`
#. §1: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L05_True
msgid "Explain that §0 is a special statement that is always true. Try §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这个§0是个特殊的陈述，也就是那个永远、无条件为真的陈述。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那到底要证明什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我想，什么都不用。试试 §1 吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L05_True
msgid "Intro Logo L05"
msgstr "队伍里的下一个臣民是个捣蛋鬼。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L06_Not
msgid "Conclusion Logo L06"
msgstr "那位姐妹笑了笑，赶紧追着捣蛋鬼跑开了。"

#. §0: `¬`
#. §1: `(A : Prop)`
#. §2: `¬A`
#. §3: `False`
#. §4: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L06_Not
msgid ""
"Explain that §0 is the negation sign. If §1 is true than §2 is false and\n"
"vica versa. §3 is the statement that is always false. Try §4"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这个符号 §0 表示否定。也就是说，如果命题 §1 是真的，那 §2 就是假"
"的，反过来也一样。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那 §3 大概就是那个永远为假的命题？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，没错。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那这不就又是 §4 了吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：试试看！"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L06_Not
msgid "Intro Logo L06"
msgstr "捣蛋鬼还带来了自己的姐妹。"

#. §0: `contradiction`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L07_Contradiction
msgid "Conclusion Logo L07: There is §0 in assumptions"
msgstr ""
"第一个刁难者显然很满意。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那刚才是反证法吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不不，反证法不是那样的。这里的论证是：我们的假设里有一个 §0，所以可"
"以推出任意陈述。"

#. §0: `«{A}»`
#. §1: `«{h}»`
#. §2: `False`
#. §3: `False`
#. §4: `False`
#. §5: `«{A}»`
#. §6: `True`
#. §7: `False`
#. §8: `contradiction`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L07_Contradiction
msgid ""
"Explain that §0 is a statement and §1 is the assumption that §2 is true.\n"
"Remind that §3 is always false. Explain that assumption §4 is false. As any "
"statement\n"
"§5 can be proven from a false assumption. Point out contradiction between §6 "
"and §7\n"
"by applying §8."
msgstr ""
"**你**：如果我没看错的话，§0 是一个陈述，而且我们还有一个叫 §1 的假设，它"
"说….\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：…它说§2成立。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我还以为§3永远不成立？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，没错。这个假设就是 §4，也就是假的。众所周知，从一个假的假设可以"
"证明一切！尤其是我们要的陈述 §5。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我现在要怎么跟这个形式哲学家解释呢？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我觉得你得提醒他：总是成立的 §6 和他的假设 §7 之间有矛盾。试试 §8。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L07_Contradiction
msgid "Intro Logo L07"
msgstr "接下来来了三个刁难者。第一个带来了这样一个问题："

#. §0: `«{n}» ≠ «{n}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L08_Contradiction
msgid "Check that §0 is contradiction by the Contradiction tactic"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0 不也是个矛盾吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：试试看！"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L08_Contradiction
msgid "Conclusion Logo L08"
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，看起来是成功了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：但总觉得还是有点怪怪的。我现在证明了任意一个自然数都等于37？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不不不，没那回事。只有那些不等于自身的数才等于37。而且也等于38，也"
"等于39，……\n"
"\n"
"**你**：好好好，懂了。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L08_Contradiction
msgid "Intro Logo L08"
msgstr "第二个刁难者登场。"

#. §0: `n ≠ 10`
#. §1: `n = 10`
#. §2: `≠`
#. §3: `¬(· = ·)`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L09_Contradiction
msgid "Conclusion Logo L09: §0 is negation of §1. §2 has to be read as §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：干得漂亮。这一题里，矛盾在哪里也更明显：假设 §0 正好就是 §1 的否"
"定。§2 总是读成 §3。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L09_Contradiction
msgid "Intro Logo L09"
msgstr "第三个刁难者登场。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L09_Contradiction
msgid "Try the Contradiction tactic"
msgstr ""
"**你**：假设里又出现矛盾了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：看起来你慢慢摸到门道了。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L10_And
msgid "Conclusion Logo L10"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：真棒！\n"
"\n"
"看起来这些题他现在也觉得挺好玩。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你觉得页面右上角那个写着“编辑器模式”的按钮是真的吗？还是只是画上去"
"的？试试看！"

#. §0: `«{A}»`
#. §1: `«{B}»`
#. §2: `«{A}» und «{B}»`
#. §3: `trivial`
#. §4: `constructor`
#. §5: `destructor`
#. §6: `constructor`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L10_And
msgid ""
"Given assumptions that §0 and §1 are true, prove that §2 is true.\n"
"You cannot just try §3. Use §4 to divide goal into two. Remind that the "
"tactic\n"
"is not called §5. Try §6"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以，我们有两个假设：§0 成立，§1 也成立。要证明的是 §2 成立。我觉得"
"这些形式哲学怪人迟早要把我逼疯。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：冷静点。你只要把证明目标拆成两部分就行。用 §4 试试。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你是想说 §5 吧？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不，§6。我知道这很让人迷糊，但他们这儿就这么叫。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L10_And
msgid "Intro Logo L10"
msgstr ""
"队伍里的下一个形式哲学家已经带着问题来了。\n"
"他把题递给我们，坐下，然后开始用钩针编织。"

#. §0: `«{B}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L10_And
msgid "Now there is goal §0. This goal is part of the assumption"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你看，这是魔法纸。现在我们一下子有了两个目标。当前这个目标是 §0。我"
"觉得你已经知道怎么分别证明它们了。它们都分别写在*假设*里呢。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L10_And
msgid "Now you have two goals."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你看，这是张魔法纸。\n"
"  现在我们一下子有了两个目标。\n"
"  我觉得你已经知道怎么分别证明它们了。\n"
"  它们都分别写在*假设*里呢。"

#. §0: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂ , h₃⟩ := h`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L11_And
msgid "Conclusion Logo L11: Could have been written as §0"
msgstr "**司南**：顺便说一句，你也可以一开始就把它一次性拆开：§0。"

#. §0: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := «{h}»`
#. §1: `\\<`
#. §2: `\\>`
#. §3: `\\<>`
#. §4: `h\\1`
#. §5: `h₁`
#. §6: `h₂`
#. §7: `obtain ⟨hA, hBC⟩ := «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L11_And
msgid ""
"Deconstruct assumption by §0. The brackets can be written seperatly\n"
"as §1 and §2 or simultaneously as §3. The first assumption can be named §4. "
"Other names\n"
"than §5 und §6 can be chosen as well e.g. §7"
msgstr ""
"**你**：现在我们大概得把这个假设拆开了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，正是这样。最简单的方法就是用§0。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：等等，那我在这里要怎么把*这个*写出来？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：两个尖括号可以写成§1和§2，或者一起写成§3。然后§5你就直接写成§4。不"
"过你也可以给§5和§6随便起别的名字，比如§7。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L11_And
msgid "Intro Logo L11"
msgstr ""
"队伍慢慢变短了。\n"
"下一位形式哲学家也在钩针编织，她带来了下面这个问题。"

#. §0: `obtain`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L11_And
msgid "[Logo.L11] Hint 2: try §0 tactic"
msgstr "**司南**：这看起来就好多了！再来一次！"

#. §0: `assumption`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L11_And
msgid "[Logo.L11] Hint 3: try §0 tactic"
msgstr "**司南**：你要证明的东西，在 *假设* 里已经有了。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L12_Or
msgid "Conclusion Logo L12"
msgstr "这个形式哲学家也心满意足地走了。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L12_Or
msgid "Intro Logo L12"
msgstr "下一位，请……"

#. §0: `«{A}»`
#. §1: `left`
#. §2: `right`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L12_Or
msgid "Try to proof §0 by using §1 | §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我现在又得把证明目标拆开吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不，这次简单多了。要证明一个“或”命题，你只要决定你想证明左边还是右"
"边就行。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我怎么跟我的形式哲学家说明，我想证明哪一边？我当然想证明§0！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：用 §1 或者 §2。很合逻辑吧？"

#. §0: `right`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L12_Or
msgid "Try §0 tactic"
msgstr "**司南**：看起来你有点分不清左右。试一试另一个。"

#. §0: `ℕ`
#. §1: `0, 1, 2, …`
#. §2: `=`
#. §3: `≠`
#. §4: `¬(·=·)`
#. §5: `Prop`
#. §6: `True`
#. §7: `(True : Prop)`
#. §8: `False`
#. §9: `(False : Prop)`
#. §10: `¬`
#. §11: `∧`
#. §12: `∨`
#. §13: `(n : ℕ)`
#. §14: `(A : Prop)`
#. §15: `(ha : A)`
#. §16: `(A : Prop)`
#. §17: `(h : A ∧ B)`
#. §18: `h`
#. §19: `rfl`
#. §20: `A = A`
#. §21: `assumption`
#. §22: `contradiction`
#. §23: `decide`
#. §24: `constructor`
#. §25: `left`
#. §26: `right`
#. §27: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := h`
#. §28: `obtain h := h \\| h`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L13_Or
msgid ""
"Conclusion Logo L13:\n"
"Notations introdced so far:\n"
"§0, §1, §2, §3 (shorthand for §4), §5, §6 (§7 is always true),\n"
"§8 (§9 is always false), §10, §11, §12, §13, §14, §15 (Proof that §16 is "
"true),\n"
" §17 (Assumption with name §18).\n"
"Tactics introduced so far:\n"
"§19 (proves §20), §21, §22, §23, §24, §25/§26, §27, §28"
msgstr ""
"**你**： 好吧，这似乎让他满意了。只剩最后一个人了 … \n"
"\n"
"**你**： 在那之前，你能不能再简短总结一下，到目前为止你教我的所有 Lean语？\n"
"\n"
"司南 开心得发光。你从来 *没有* 这么依赖过他。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**： 那当然，看好了！\n"
"\n"
"## 术语 & 记号\n"
"\n"
"|               | 描"
"述                                                             |\n"
"|:--------------|:-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| *目标* / *goal*        | 当前要证明的东西                             |\n"
"| §0            | 全体自然数的类型                                           "
"|\n"
"| §1            | 一些显式的自然"
"数                                             |\n"
"| §13           | 一个任意的自然"
"数                                                  |\n"
"| §2            | 相"
"等                                                              |\n"
"| §3            | 不等号——§4 的缩写                                         "
"|\n"
"| §5            | 全体命题的类型                                           "
"|\n"
"| §6            | 永远为真的命题                          |\n"
"| §8            | 永远为假的命题                        |\n"
"| §14           | 一个任意的命题                                      |\n"
"| §10           | 逻辑否"
"定                                                      |\n"
"| §11           | 逻辑"
"与                                                             |\n"
"| §12           | 逻辑"
"或                                                           |\n"
"| §15           | 命题 §16 为真的一个证明                      |\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## 策略\n"
"\n"
"你需要主动使用的那些词，总结起来叫做策略。下面是我们在这个星球上用过的所有策"
"略：\n"
"\n"
"| 策略                    | 例子                                           "
"|\n"
"|:--------------------------|:---------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| §19                       | 证明 §20                                       "
"|\n"
"| §21                       | 在假设里寻找证明目标                   |\n"
"| §22                       | 在假设中寻找矛盾                           |\n"
"| §23                       | 尝试用算法决定一个命题是否为真 |\n"
"| §24                       | 把证明目标里的“与”拆开                         "
"|\n"
"| §25/§26              | 开始证明目标中“或”的一边             |\n"
"| §27                       | 把假设里的“与”拆开                 |\n"
"| §28                       | 根据某个假设里的“或”做分类讨论  |\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你怎么会知道这些的？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不知道。大概是出厂自带的吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L13_Or
msgid "Intro Logo L13"
msgstr "下一位，请 …."

#. §0: `(«{A}» ∧ «{B}») ∨ «{A}»`
#. §1: `obtain …`
#. §2: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := «{h}»`
#. §3: `obtain h | h := «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L13_Or
msgid ""
"Observe goal as §0.\n"
"Do not try §1 as §2 but as §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你看，要是你用手指碰一下某个假设，它就会高亮显示里面的括号结构。离"
"谱….\n"
"\n"
"**你**：啊，我懂了，所以是 §0！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我开始觉得这里整件事都有点可疑了：先是目标里来个“且”，然后假设里也来"
"个“且”，接着目标里来个“或”，现在假设里又来个“或”。他们肯定是提前商量好的！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：就让他们玩吧。我们马上就搞定这里，然后飞去一个更有意思的星球。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以，还是用 §1？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，不过这次不是写成 §2，而是写成 §3。"

#. §0: `«{A}» ∧ «{B}»`
#. §1: `«{A}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L13_Or
msgid "Prove goal once for §0 and once for §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在你得分两种情况证明目标：一种是假设左边的 §0 成立，另一种是假设"
"右边的 §1 成立。我们先假设左边 §0 是真的。"

#. §0: `(«{A}» ∧ «{B}») ∨ «{A}»`
#. §1: `«{A}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L13_Or
msgid "Show goal via §0 i.e. assume §1 is true"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在你还得在 §0 的右半边成立的情况下证明目标，也就是假设 §1 成立。"

#. §0: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := «{h}»`
#. §1: `\\<>`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L13_Or
msgid "Try §0. Write brackets as §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：假设里的“且”该怎么处理，你不是已经会了吗：用 §0。提醒一下：尖括号写"
"成 §1。"

#. §0: `∧`
#. §1: `constructor`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L14_Summary
msgid "Approach §0 with §1"
msgstr "**司南**：现在你可以用 §1 来处理目标里的 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L14_Summary
msgid "Conclusion Logo L14"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：太棒了！不过现在赶紧溜吧，免得又排起新队伍！\n"
"\n"
"洛格温女王这会儿已经睡着了，你们就悄悄溜走。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `obtain ⟨⟩ := «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L14_Summary
msgid "Divide assumption §0 using §1"
msgstr "**司南**：会先把假设 §0 用 §1 拆开。"

#. §0: `obtain ⟨⟩ := h`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L14_Summary
msgid "Explain that each sub-goal needs §0"
msgstr "**司南**：这种顺序的缺点是，你现在在每个子目标里都得调用 §0。"

#. §0: `∧`
#. §1: `∨`
#. §2: `obtain ⟨h₁, h₂⟩ := h`
#. §3: `obtain h \\| h := h`
#. §4: `constructor`
#. §5: `left`
#. §6: `right`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L14_Summary
msgid ""
"Intro Logo L14: The most important tactics of this chapter concerning §0 and "
"§1.\n"
"For both logical operations the tactis §2 and §3 can be used respectivelly.\n"
"Analogously, when working with the goal §4 and §5/§6 can be used "
"respectivelly as well."
msgstr ""
"最后一位臣民走上前来。她的诉求比前面的要复杂一点。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：把你学过的都往上招呼就行。来，我还挺好心的，再给你把这种情况下最重"
"要的四个策略展示一遍。\n"
"\n"
"|（概览）    | 与（§0）                 | 或（§1）               |\n"
"|:------------|:-------------------------|:------------------------|\n"
"| 假设        | §2                       | §3                      |\n"
"| 目标        | §4                       | §5/§6                   |\n"
" "

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `obtain`
#: Game.Levels.Logo.L14_Summary
msgid "Split §0 once more with §1"
msgstr "**司南**：我会再用 §1 把 §0 拆一次。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna
msgid "Intro Luna"
msgstr ""
"司南发现了一颗小月球，你们现在正朝它飞去。它的表面非常光滑，但有一处表面有个"
"小开口，一段楼梯通向内部。你们着陆后，好奇地走下去。\n"
"\n"
"到了下面，你发现自己置身于你见过最整洁的公寓里。一个小女孩向你们打招呼。\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：我是 Lina，月球的唯一居民。\n"
"\n"
"然后她看到了司南。\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：嗯嘛，其实我们这里也算两个人……\n"
"\n"
"她转过身喊了句什么，这时一位智能小精灵飞了过来。\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：这是 Ritha！\n"
"\n"
"司南显然觉得她很可爱。\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：不过你们现在别这么乱七八糟地站着啦，拜托！鞋子和头盔放到那边那边，"
"然后请站到标好的访客站位上。不然我这儿又要被你们搞得一团糟了。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna
msgid "Luna"
msgstr "月球"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L01_le_rfl
msgid "Conclusion Luna L01"
msgstr "**Lina**：好吧，这确实是个很平凡的例子。"

#. §0: `n ≤ n`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L01_le_rfl
msgid "Intro Luna L01: Know that §0"
msgstr ""
"你感觉有点被她弄懵了，但还是试着开口回应。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：行，我们会努力不把东西弄乱。要在这里维持秩序很难吗？\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：比如说，你得知道 §0。"

#. §0: `rfl`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L01_le_rfl
msgid "Try using §0 here"
msgstr "**司南**：§0？"

#. §0: `omega`
#. §1: `omega`
#. §2: `omega`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L02_Omega
msgid ""
"Conclusion Luna L02: §0 is popular, even though §1 is quiet useless.\n"
"§2 is only really applicable over integers."
msgstr ""
"Lina 翻了个白眼。\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：Ritha 是 §0 的超级粉丝。可 §1 挺没用的。一旦离开整数，§2 就什么也干"
"不了了。\n"
"\n"
"**Ritha**：你才没用！\n"
"\n"
"Ritha 扮了个鬼脸。"

#. §0: `0 < n`
#. §1: `n < 0`
#. §2: `n ≠ 0`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L02_Omega
msgid "Intro Luna L02: For integers §0 or §1 means §2"
msgstr ""
"**Lina**：另外，比如你得知道，对整数而言，命题 §0 或者 §1 其实就等价于 §2。"

#. §0: `omega`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L02_Omega
msgid "Try out §0"
msgstr "**Ritha** *(低声)*：试试 §0！"

#. §0: `apply lt_trichotomy`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L03_Linarith__lt_trichotomy
msgid "Conclusion Luna L03: Alternatively §0 could have been used."
msgstr "**Lina**：顺便说一句，你们其实也可以直接用 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L03_Linarith__lt_trichotomy
msgid "Intro Luna L03"
msgstr "**Lina**：试试这个呗！"

#. §0: `linarith`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L03_Linarith__lt_trichotomy
msgid "Now try §0!"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那现在呢？？\n"
"\n"
"**Lina** (*得意洋洋*)：§0!"

#. §0: `by_cases h_leq : «{a}» ≤ «{b}»`
#. §1: `by_cases h_lt : «{a}» < «{b}»`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L03_Linarith__lt_trichotomy
msgid "Try §0, §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：分类讨论？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，可以试试。比如先写 §0，然后再写 §1。"

#. §0: `obtain`
#. §1: `x < y`
#. §2: `x = y`
#. §3: `x > y`
#. §4: ```
#. obtain h | h | h := lt_trichotomy x y
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L03_Linarith__lt_trichotomy
msgid ""
"Wird typischerweise mit §0 verwendet, um in einem Beweis die drei Fälle §1, "
"§2 und §3 zu unterscheiden:\n"
"\n"
"§4"
msgstr ""
"通常会和 §0 一起用，用来在证明里区分三种情况 §1、§2 和 §3：\n"
"\n"
"§4"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L04_Omega2
msgid "Conclusion Luna L04"
msgstr "**Lina**：好吧，是我的锅。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L04_Omega2
msgid "Intro Luna L04"
msgstr "**Lina**：这个呢？"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L04_Omega2
msgid "Try omega"
msgstr "Ritha 似乎想用眼神给你们打个什么暗号。"

#. §0: `«{hx}»`
#. §1: `obtain`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L05_Linarith2
msgid "Divide §0 with §1"
msgstr "**司南**：好。这样好多了。然后你还可以用 §1 把 §0 拆成两个部分。"

#. §0: `«{hx}»`
#. §1: `push Not at «{hx}»`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L05_Linarith2
msgid "Increase readability of §0. Try §1"
msgstr "**司南**：现在把假设 §0 整理的更可读一点。也许可以试试 §1？"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L05_Linarith2
msgid "Intro Luna L05"
msgstr "**Lina**：同样的问题，现在换到 ℝ 里！"

#. §0: `«{hx}» : m ≤ x → n < x`
#. §1: `→`
#. §2: `rw`
#. §3: `imp_iff_or_not`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L05_Linarith2
msgid "We now have §0. Knowing what §1 means, try §2 with §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：嗯…… §0 看起来还是不太理想。不过我们知道 §1 是什么意思——试试用 §2 "
"配上 §3！"

#. §0: `omega`
#. §1: `linarith`
#. §2: `linarith`
#. §3: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L05_Linarith2
msgid ""
"§0 and §1 alone don't help here. §2 will need some help. Try to untangle\n"
"the implications via §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**（*对司南*）：这里我用 §0 和 §1 都推不下去。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我觉得你只要稍微帮 §2 一把就行。要不按老办法，用 §3 处理掉这个两个"
"蕴涵先。"

#. §0: `ext`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L06_Icc__Icc_insert_succ_right
msgid "Equality of sets demands §0"
msgstr "**司南**：集合相等需要用 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L06_Icc__Icc_insert_succ_right
msgid "Intro Luna L06"
msgstr "**Ritha**：我也能出一道题吗？给。"

#. §0: `Icc`
#. §1: `Icc a b`
#. §2: $[a, b]$
#. §3: $\\{a, a + 1, \\dots, b\\}$
#. §4: $$ [a, b] ∪ \\{ b + 1 \\} = [a, b + 1] $$
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L06_Icc__Icc_insert_succ_right
msgid ""
"Remind that §0 is an interval which is closed to both sides. You could write "
"§1\n"
"as §2 or §3, because we are in the natual numbers. Therfore, the\n"
"goal is: §4"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0 到底是什么？\n"
"\n"
"**Ritha**：这是闭区间。`I` 代表 interval，也就是“区间”；两个 `c` 代表 "
"closed，也就是左右两端都是闭的。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：因为这里是在自然数里，你可以把 §1 写成 §2，或者写成 §3。要证明的就"
"是：\n"
"\n"
"§4"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L06_Icc__Icc_insert_succ_right
msgid "Ritha gives signs to try omega"
msgstr "Ritha又在朝你们使眼色。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L06_Icc__Icc_insert_succ_right
msgid "Try §0 afterwards"
msgstr "**司南**：然后试试 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L07_Linarith2
msgid "Conclusion Luna L07"
msgstr "**你**：还不错！"

#. §0: $$
#. \\begin{aligned}
#. \\tfrac{35}{11}\\cdot y &\\le -\\tfrac{22}{21}\\cdot x + \\tfrac{35}{2}  \\ %(new line)
#. \\tfrac{8}{9} \\cdot y &\\le x + \\tfrac{17}{8}
#. \\end{aligned}
#. $$
#. §1: $$
#. y ≤ \\tfrac{34}{7}
#. $$
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L07_Linarith2
msgid ""
"Given\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"Show\n"
"§1\n"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我得先自己把它写下来。也就是说，已知：\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"要证明的是：\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"司南？？\n"
"\n"
"Lina 咧嘴一笑。\n"

#. §0: `omega`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L07_Linarith2
msgid "Intro Luna L07: Enough of §0"
msgstr "**Lina**：§0 用够了，现在轮到我了。"

#. §0: `simp at «{h'}»`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L08_Omega3
msgid "Definitely use §0"
msgstr "**Ritha**：一定要试试 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L08_Omega3
msgid "Intro Luna L08"
msgstr "**Ritha**：现在又轮到我啦！"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L09_lt_trichotomy2
msgid "Conclusion Luna L09"
msgstr ""
"**Lina**：你们做得很好！可惜，你们要继续你们的旅途了。不过要是你们再多待一会"
"儿，就会把我们的作息彻底打乱了。"

#: Game.Levels.Luna.L09_lt_trichotomy2
msgid "Intro Luna L09"
msgstr "**Lina**：现在又轮到我了。"

#. §0: `b`
#. §1: `use …`
#. §2: `lt_trichotomy`
#. §3: ```
#. obtain h | h | h := lt_trichotomy a c
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L09_lt_trichotomy2
msgid ""
"It is clear which §0 can be used. Start with §1 and continue with §2 e.g.\n"
"§3\n"
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，其实这里该用哪个 §0 已经很明显了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：既然你这么清楚，那就先从 §1 开始吧。\n"
"然后你需要用 §2。比如这样：\n"
"§3\n"

#. §0: `omega`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L10_Icc_subset_Icc_iff
msgid "Intro Luna L10: Use §0 again"
msgstr ""
"**Ritha**（*对Lina*）：拜托，也让我再问一个问题嘛……\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：好吧，就一个……但别又是 §0！\n"
"\n"
"Ritha睁大眼睛，可怜巴巴地看着Lina。\n"
"\n"
"**Lina**：如果你*非得*问的话。那就快点！我们现在真的没时间了！"

#. §0: `subset_iff`
#. §1: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L10_Icc_subset_Icc_iff
msgid "Try using §0 and if nothing else helps, §1"
msgstr "**司南**：也许这里又该用一下 §0。要是实在不行，就试试 §1。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `«{h}»`
#. §2: `a₁ ≤ b₁`
#. §3: `a₁ ≤ a₁`
#. §4: `a₁ ≤ a₁`
#. §5: `have`
#: Game.Levels.Luna.L10_Icc_subset_Icc_iff
msgid ""
"Use assumption §0. E.g. apply §1 onto §2 or §3.\n"
"Formulate §4 using §5"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你肯定得想办法用上假设 §0。比如你可以把 §1 用到不等式 §2 上，或者用"
"到 §3 上！（不等式 §4 最好用 §5 先写出来。）"

#: Game.Levels.Mono
msgid "Intro Mono"
msgstr ""
"在下一个星球上，又有两栋高楼并排而立。还是一栋又窄又高，另一栋稍微宽些、矮"
"些。它们又被一套管道系统连在一起——看来也又有某种运输舱系统。有了在满射上的经"
"验，你们这次径直朝较矮的那栋楼飞去，并降落在屋顶上。\n"
"\n"
"**门卫**：别别别。你们没看到大家都在挥手吗？这里不过是我们的宿舍楼。我们白天"
"都在那边的办公楼里。不过好吧，现在你们既然来了。先欢迎一下！\n"
"\n"
"你们每个人都和他的四只手之一握了握。\n"
"\n"
"**门卫**：这样我倒正好可以给你们介绍一下我们独一无二的市内交通系统。你们是从"
"满射来的，对吧？那地方的事故可多了。隔三岔五就出事故。他们就是理不顺自己的管"
"道。我们可是好多年零事故！\n"
"\n"
"你们往下走了四层楼。到了那里，又给每个人分配了一个运输舱，然后你们无声地向上"
"滑进办公塔。驱动是怎么工作的，依然是个谜。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：哦。这里也没人啊！\n"
"\n"
"**门卫**：当然没人。他们都在最上面。而且不是每一层都能通过管道到达。不过我们"
"快到了。再上两段楼梯就行。"

#: Game.Levels.Mono
msgid "Mono"
msgstr "单射"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L01_Injective
msgid "Conclusion Mono L01"
msgstr "形式哲学家们觉得你们干得不错。"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L01_Injective
msgid "Intro Mono L01"
msgstr ""
"在最上面，果然又聚着一大群形式哲学家。\n"
"他们热情地欢迎你们，然后立刻切入正题。"

#. §0: `intro a b`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L01_Injective
msgid "Try starting with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：先从 §0 开始吧。"

#. §0: `«{f}»`
#. §1: `«{ha}»`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L01_Injective
msgid "Use §0 to simplify assumption §1"
msgstr "**司南**：我觉得你现在应该用 §0 的定义把假设 §1 简化一下。"

#. §0: `Injective`
#. §1: `∀ {a b : U}, f a = f b → a = b`
#. §2: `unfold`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L01_Injective
msgid "§0 is defined as §1. You can check this with §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：§0 的定义跟你想的一样：§1。你要是不信我，也可以用 §2 快速检查一下。"

#. §0: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L02_InjectiveNeIff
msgid "Perhaps, try using §0 here"
msgstr "**司南**：§0?"

#. §0: `Injective f`
#. §1: `a ≠ b → f a ≠ f b`
#. §2: `Injective.ne_iff`
#. §3: `f a ≠ f b ↔ a ≠ b`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L02_InjectiveNeIff
msgid ""
"Use short cut by instead of the definition of §0 using equivalent "
"description\n"
"§1. In Leanic it is part of §2. For injective mapping it holds\n"
"that §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这里你可以走个捷径：不用 §0 的定义，而是用单射性的等价描述 §1。在"
"Lean语里这是 §2 的一部分：对单射映射有 §3。"

#. §0: `Injective`
#. §1: `unfold`
#. §2: `¬ ∀`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L03_NotInjective
msgid "Open §0 via §1 to see §2 ..."
msgstr "**司南**：也许你可以用 §1 把 §0 展开。这样就会得到 §2……"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L03_NotInjective
msgid "Provide a counter example"
msgstr ""
"**你**：现在我只要给出一个反例就行了，对吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错！你想用哪两个数呢？"

#. §0: `push Not`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L03_NotInjective
msgid "Remind yourself of §0"
msgstr "**司南**：你还记得 §0 吗？"

#. §0: $$
#. f(n) = \\begin{cases}
#. n^2 & \\text{falls } n \\text{ gerade} \\ %(new line)
#. n+1 & \\text{andernfalls.}
#. \\end{cases}
#. $$
#. §1: `f + f`
#. §2: `ℕ → ℕ`
#. §3: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L03_NotInjective
msgid ""
"The given mapping has the form\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"and §1 is the mapping §2, that for each input return the doubeled value of "
"§3.\n"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以，给定的映射是这样的：\n"
"§0\n"
"那 §1 是什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那是映射 §2，它在每个位置取 §3 的两倍。\n"

#. §0: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L03_NotInjective
msgid "§0 might suffice"
msgstr "**司南**：这里都这么具体，也许直接用 §0 就够了。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `Fin (n + 1)`
#. §2: `congr_fun`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L04_Diagonal
msgid "Evaluate mappings in §0 on element from §1. §2 could help"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你可以把 §0 里的映射拿到 §1 的某个元素上取值。也许 §2 能以某种形式"
"帮上忙？"

#. §0: `diag`
#. §1: `A → (Fin (n + 1) → A)`
#. §2: `diag`
#. §3: `A`
#. §4: `Fin (n + 1) → A`
#. §5: `Fin (n+1)`
#. §6: $\\{0,1,…,n\\}$
#. §7: `Fin (n + 1) → A`
#. §8: $\\{0,1,…,n\\}$
#. §9: $A$
#. §10: $(n+1)$
#. §11: $A$
#. §12: `diag`
#. §13: $A$
#. §14: $A^{n+1}$
#. §15: `diag`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L04_Diagonal
msgid ""
"Explain §0: in the definition add brackets so it's §1. So, §2\n"
"is a mapping from §3 to §4. §5 is the set §6 and therfore,\n"
"§7 is the set of mappings from §8 to §9. Hence, such a mapping can be seen\n"
"as a §10-tuple of elements in §11. So, §12 is given as a mapping from §13 to "
"§14.\n"
"Name §15 should be clear now"
msgstr ""
"**你**：在 §0 的定义里又出现了两个箭头连在一起。我得先在脑子里理一理。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：先照例加上括号：§1。也就是说，§2 是一个从 §3 到集合 §4 的映射。现"
"在 §5 是集合 §6，所以 §7 就是从 §8 到 §9 的映射所组成的集合。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：嗯……这种映射其实不过就是一个由 §11 里的元素组成的 §10-元组，对吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也可以这么看。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：好。给定的是一个映射 §12，从 §13 到 §14。而且这个映射……啊，我懂它为什"
"么叫 §15 了。"

#. §0: `unfold Injective`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L04_Diagonal
msgid "If unsure start with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：要是你完全不知道怎么继续，最好先从 §0 开始。"

#. §0: `diag «{a₁}»`
#. §1: `diag «{a₂}»`
#. §2: `Fin (n + 1) → A`
#. §3: `Fin (n + 1)`
#. §4: `congr_fun`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L04_Diagonal
msgid ""
"Remind that 'tuples' §0 and §1 are two mappings §2.\n"
"Evaluate them on elements from §3. Try §4"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：记住，你的“元组” §0 和 §1 其实是两个映射 §2。你可以取一个 §3 中的元"
"素，把这两个映射都代入它。也许 §4 能够帮到你？"

#. §0: `diag`
#. §1: $a$
#. §2: $i \\in \\{0,1,…,n\\}$
#. §3: $a$
#. §4: $a ↦ (a,…,a)$
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L04_Diagonal
msgid ""
"To be more precise: §0 sends an §1 onto the mapping, which maps each index "
"§2 onto §3.\n"
"In the former intepretation this is the mapping §4."
msgstr ""
"**你**：或者也许不是。你能把这个再拆开讲讲吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：映射 §0 会把一个元素 §1 按照如下映射处理：它把*每个*索引 §2 都映到 "
"§3。按照你的理解，这其实就是映射 §4。"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid "The next part is elementary"
msgstr "**你**：哈！那这一部分现在大概又会变得很基础了。"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid "Try again from the beginning"
msgstr "**司南**：我觉得这条路太绕了。还是从头再来一遍吧！"

#. §0: `unfold`
#. §1: `StrictMono`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid "Use §0 to look into definition of §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：或者……？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对对。你用 §0 去看看 §1 的定义。"

#. §0: `n`
#. §1: `x ↦ x^n`
#. §2: `h_odd : Odd n`
#. §3: `Odd.strictMono_pow h_odd`
#. §4: `h_odd.strictMono_pow`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid ""
"[Doc.Theorem] Odd.strictMono_pow\n"
"for odd §0, §1 is strictly monotonous\n"
"given §2, can write §3 as §4"
msgstr ""
"当 §0 是奇数时，§1 是严格单调的。\n"
"\n"
"如果你已经有假设 §2，那么你也可以不写 §3，而是直接写 §4。"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `g`
#. §2: `f + g`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid ""
"[Doc.Theorem] StrictMono.add\n"
"if §0 and §1 strictly monotonous, then also §2 strictly monotonous"
msgstr "如果 §0 和 §1 都严格单调，那么 §2 也严格单调。"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid "[Doc.Theorem] StrictMono.injective"
msgstr "每个严格单调的映射（在合适的定义域和值域之间）都是单射。"

#. §0: `Odd 3`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid "§0 is trivial"
msgstr "**你**：§0。这不是显然的吗？等等！"

#. §0: `StrictMono`
#. §1: `StrictMono.injective`
#. §2: `StrictMono.add`
#. §3: `Odd.strictMono_pow`
#. §4: `n`
#. §5: `x ↦ x ^ n`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid ""
"§0 is useful. §1 says that each strictly monotone mapping\n"
"is injective. To show that a mapping is monotone one can use e.g. §2 or §3,\n"
"which says that for uneven §4, §5 is monotone."
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，这个有点更难了……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我现在也没什么好主意。\n"
"\n"
"这时你们听到人群里有人小声嘀咕：§0……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：啊，对。这里有个引理 §1：每个严格单调的映射都是单射。还有一大堆引理"
"可以用来证明映射是单调的。比如：\n"
"\n"
"§2 – 两个严格单调映射的和仍然严格单调\n"
"\n"
"§3 – 对于奇数 §4，§5 是严格单调的\n"
"\n"
"要不要用这个试试看？"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L05_StrictMono
msgid "§0 is what is looked for"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 就是你要找的。"

#. §0: `StrictMono.injective`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L06_StrictMono
msgid "Intro Mono L06: Prove §0"
msgstr ""
"看起来有人注意到 §0 是刚才在提示中给出的。\n"
"现在他们也想看看它的证明。"

#. §0: `Injective f`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L06_StrictMono
msgid "Introduce all varaibles and assumptions from §0"
msgstr "**司南**：要不先按经典套路，把 §0 里的所有变量和假设都引入一下？"

#. §0: `lt_trichotomy`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L06_StrictMono
msgid "Try case distinction. Use §0"
msgstr "**司南**：现在也许要做个分类讨论。你还记得 §0 吗？"

#. §0: `0 - 1`
#. §1: `0`
#. §2: `n ↦ n - 1`
#. §3: `n ↦ n - 1`
#. §4: `0`
#. §5: `0`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L07_SuccHasLeftInv
msgid ""
"Conclusion Mono L07: Explain that here §0 is §1, as there is mapping §2 "
"defined only on natural numbers.\n"
"In Lean §3 is such a mapping and there for it maps §4 onto §5."
msgstr ""
"**你**：我还是震惊。我以为我们在做数学。为什么 §0 又会是 §1？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：纯粹是怎么看的问题。你把 §2 想成一个只在正自然数上定义的映射。在"
"Lean语里，§3 就是一个在所有自然数上定义的映射，它把 §4 送到 §5。有什么不行"
"呢？反正最后我们也只会把这个映射用在正数上，而在正数上，你的理解幸好和Lean语"
"里的理解是一致的。"

#. §0: `n ↦ n + 1`
#. §1: `n ↦ n - 1`
#. §2: `n = 0`
#. §3: `if … then … else`
#. §4: `0 - 1`
#. §5: `ℕ`
#. §6: `0`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L07_SuccHasLeftInv
msgid ""
"It conjected that §0 has left inverse. One would assume that §1 would\n"
"not work for §2. Tackling this by case distinction e.g. §3 is unecessary as\n"
"in Leanic §4 is in §5. It is simply defined as §6"
msgstr ""
"**你**：看起来是在断言，映射 §0 有一个左逆。那我就直接给出映射 §1……只不过对 "
"§2 来说不成立。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你可以用 §3 做个分类讨论。不过其实你根本不需要。在Lean语 里，§4 也"
"属于 §5。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：什么……??!\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。简单起见，它被定义成 §6。"

#. §0: `n ↦ n - 1`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L07_SuccHasLeftInv
msgid "[Hint wdpf] Try §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：看起来不错。但相信我，这个分类讨论完全没必要。你也可以直接用 §0。试"
"试看！"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `g`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L08_RightInvOfLeftInv
msgid ""
"Explain goal: An injective mapping §0 which is left inverse to mapping §1, "
"is to the same mapping also right inverse"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这里写的是什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：一个单射映射 §0，如果它是某个映射 §1 的左逆，那么它也是那个映射的右"
"逆。"

# GPT: „durch“ kann „fertig“ oder „hindurch“ bedeuten; hier im Sinn von „fertig sein“ übersetzt.
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L09_InjOfHasLeftInv
msgid "Conclusion Mono L09"
msgstr "**司南**：干得好！我觉得我们在这儿很快就能搞定了……"

# GPT: „Linksinverses“ könnte man auch als „linksseitiges Inverses“/„Links-Inverse“ formulieren; ich habe es als „左逆“ übersetzt (üblich in der Mathematik).
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L09_InjOfHasLeftInv
msgid "Explain that a mapping, which is left inverse ..."
msgstr "**你**：一个拥有左逆的映射是单射。我觉得好像听过……"

#. §0: `congr_arg g`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L09_InjOfHasLeftInv
msgid "Try using §0"
msgstr "**司南**：也许可以试试和 §0 有关的方法？"

#. §0: `a`
#. §1: `a`
#. §2: ```
#. ∀ b : B, ∃ a : A,
#. ( f a = b   ∨   ¬ ∃ a' : A , f a' = b )
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L10_Auxiliary
msgid ""
"Be careful with interpreting goal as 'there is §0 or there is no §1'. "
"Rewrite goal as §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我们现在回到量词了吗？总之：要么有一个 §0，要么没有任何 §1，这看起来"
"像个永真式。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：慢点！你得注意隐含的括号。我给你把括号写得更明确一点：\n"
"§2"

#. §0: `«{A}»`
#. §1: `obtain`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L10_Auxiliary
msgid "Known that there exists some element in §0. Try §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你至少知道，§0 里存在*某个*元素。也许你可以用 §1 把它“构造”出来。"

#. §0: `by_cases`
#. §1: `«{b}»`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L10_Auxiliary
msgid "Try §0 to see if §1 has preimage"
msgstr "**司南**：嗯，你可以用 §0 做个分类讨论，看看 §1 到底有没有原像。"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L11_InjHasLeftInv
msgid "Conclusion Mono L11"
msgstr ""
"你们又赢得了一阵热烈的掌声，并被送别。\n"
"回程仍然没有运输舱。\n"
"不过好在另一栋楼也没那么远。"

#. §0: `Nonempty A`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L11_InjHasLeftInv
msgid "Intorduce new prerequisite §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我懂了。满射哲学家想证明：一个映射当且仅当它有一个右逆时是满射。而这"
"边的单射哲学家想证明：一个映射当且仅当它有一个左逆时是单射。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，不过他们还需要这个额外的前提 §0。"

#. §0: ` ∀ b : B, ∃ a : A, …`
#. §1: `choose`
#. §2: `have`
#: Game.Levels.Mono.L11_InjHasLeftInv
msgid ""
"One could choose left inverse on the previous proven statement §0 by using "
"§1.\n"
"As proven statement has no name formulate statement again with §2 and prove "
"it again."
msgstr ""
"**你**：我看不出来，怎么才能具体构造出一个左逆。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：还记得我们刚刚证明过的那个陈述吗：§0。如果手里有这个陈述，你大概就"
"可以用 §1 选出你要找的左逆。可惜。这个陈述没有名字。也许你可以用 §2 再把它重"
"新写出来，然后在这里再证明一遍。"

#: Game.Levels.Mono.L11_InjHasLeftInv
msgid "Remember proof"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这个我们不是也已经证明过了吗……只是我忘了保存。你还记得那个证明吗？"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza
msgid "Intro Piazza"
msgstr ""
"看起来，你们降落在了一颗贸易星球上。到处都是商贩在叫卖他们的货物。你们好奇地"
"打量着几个摊位。有些东西看起来很眼熟、似乎也能吃；很多则不能吃。但所有东西都"
"被分门别类地整理得整整齐齐。有装蓝莓（？）的篮子，有装红色植物的箱子——让你们"
"想起番茄——还有敞口的麻袋，里面是一些小小的粉色星星，等等。\n"
"\n"
"几个孩子——或者说，几个个头很小的形式哲学家，他们的行为就像孩子——差点从你们脚"
"边冲过去。司南往后一跳，这时他们注意到了你们，便停了下来。他们自我介绍说自己"
"叫“Fin”“Ext”“Mem”“Set”和“Sub”，看起来很好奇。\n"
"\n"
"**Fin**：你们在这儿干什么？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：呃……我们只是想随便逛逛。\n"
"\n"
"**Set**：我们在这儿学点集合论。我们的父母把我们丢在这儿了。\n"
"\n"
"**Ext**：算是为了学习吧。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那，你们已经学到什么了吗？"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza
msgid "Piazza"
msgstr "广场"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L01_Mem__Set
msgid "Conclusion Piazza L01"
msgstr ""
"**Set**： 所以你们也已经对集合有点了解了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**： 嗯，*一点点* 吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L01_Mem__Set
msgid "Intro Piazza L01"
msgstr "**Fin**： 嗯，当然。 比如这个。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L01_Mem__Set
msgid "Try tauto"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我理解得没错吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我想是吧。看起来是个重言式，不是吗？试试 *tauto*。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L02_Simp
msgid "Intro Piazza L02"
msgstr "**Mem**： 要不试试这个？"

#. §0: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L02_Simp
msgid "Remember to use §0 here"
msgstr "**司南**：还记得 §0 吗？"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L02_Simp
msgid "The simplest method here is §0"
msgstr "**司南**： 我觉得这里最简单的方法是用 §0。"

#. §0: `simp`
#. §1: `simp`
#. §2: `simp`
#. §3: ```
#. «{x}» ∈ «{A}» ∩ «{B}» ↔ «{x}» ∈ «{A}» ∧ «{x}» ∈ «{B}»
#. ```
#. §4: ```
#. «{x}» ∈ «{B}» ∪ «{C}» ↔ «{x}» ∈ «{B}» ∨ «{x}» ∈ «{C}».
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L03_Ext__Set__Union__Inter
msgid ""
"Explain §0: §1 looks for known equations and equivalences which would be "
"currently\n"
"applicable. §2 uses all simplifications it can find. Currently the following "
"simplifications\n"
"were performed:\n"
"§3\n"
"and\n"
"§4\n"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0 到底具体是干什么的？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1 会去找当前适用的常见等式和等价命题——把它们当作化简规则。§2 会应"
"用它找到的所有化简规则。刚才应用的化简就包括：\n"
"§3\n"
"以及\n"
"§4\n"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L03_Ext__Set__Union__Inter
msgid "Intro Piazza L03"
msgstr "**Set**： 如果刚才那题太简单了——你们熟悉这个命题吗？"

#. §0: `tauto`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L03_Ext__Set__Union__Inter
msgid "The rest can be dealt with §0"
msgstr "**司南**： 剩下的交给 §0 就行。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L03_Ext__Set__Union__Inter
msgid "Use §0 again"
msgstr "**司南**：然后再用一次 §0。"

#. §0: `A B C : Set ℕ`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `B`
#. §3: `C`
#. §4: `ℕ`
#. §5: `Set`
#. §6: `ext x`
#. §7: `A = B`
#. §8: `x ∈ A ↔ x ∈ B`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L03_Ext__Set__Union__Inter
msgid ""
"§0 means that §1, §2 and §3 are subsets of §4. Therefore, §5\n"
"can be interpreted as 'subset'. Use §6 to replace a set equation §7 with §8"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0在这里到底是啥意思？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：就是说§1、§2和§3都是§4的*子集*。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：§5 的意思是“subset”？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你要这么理解，也行。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我大概*知道*这个命题。但完全不知道在这儿该怎么证。\n"
"\n"
"**Ext**：我可以告诉你！有个魔法词，就跟我名字一模一样！！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对了——§6会把集合等式 §7 替换成等价命题 §8。"

#. §0: `univ`
#. §1: `univ`
#. §2: `ℕ`
#. §3: `univ : Set ℕ`
#. §4: `ℕ`
#. §5: `5 : ℕ`
#. §6: `univ : Set ℕ`
#. §7: `5`
#. §8: `5 ∈ univ`
#. §9: `rw [eq_univ_iff_forall]`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L04_Generalize__univ__eq_univ_iff_forall
msgid ""
"Explain §0: §1 is interpreted as §2 but as a subset of it self i.e. §3\n"
"is subset of §4. So, as 5 is a natural number (§5) and it holds that §6, §7\n"
"is also in this set i.e. §8. Try §9"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那 §0 是什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1 是最大的子集：所有自然数。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以就是 §2？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也算，但又不完全是。§3 是“整个 ℕ”，但要把它理解成 §4 的一个*子集"
"*。\n"
"\n"
"Ext、Fin、Set、Sub 和 Mem 都瞪大眼看着你们。\n"
"\n"
"**Set**：这怎么可能搞混嘛！这里*是*一颗*蓝莓*，而它*在*这个*装着所有蓝莓的篮"
"子*里。当然它不可能“在蓝莓里”。\n"
"\n"
"孩子们笑了。\n"
"\n"
"**Mem**：同样地，5 *是*一个自然数（§5），而它属于*所有自然数的集合 §6*"
"（§8）。这有什么好困惑的？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**（*对你*）：别为这个纠结了。我建议你先从 §9 开始，这样你就能清楚看到"
"到底在问什么。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L04_Generalize__univ__eq_univ_iff_forall
msgid "Intro Piazza L04"
msgstr "**Sub**：我也学到点东西："

#. §0: `by_cases h : Even «{n}»`
#. §1: `not_odd_iff_even`
#. §2: `not_even_iff_odd`
#. §3: `¬Odd ««{n}»» ∨ Odd ««{n}»»`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L04_Generalize__univ__eq_univ_iff_forall
msgid ""
"One option: §0.\n"
"But in any case, will need §1\n"
"(or §2) at some point,\n"
"so might as well start with it\n"
"and obtain tautology §3."
msgstr ""
"**你**：那现在用 §0 进行分类讨论？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，那样也能完成目标。\n"
"不过不管怎样，你迟早大概都得用 §1（或者 §2）。  \n"
"不如直接从它开始，这样目标就会变成重言式 §3。"

#. §0: `simp`
#. §1: `simp [eq_univ_iff_forall]`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L04_Generalize__univ__eq_univ_iff_forall
msgid "Try via §0 or directly §1"
msgstr "**司南**：现在用 §0。实际上你可以直接用 §1。"

#. §0: `tauto`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L04_Generalize__univ__eq_univ_iff_forall
msgid "[Piazza] §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以现在直接用 §0？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：试试！"

#. §0: `∅`
#. §1: `rw [eq_empty_iff_forall_notMem]`
#. §2: `simp [eq_empty_iff_forall_notMem]`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L05_empty__eq_empty_iff_forall_notMem
msgid ""
"Having §0 you could either start with §1 or\n"
"§2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：不，§0 我认识。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：为了确认它确实和你理解的一样，你可以在这里从 §1 开始。或者如果你想"
"快点搞定，也可以用 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L05_empty__eq_empty_iff_forall_notMem
msgid "Intro Piazza L05"
msgstr "**Mem**：你们不会也觉得这个命题很让人困惑吗？"

#. §0: `ext`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L06_Ext2__univ2
msgid "Conclusion Piazza L06: Explain that §0 means extensionality"
msgstr ""
"**你** *(对司南)*：ext为什么叫ext啊？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我哪知道那小子名字怎么来的？？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：不，我是说这里这个 §0！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：哦。逻辑学家把“两个集合当且仅当拥有同样的元素时相等”这个原则叫做*外"
"延性*（extensionality）。形式哲学家大概觉得太长了，就把它缩写成了*ext*。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L06_Ext2__univ2
msgid "Intro Piazza L06"
msgstr "**Ext**：我喜欢*这个*等式。"

#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L06_Ext2__univ2
msgid "Perform §0 again"
msgstr "**司南**：现在当然还是用 §0。"

#. §0: `ext`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L06_Ext2__univ2
msgid "[Hint cqvs] Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：这次你直接再用一次 §0 就行。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L07_antisymm_iff
msgid "Intro Piazza L07"
msgstr "**Set**：我也喜欢这个等价。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L07_antisymm_iff
msgid "Reminder of set equality"
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，我觉得我以前就是这么学的——两个集合相等，当且仅当它们互相包含。"

#. §0: `constructor`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L07_antisymm_iff
msgid "Start here by trying §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我也说不准，但我会从 §0 开始。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L07_antisymm_iff
msgid "Try ext, tauto"
msgstr "**司南**：从这里开始，应该又能套用刚才那个套路了。"

#. §0: `«{A}»`
#. §1: `«{B}»`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L07_antisymm_iff
msgid "Try replacing §0 by §1"
msgstr "**司南**：把 §0 换成 §1。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L08_subset_iff
msgid "Intro Piazza L08"
msgstr "**Sub**：你说得对。我们应该再多考考这些访客对包含关系的理解。"

#. §0: `tauto`
#. §1: `rfl`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L08_subset_iff
msgid "Try §0 or directly §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这不就是定义嘛！\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(对你说)*：试试 §0 吧。或者干脆 §1。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L09_subset_iff2
msgid "Intro Piazza L09"
msgstr "**Sub**：哦，是吗。就一个定义！那要是接下来让你们处理这种包含关系呢？"

#. §0: `ext`
#. §1: `intro a`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `C`
#. §4: `rw [subset_iff] at *`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L09_subset_iff2
msgid ""
"Using §0 would be too complicated. It is simpler to use §1 to introduce\n"
"an arbitrary element from §2 and show that it is also in §3. Firstly, write "
"all inclusions\n"
"exolicitly with §4"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我能不能在这里也用 §0 来论证？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不，有更简单的办法。先用 §1 从 §2 里随便取一个元素，然后证明它在 "
"§3 里。\n"
"\n"
"不过也许你还是先用 §4 把所有包含关系都展开写一遍，这样你就能看出来发生了什"
"么。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L10
msgid "Conclusion Piazza L10"
msgstr "**Mem**：哇塞，你们学得也太快了吧！"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L10
msgid "Intro Piazza L10"
msgstr "**Mem**：也让我再问一个问题！"

#. §0: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L10
msgid "Start with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我会再从 §0 开始。"

#. §0: `intro`
#. §1: `SECOND`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L10
msgid "Try §0 again §1"
msgstr "**司南**：再来一个 §0！"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L11_erase
msgid "Intro Piazza L11"
msgstr ""
"**Mem**：喂，Fin，你在干什么呢？\n"
"\n"
"Fin是这群人里最小的，到现在一句话都没说。可现在，他显然刚从旁边的摊位顺了一颗"
"开心果。\n"
"\n"
"**Fin**：不就是个小练习嘛。\n"
"\n"
"**Mem**：什么练习？\n"
"\n"
"Fin是这么解释的。"

#. §0: `Finset`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `a`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `a`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L11_erase
msgid ""
"§0 here means that §1 belongs to the finite subsets of ℕ.\n"
"Left it states §2 without §3 and on the right it also says §4 without §5"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那这里的 §0 到底是什么意思？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这表示 §1 是 ℕ 的*有限*子集。不过对这个问题其实没区别。左边是没有 "
"§3 的 §2，右边也是没有 §5 的 §4。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L12_insert
msgid "Intro Piazza L12"
msgstr "**Fin**：没错。然后我把我的开心果再放回去。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L13_insert_erase
msgid "Conclusion Piazza L13"
msgstr ""
"孩子们笑了起来，围着你们俩站成一圈，用一种你们都听不懂的语言唱起歌来。然后他"
"们跑开了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我觉得我们可以继续我们的旅途了。"

#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L13_insert_erase
msgid "Intro Piazza L13"
msgstr "**Fin**：那么，你们觉得——现在所有开心果都回家了吗？"

#. §0: `«{b}» = a`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L13_insert_erase
msgid "Try proof by cases, if §0"
msgstr "**Fin**：做个分类讨论，看 §0 成不成立。"

#. §0: `constructor`
#: Game.Levels.Piazza.L13_insert_erase
msgid "[Piazza.L13] Hint 1: You can begin with §0"
msgstr "**Fin**：嗯，可以这么搞。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado
msgid "Intro Prado"
msgstr ""
"你们降落在一颗冰冻星球上，就在一座冰宫旁边。你感觉自己好像以前见过这座宫殿，"
"但怎么也想不起来是在哪里见过的。\n"
"\n"
"在入口处，一个长得像企鹅的生物迎接了你们。\n"
"\n"
"**吉诺**：欢迎来到普拉多！\n"
"我可太高兴你们来了。你们是第一批访客！\n"
"不过嘛，我们也才刚开馆。\n"
"快进来，快进来！\n"
"你们就是大家都在说的那些地球人，对吧？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：呃，是的。那你是……？\n"
"\n"
"**吉诺**：我是吉诺，普拉多的馆长——PRime ADOration Museum（也就是素数崇拜博物"
"馆）！来来来！\n"
"\n"
"吉诺带你们走上入口的台阶，穿过大门进入一座巨大的大厅。大厅中央漂浮着一个小小"
"的底座，上面放着两颗弹珠。\n"
"\n"
"**吉诺**：看，看！我们的第一件展品！素数——二！\n"
"\n"
"你们俩都有点懵。吉诺挑了挑眉。\n"
"\n"
"**吉诺**：你们应该知道怎么证明它是素数吧？"

#: Game.Levels.Prado
msgid "Prado"
msgstr "普拉多"

#. §0: `2`
#. §1: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L01_prime_two
msgid ""
"Because §0 is a concrete data and there is a algorithm to decide if a number "
"is prime you can use §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南** *(低声)*：这太简单了。因为 §0 是一个具体的数，而且有算法能判定一个数"
"是不是素数，你就直接用 §1 就行！"

#. §0: `2`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L01_prime_two
msgid "Conclusion Prado L01: Present §0 as prime number"
msgstr ""
"**你**：的确。我们知道。那你们还有什么展品？\n"
"\n"
"吉诺显得有些尴尬。\n"
"\n"
"**吉诺**：嗯，正如我刚才所说，我们才刚开馆。我们决定先只展出最最漂亮的素数："
"偶数。现在§0是我们唯一的展品。不过我们正加班加点，想为我们的常设展再找到更多"
"偶素数。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L01_prime_two
msgid "Intro Prado L01"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：对对。我们知道。\n"
"\n"
"他飞快地把这个陈述用Lean语写出来，递到你面前。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L02_dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left
msgid "Conclusion Prado L02"
msgstr ""
"**吉诺**：你们在那儿嘀咕什么呢？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：啊，没什么。司南只是想提醒我，素数到底是什么。\n"
"\n"
"吉诺看了看你们的证明。\n"
"\n"
"**吉诺**：不错，不错。不过我们还是再往前走一点吧。博物馆虽然还空着，但已经完"
"工了。而且真的做得很棒。来，看这边！"

#. §0: `obtain`
#. §1: `use`
#. §2: `obtain ⟨x ,hx⟩ := _`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L02_dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left
msgid "Continue with §0 and §1. Fristly diect assumptions with §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那我现在继续用 §0 和 §1 来做证明？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。接下来用 §2 之类的写法把假设拆开。"

#. §0: `2`
#. §1: `a`
#. §2: `b`
#. §3: `a`
#. §4: `b`
#. §5: `a ∣ b`
#. §6: `\\|`
#. §7: `\\dvd`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L02_dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left
msgid ""
"Intro Prado L02: Prove that §0 is only even prime by using the expression "
"„§1 divides §2“.\n"
"„§3 divides §4“ is written as §5, where the vertical bar can be either "
"written as §6 or §7"
msgstr ""
"**你** *(低声)*：司南，你觉得我们该告诉他吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：说 §0 是唯一的偶素数？只要我们不给他拿出证明，他是不会相信的。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那你不觉得我们能证明给他看吗？你不是懂这门语言嘛。我们试试。比如"
"说，“§1 整除 §2”我该怎么写？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：行吧。那“§3 整除 §4”你写成 §5，其中那根竖线你得写成 §6 或者 §7。先"
"试试这里这道问题。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L02_dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left
msgid "Rewrite so you can use §0"
msgstr "**司南**：稍微改写一下，肯定就能用上 §0。"

#. §0: `use _`
#. §1: `«{b}» + «{c}» = «{a}» * _`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L02_dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left
msgid "Try §0 such that §1"
msgstr "**司南**：现在你只需要给出一个合适的值。试试 §0，使得 §1 成立。"

#. §0: `a ∣ b`
#. §1: `∃ k, b = a * k`
#. §2: `∣`
#. §3: `\\dvd`
#. §4: `|`
#. §5: `obtain h₁ | h₂ := h`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L02_dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left
msgid ""
"§0 bedeutet §1.\n"
"\n"
"**Warnung**: Die Symbole §2 (§3) und §4 (ASCII vertikaler Strich) sind zwei "
"unterschiedliche\n"
"Zeichen! Das erste wird ausschließlich für „teilt“ verwendet, das andere "
"kommt zum Beispiel in der\n"
"Syntax §5 vor."
msgstr ""
"§0 表示 §1。\n"
"\n"
"**警告**：符号 §2（§3）和 §4（ASCII 竖线）是两个不同的字符！第一个只用于表示"
"“整除”，另一个比如会出现在语法 §5 里。"

#. §0: `a ∣ b`
#. §1: `∃ k, b = a * k`
#. §2: ```
#. rw [dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left] at *
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L02_dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left
msgid ""
"§0 is defined as §1. State is explicitly with\n"
"§2\n"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：§0 当然被定义为 §1。最好一开始你就把它们全都明确展开：\n"
"§2\n"

#. §0: `rw [dvd_iff_exists_eq_mul_left]`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L03_even_iff_two_dvd
msgid "Begin with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：要不再从 §0 开始？"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L03_even_iff_two_dvd
msgid "Intro Prado L03"
msgstr "你们跟着吉诺参观博物馆时，司南又给了你出了几道题。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L04_99
msgid "Intro Prado L04"
msgstr ""
"吉诺这会儿似乎有些不悦，因为你们压根没把注意力放在他超棒的博物馆上。\n"
"他觉得自己被无视了。\n"
"为了吸引你们的注意，他给了你们下面这个问题。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L05_not_dvd_of_lt_of_lt_mul_succ
msgid "Intro Prado L05"
msgstr ""
"**你** *(对司南)*：来点更有意思的问题！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这个怎么样？"

#. §0: `by_contra`
#. §1: `lt_of_mul_lt_mul_left`
#. §2: `a b c : ℕ`
#. §3: `a * b < a * c`
#. §4: `b < c`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L05_not_dvd_of_lt_of_lt_mul_succ
msgid ""
"Use §0 and the lemma §1.\n"
"For the latter, given §2 it concludes from the assumption §3 that §4"
msgstr ""
"**你**: §0？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这可能行得通。而且你大概会需要引理 §1。对于 §2，它会从假设 §3 推出"
"结论 §4。"

#. §0: `2`
#. §1: `1`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L06_Prime_Specialize__prime_def
msgid ""
"A prime number is a natural number greater or equal to §0, which is only "
"divisible by §1\n"
"and itself"
msgstr ""
"**你**：啊哈。所以素数就是一个大于等于 §0 的自然数，只能被 §1 和它自己整除。"
"听起来很熟悉。"

#. §0: `«{hp}»`
#. §1: `«{a}»`
#. §2: `have hp' := «{hp}» «{a}»`
#. §3: `specialize «{hp}» «{a}»`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L06_Prime_Specialize__prime_def
msgid "Apply §0 onto §1. Try either §2 or §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我现在肯定要把 §0 用到 §1 上，对吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那你就说 §2。或者更优雅一点：§3。"

#. §0: `unfold`
#. §1: `Prime`
#. §2: `rw [prime_def] at hp`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L06_Prime_Specialize__prime_def
msgid "Do not §0 §1. Use §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：不，还是别。\n"
"你不该把 §1 §0！——那只会让一切更难。\n"
"还是用我说的 §2 吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L06_Prime_Specialize__prime_def
msgid "Intro Prado L06"
msgstr ""
"**你**：好。那你现在能给我演示一下怎么用素数做推理吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：让我看看手头有没有关于素数的推理题……也许就这题？"

#. §0: `linarith`
#. §1: `«{a}» = 1`
#. §2: `2 ≤ «{a}»`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L06_Prime_Specialize__prime_def
msgid "Try §0 to show contradiction between §1 and §2"
msgstr "**司南**：试试 §0。这应该能找出 §1 和 §2 之间的矛盾。"

#. §0: `(hp : Prime p)`
#. §1: `p`
#. §2: `rw [prime_def] at hp`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L06_Prime_Specialize__prime_def
msgid "§0 is the assumption that §1 is prime. Use §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这里 §0 当然就是假设 §1 是个素数。要用这个假设来做证明，你最好总是"
"用 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L07_dvd_mul
msgid "Conclusion Prado L07"
msgstr "**你**：你出的题也太简单了吧。"

#. §0: `Prime.dvd_mul`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L07_dvd_mul
msgid "Intro Prado L07: Use lemma §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这里还有一道小素数问题。引理 §0 说：一个素数整除一个乘积，当且仅当"
"它整除其中一个因子。你在这里把它用上就行。"

#. §0: `exists_prime_and_dvd`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L08_exists_prime_and_dvd
msgid "Apply §0 to prove existence of prime factor"
msgstr ""
"**你** *(对司南)*：你有想法这里的素因子可能是什么吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没。\n"
"\n"
"司南想了想。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不过也无所谓。他又没问某个具体的因子，只问是否存在某个素因子。但那"
"太显然了。让我想想……我觉得你这里需要的就是 §0 这个命题。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L08_exists_prime_and_dvd
msgid "Conclusion Prado L08"
msgstr ""
"**吉诺**：好吧，我们继续走。你们看，这楼梯是不是很棒？我们上去！\n"
"\n"
"**你** *(对司南)*：我们现在试着把要给吉诺看的那个命题表述出来吧。恰好有一个"
"偶……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：停！“恰好一个”我们还没学过。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L08_exists_prime_and_dvd
msgid "Intro Prado L08"
msgstr ""
"为了让吉诺保持好心情，司南小心翼翼地问他要不要也给你们出一道题。\n"
"于是，他给了你们一道先前问题的变体。"

#. §0: `use`
#. §1: `∃!`
#. §2: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L09_ExistsUnique
msgid ""
"Applying §0 onto §1 is usually badly readable. Try §2 directly afterwards"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：其实 §0 用在 §1 上总会弄得有点乱。最好每次立刻再跟一个 §2，这样就清"
"楚多了。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L09_ExistsUnique
msgid "Intro Prado L09"
msgstr "**司南**：但这也没那么难。来，你看看这道问题。"

#. §0: `«{w}»`
#. §1: `a * «{w}» = b`
#. §2: `«{w}»`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L09_ExistsUnique
msgid ""
"Show two statements: (1) §0 satisfies §1 and (2) §2 is the only element "
"with\n"
"such a property"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：如我所说，你现在要证明两个命题：(1) §0 满足 §1，(2) §2 是唯一具有这"
"个性质的元素。"

#. §0: `mul_eq_mul_left_iff`
#. §1: ```
#. a * b = a * c ↔ b = c ∨ a = 0
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L09_ExistsUnique
msgid ""
"Try §0 which states\n"
"§1\n"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：太好了。现在说唯一性。我觉得引理 §0 可能有用：\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"

#. §0: `∃! m, P(m)`
#. §1: `m`
#. §2: `P(m)`
#. §3: `m`
#. §4: `P(m)`
#. §5: `m'`
#. §6: `P(m')`
#. §7: `m`
#. §8: `m`
#. §9: `use _`
#: Game.Levels.Prado.L09_ExistsUnique
msgid ""
"§0 is notation for 'there exists exactly one §1 for which §2 holds'.\n"
"It is defined as 'There exists a §3 , s.t., §4 holds, and each other element "
"§5, for which\n"
"§6 holds, is equal to §7'. Try finding an appropriate §8 and apply §9"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我懂了——§0 就是“恰好存在一个 §1 使得 §2 成立”的记号。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。而它的定义很简单：“存在一个 §3，使得（1） §4 成立，并且（2） "
"任意其他元素 §5，只要 §6 成立，就已经等于 §7。”所以第一步就是找一个合适的 "
"§8，然后用 §9。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L10_EvenPrime
msgid "Conclusion Prado L10"
msgstr ""
"**你**：太棒啦！那现在谁去告诉他？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也许我们还是别说了。我感觉他本来就最喜欢他的博物馆空空如也的样"
"子。\n"
"\n"
"于是你们礼貌地感谢了这次讲解，表示对这里的冰雕建筑技艺深感震撼，然后继续踏上"
"旅程。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L10_EvenPrime
msgid "Intro Prado L10"
msgstr ""
"这时你们已经到了屋顶露台。不过吉诺也已经放弃解释所有建筑细节了。风景还不"
"错。\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(对你)*：我觉得差不多了。"

#: Game.Levels.Prado.L10_EvenPrime
msgid "Remind former proof"
msgstr "**司南**：再仔细过一遍我们已经证明过的那些命题。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus
msgid "Intro Quantus"
msgstr ""
"在“量词”上，一大群形式哲学家在等着你们了。她们七嘴八舌地说个不停，你们甚至很"
"难让别人听见自己的声音。最后，司南发出一声响亮的锣声——她们才短暂安静下来。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我们有一封信要交给你们的女王。你们能带我们去见女王吗？\n"
"\n"
"**所有人** *(齐声)*：我们已经都在这儿了！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：行吧。那你们谁是女王？\n"
"\n"
"一阵尴尬的沉默。大家都耸耸肩。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你们到底有没有女王？\n"
"\n"
"**所有人** *(齐声)*：有有有。我们有女王，我们有女王。\n"
"\n"
"**司南** *(对你)*：我总结一下：女王是存在的，但没人知道她是谁……\n"
"\n"
"**你**：这不矛盾吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你一个数学家还这么问？不，这不矛盾。这只是一个“纯存在性陈述”。\n"
"\n"
"你不太确定他到底有多认真。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我建议，我们就把包裹直接交给*所有*居民。这样我们自然也就交给女王"
"了。\n"
"\n"
"**你** *(对着人群)*：我们给你们带来了一个来自“蕴涵”的包裹。喏，这个给你们。\n"
"\n"
"司南把它扔进人群里，形式哲学家们一把撕开。里面确实只有一张纸。几分钟后，它又"
"回到了你们手里。而形式哲学家们都好奇地看着你们会怎么处理它。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus
msgid "Quantus"
msgstr "量词"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L01_NonemptyUse
msgid "Conclusion Quantus L01"
msgstr "你们翻到了纸的背面。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L01_NonemptyUse
msgid "Intro Quantus L01"
msgstr "纸的正面写着："

#. §0: `use _`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L01_NonemptyUse
msgid "Show that there is a natural number by §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我是要证明存在一个自然数吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。你用 §0 随便给出一个自然数就行。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L02_NonemptyObtain
msgid "Conclusion Quantus L02"
msgstr ""
"你们得到了一阵礼貌性的掌声。\n"
"形式哲学家们彼此窃窃私语。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L02_NonemptyObtain
msgid "Intro Quantus L02"
msgstr "纸的背面写着："

#. §0: `A`
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `h`
#. §3: `A`
#. §4: `obtain`
#. §5: `obtain ⟨a⟩ := h`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L02_NonemptyObtain
msgid ""
"§0 is in 'type', whcih can be interpreted as §1 being a set which is by "
"assumption §2\n"
"not empty. The goal is to show that there is an element in §3. Use §4 to "
"disect assumption.\n"
"Try §5."
msgstr ""
"**你**：这又是什么情况？§0 在“Type”里？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你可以把 §1 直接当成一个集合……\n"
"\n"
"**你**：……根据假设 §2，它不是空集？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：然后我要证明在 §3 里存在一个元素？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那这不就正好从假设里直接出来吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这又是那种可以用 §4 来“拆开”的假设。试试 §5。"

#. §0: `decide`
#. §1: `Even 42`
#. §2: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L03_Decide
msgid ""
"Conclusion Quantus L03: Explain that §0 can show True/False for §1, if\n"
"§2 possesses an algorithm for making this decision"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0 还能干些什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：策略 §0 知道一系列可执行的算法，用来判定某些命题到底是真的还是假"
"的。  \n"
"对于 §1，你大概能猜到算法是什么。  \n"
"我们肯定还会遇到别的例子。"

#. §0: ```
#. def Even (n : ℕ) : Prop := ∃ r, n = r + r
#. ```
#. §1: `Odd`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L03_Decide
msgid ""
"Intro Quantus L03: Show defintion\n"
"§0\n"
"before introducing §1"
msgstr ""
"显然，这些形式哲学家们正商量着出另外一个问题来考考你们。\n"
"过了一会儿，两个阵营逐渐成形。\n"
"你们交替听到“Even”和“Odd”的喊声。\n"
"谨慎起见，司南先把对应的定义给你看：\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"还没等他继续讲 §1，不知从人群的哪个角落又冒出来了下面这张纸："

#. §0: `decide`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L03_Decide
msgid ""
"Remind that §0 solves every task where a simple algorithm is available to "
"solve them"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：等等！这根本不需要定义！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：这也太……平凡了吧……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：还记得吗？§0 能解决所有那些存在简单算法来判定真假的问题。关于具体数"
"字的命题大多都属于这一类！"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid "Conclusion Quantus L04"
msgstr "掌声！"

#. §0: `Even «{n}»`
#. §1: `r`
#. §2: `r + r = «{n}»`
#. §3: `unfold Even at *`
#. §4: `decide`
#. §5: `decide`
#. §6: `«{n}»`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid ""
"Explain definition of §0 by §1 using §2. Look up definition by §3.\n"
"§4 might be considered but §5 does not work, because of §6 arbitrary."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：如你在上面看到的，§0 的定义是：存在一个 §1，使得 §2。最好你先用 §3 "
"把这个定义展开一下。这样你就更清楚发生了什么。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那 §4 呢？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§5 行不通，因为 §6 不是一个具体的数，而是任意的数。你得自己动点脑"
"筋！"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `s`
#. §2: `s + s = «{n}»`
#. §3: `choose s hs using «{h}»`
#. §4: `s`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid ""
"Explain that from §0 follow that there is §1 such that §2. Try §3\n"
"to introduce §4."
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以从 §0 我现在知道，存在一个§1，使得§2……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：用 §3，你确实可以把这个 §4 引入进来。"

#. §0: `r`
#. §1: `n ^ 2 = r + r`
#. §2: `let r := …`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid "Find §0 such that §1. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那现在我得找一个合适的数 §0，使得 §1？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。你要是愿意，可以先用 §2 定义这个数。"

#. §0: ```
#. def Even (n : ℕ) : Prop := ∃ r, n = r + r
#. ```
#. §1: ```
#. def Odd (n : ℕ) : Prop := ∃ r, n = 2 * r + 1
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid ""
"Intro Quantus L04: Show defintion\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"and\n"
"\n"
"§1"
msgstr ""
"“Even”和“Odd”的喊声从人群里久久不息，所以司南又给你展示了一遍定义：\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"以及\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"随后，你们又收到了一张纸："

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid "Set number"
msgstr "**司南**：也行。不过现在你真的得想一个数出来。"

#. §0: `use r`
#. §1: `use 2 * s^2`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid "Try §0 or instead §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这个数看起来不错！现在你就直接写 §0。你当然也可以一开始就写 §1。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid "[Doc.Theorem] Nat.even_square"
msgstr "一个偶数的平方是偶数。"

#. §0: `unfold Even at h`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid "[Hint jrxb] Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：你最好也再写一下 §0，这样你就明白怎么回事了。"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `rw`
#. §2: `n`
#. §3: `«{s}» + «{s}»`
#. §4: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid ""
"before using §0, use §1 to replace §2 by §3, because\n"
"§4 does not know otherwise."
msgstr ""
"**你**：啊，现在用 §0！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：但首先你还得用 §1 把 §2 替换成 §3，不然 §4 并不知道这一点。"

#. §0: `«{n}» ^ 2 / 2`
#. §1: `ℕ`
#. §2: `«{n}» = 1`
#. §3: ```
#. 1 ^ 2 = (1 ^ 2) / 2 + (1 ^ 2) / 2
#. ```
#. §4: `1 = 1 / 2 + 1 / 2 = 0 + 0`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L04_Exists
msgid ""
"§0 is a natural number because division over §1 in Lean is always rounded "
"down.\n"
"For §2 that means\n"
"§3\n"
"which is  §4.\n"
msgstr ""
"人群中响起一阵困惑的嘟囔。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：等等，为什么 §0 居然又是个自然数？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：在 Lean 里，对 §1 的除法总是向下取整。等式 \n"
"\n"
"§3\n"
"\n"
"就会变成 §4。你这是走偏了！\n"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L05_neg_pow
msgid "Intro Quantus L05"
msgstr ""
"又有一个问题传到你们这儿。\n"
"这显然来自另一个阵营。"

#. §0: `Odd.neg_pow`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L05_neg_pow
msgid "Try continue with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我觉得你可以在这里用 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L06_not_even_iff_odd
msgid "Conclusion Quantus L06"
msgstr ""
"这次你们显然给形式哲学家们留下了深刻印象。\n"
"她们赞许地点点头。\n"
"\n"
"随后，她们又开始窃窃私语。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L06_not_even_iff_odd
msgid "Intro Quantus L06"
msgstr ""
"下一张纸立刻冒了出来。\n"
"看起来她们这次达成了一个折中方案。"

#. §0: `i`
#. §1: `by_cases h : Even i`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L06_not_even_iff_odd
msgid "Try case distinction if §0 is even or uneven. Try §1."
msgstr ""
"**你**：我觉得我想做个分类讨论，看 §0 是偶数还是奇数。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那就做呗——比如用 §1。"

#. §0: `not_even_iff_odd`
#. §1: `¬Even`
#. §2: `Odd`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L06_not_even_iff_odd
msgid "With §0 one can transform §1 to §2"
msgstr "**司南**：用 §0，你可以把 §1 变成 §2。"

#. §0: `not_odd_iff_even`
#. §1: `¬Odd`
#. §2: `Even`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L06_not_even_iff_odd
msgid "With §0 one can transform §1 to §2."
msgstr "**司南**：用 §0 你可以把 §1 变成 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L07_Forall
msgid "Conclusion Quantus L07"
msgstr ""
"又是一阵赞许的点头。\n"
"\n"
"又是一阵窃窃私语。"

#. §0: `∀`
#. §1: `\\forall`
#. §2: `∀ x, …`
#. §3: `intro x`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L07_Forall
msgid "Explain §0 i.e. §1 and approch to prove §2  by §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这个 §0 肯定就是“对任意一个”。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：而且写作 §1。证明目标里的一个 §2，你可以像处理一个蕴涵那样用 §3 来"
"搞定。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L07_Forall
msgid "Intro Quantus L07"
msgstr "在一阵漫长而嘈杂的争论之后，下面这个问题从人群里传到了你们手中。"

#. §0: `push Not`
#. §1: `not_exists (P : X → Prop) : ¬ (∃ x, P x) ↔ ∀ x, (¬ P x)`
#. §2: `not_forall (P : X → Prop) : ¬ (∀ x, P x) ↔ ∃ x, (¬ P x)`
#. §3: `push Not`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L08_PushNeg
msgid ""
"Conclusion Quantus L08: §0 internally uses §1\n"
"and §2. Memorize §3."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：干得漂亮。顺带一提，§0 在内部其实用了两个引理：\n"
"\n"
"* §1 \n"
"* §2\n"
"\n"
"第一个引理就是你刚刚证明的那个命题。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：太棒了。我这是用它来证明它……\n"
"\n"
"司南咧嘴一笑。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：反正你把 §3 记住就行。"

#. §0: `«{P}»`
#. §1: `«{P}»`
#. §2: `«{X}»`
#. §3: `«{X}»`
#. §4: `«{P}» x`
#. §5: `x`
#. §6: `x`
#. §7: `x`
#. §8: `«{P}»`
#. §9: `x : «{X}»`
#. §10: `push Not`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L08_PushNeg
msgid ""
"Explain §0: §1 is an expression over the type §2. §3 could e.g. be the "
"natural\n"
"numbers. §4 could be the expression: §5 is even. Or: §6 has seven prime "
"factors. Or: §7 is\n"
"a favorite number. In other words: §8 is a mapping that takes §9 and maps it "
"onto an expression.\n"
"Try §10."
msgstr ""
"**你**：那这个 §0 到底是什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1 是一个“谓词”；也就是关于类型 §2 的对象的一个命题。比如说，§3 又"
"可以是自然数的类型。然后 §4 可以是这样的命题：自然数 §5 是偶数。或者：§6 有七"
"个素因子。或者：§7 是司南最喜欢的数字。或者……\n"
"\n"
"**你**：好吧，我觉得我懂了。§8 就像是一个映射：给它一个元素 §9，它就会返回一"
"个命题。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，差不多。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：好。那这里的命题是什么也就很清楚了。你现在要告诉我怎么用 Lean语证明这"
"个？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。你需要的是 §10。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L08_PushNeg
msgid "Intro Quanus L08"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：趁我们等着，我先简单讲讲否定和量词是怎么搭配的。我有种感觉，我们马"
"上就会用到。"

#. §0: `push Not`
#. §1: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L08_PushNeg
msgid "Try §0 at §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：§0 是从左往右推的。所以你在这里不能把它用到证明目标上，但可以用到 "
"§1 上。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "Conclusion Quantus L09"
msgstr ""
"形式哲学家们兴奋得不行。掌声平息之后，你也问了一个问题。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：这里有没有人能给我们一点在Lean宇宙里的方向感？\n"
"\n"
"**所有人**：有有有。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：谁啊？\n"
"\n"
"这个问题又太具体了。尴尬的沉默。"

#. §0: `Odd`
#. §1: `not_odd_iff_even`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "Go back, keep §0 and try §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这条解法在我看来有点太难了。\n"
" 我建议先退回去，保留 §0，这样你最后就能用上 §1。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "Intro Quantus L09"
msgstr "经过漫长的来回争论，这些形式哲学家们终于就下面这个问题达成了一致。"

#. §0: `not_odd_iff_even`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "Now you can apply §0"
msgstr "**司南**：好选择！现在你可以用 §0 了。"

#. §0: `¬`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "Remind about §0"
msgstr "**你**：嚯。最左边又是一个 §0。真稀奇….…"

#. §0: `use`
#. §1: `not_odd_iff_even`
#. §2: `not_odd_iff_even`
#. §3: `rw`
#. §4: `use`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid ""
"Try §0 with a number and then §1. You can not use §2\n"
"directly, as §3 cannot be applied inside of quantors. Try §4 with a number."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在你用 §0 代入一个数，然后大概就该用引理 §1 了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我现在就能用 §2 吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不行，§3 不能在量词里面改写。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：可那我该怎么做？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：以后再教你，不在这种大庭广众之下。我现在宁愿用 §4 给出一个真正的"
"数，然后再改写。"

#. §0: `push Not`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "[Doc.Theorem] can use §0 instead"
msgstr "你可以不用这个定理，而是用 §0。"

#. §0: `∃`
#. §1: `∀`
#. §2: `Even n`
#. §3: `n`
#. §4: `Odd n`
#. §5: `n`
#. §6: `rw`
#. §7: `ring`
#. §8: `+, -, *, ^`
#. §9: `decide`
#. §10: `unfold`
#. §11: `use`
#. §12: `∃`
#. §13: `choose x hx using h`
#. §14: `∃`
#. §15: `intro`
#. §16: `∀`
#. §17: `push Not`
#. §18: `¬∃`
#. §19: `¬∀`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid ""
"Conclusion Quantus L10: Overview of planet contents: §0, §1, §2 (§3 is "
"even),\n"
"§4 (§5 is odd), §6, §7 (solves equations containing §8), §9,\n"
"§10, §11 (to tackle §12 in goal), §13 (to disect §14 in assumptions),\n"
"§15 (to tackle §16 in goal) and §17 (for §18 and §19 in goal)."
msgstr ""
"**你**：明白了。但我现在真的受够这套谓词逻辑了！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那我们最好继续飞吧！不过在你开口问之前——这里再给你一份总览：你在这"
"个星球上学到的最重要的东西。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"|   记号  | 含义     | \n"
"|:--------------|:----------------------------| \n"
"| §0            | 存在量词      | \n"
"| §1            | 全称量词           | \n"
"\n"
"| 策略                    | 用"
"法                                               | \n"
"|:--------------------------|:-------------------------------------------------------| \n"
"| §6                        | 用等式改写                          | \n"
"| §9                        | 用算法证明关于具体数字的命题    | \n"
"| §10                       | 把定义“展开”      | \n"
"| §11                       | 为目标里的 §12 给出一个具体值               "
"| \n"
"| §13                       | 在一个假设里拆开 §14                | \n"
"| §15                       | 处理目标里的 §16                          | \n"
"| §17                       | 把对 §18 或 §19 的否定推过量词  | "

#. §0: `push Not at «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "Continue with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：你可以在这里用 §0 接着往下做。"

#. §0: `«{isDrinking}»`
#. §1: `p`
#. §2: `«{isDrinking}» p`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "Explain §0 and §1 in statement §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以，§0 又是个谓词……如果 §1 是一个人，那 §2 就是一个要么真、要么假的"
"命题。到这儿都没问题。"

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "Intro Quantus L10"
msgstr ""
"**你**：你们是不是只会齐声说话，或者七嘴八舌地一起说？\n"
"\n"
"又是一阵更长的沉默。然后突然：\n"
"\n"
"**所有人**：我们中间有一个人，只要她说话，那大家就都会说话！\n"
"\n"
"你挠了挠头。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这不是很明显吗？每个有人居住的星球上都是这样的！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：什么？！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这是“饮者悖论”的一个版本！你不知道吗？那你最好去你的随身小书库里查"
"查！*在每家酒吧里，都有一个人具有这样的性质：只要她喝酒，所有人就都喝酒。* 更"
"准确地说：在每个非空的酒吧里。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我不信。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我信。我甚至觉得你能证明。来，试试！"

#. §0: `by_cases`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "Look at §0"
msgstr "**司南**：看看 §0。"

#. §0: `«{hp}»`
#. §1: `«{hp'}»`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "Observe §0 and §1"
msgstr "**司南**：你看着 §0 和 §1 的时候，看到了什么？"

#. §0: `∀ (y : «{People}»), «{isDrinking}» y`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "Try proof by case for §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那我现在怎么开头？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我不是说了嘛，最好去翻翻你的随身小书库。要是我没记错的话，可以按 "
"§0 这个命题是真是假来做分类讨论。"

#. §0: `h_nonempty`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "Use assumption §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那我现在选谁？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这不都一样吗？根据假设 §0，你知道至少有那么一个人。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `obtain`
#. §2: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
msgid "We have assumption §0. Try applying §1 on §2."
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以按 §0，确实存在一个不喝酒的人。我能不能用这个，让命题变得“显然”为"
"真？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你看看怎么把 §1 应用到假设 §2 上。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana
msgid "Intro Robotswana"
msgstr ""
"你们降落在一颗温暖的星球上，走出飞船，踏上一片辽阔的草原。\n"
"\n"
"四处张望了一会儿后，司南发现了一些足迹，从你们的着陆点向外延伸，穿过零星的树"
"木。\n"
"你们简单商量了一下，决定沿着这些足迹走。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana
msgid "Robotswana"
msgstr "埃托沙"

#. §0: `Matrix.smul_ebasis`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L01_SMulEBasis
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L01: Save result as §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那我们现在拿这个“发现”怎么办？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不知道。反正我先把它存成 §0，以防我们还要用到。\n"
"\n"
"于是你们继续沿着痕迹前进。"

#. §0: ```
#. E i j := single i j (1 : ℝ)
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L01_SMulEBasis
msgid ""
"Intro Robotswana L01: introduce definition\n"
"§0"
msgstr ""
"你们沿着足迹走，找到一张羊皮纸，最上方写着一条笔记。\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"下面是一堆乱七八糟的涂写，不过很明显是从一行清晰的文字开始的："

#. §0: `E i j`
#. §1: `n × n`
#. §2: `ℝ`
#. §3: `1`
#. §4: $(i, j)$
#. §5: `single i j (a : R)`
#. §6: `a`
#. §7: `E`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L01_SMulEBasis
msgid ""
"§0 ist die §1-Matrix (mit Werten in §2) mit einer §3 an\n"
"Stelle §4 und Null überall sonst.\n"
"\n"
"Dies ist eine spezialisierte Form der generellen §5,\n"
"welche auch nicht-quadratisch sein kann und einen beliebigen Wert §6 aus "
"einem beliebigen\n"
"Ring annehmen kann. Wir benutzen hier §7 einfach als Abkürzung."
msgstr ""
"§0 是一个 §1 矩阵（取值于 §2），在 §4 位置是 §3，其余地方全是 0。\n"
"\n"
"这是更一般的 §5 的一个特例；后者也可以不是方阵，并且可以取自任意环的任意值 "
"§6。\n"
"这里我们只是把 §7 当作缩写来用。"

#. §0: `Mat[«{n}»,«{n}»]`
#. §1: $(«{n}» \\times «{n}»)$
#. §2: `Fin «{n}»`
#. §3: `Fin «{n}»`
#. §4: $\\{0,...,n-1\\}$
#. §5: $0$
#. §6: $1$
#. §7: `single i j a`
#. §8: `(i, j)`
#. §9: `a`
#. §10: `E`
#. §11: `a = 1`
#. §12: `A i j`
#. §13: `A`
#. §14: `(i, j)`
#. §15: $$
#. A_{i,j} \\cdot
#. \\begin{pmatrix}
#. 0 & 0 & 0\\ %(new line)
#. 1 & 0 & 0 \\ %(new line)
#. 0 & 0 & 0
#. \\end{pmatrix}
#. =
#. \\begin{pmatrix}
#. 0 & 0 & 0\\ %(new line)
#. A_{i,j} & 0 & 0 \\ %(new line)
#. 0 & 0 & 0
#. \\end{pmatrix}
#. $$
#. §16: `unfold E`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L01_SMulEBasis
msgid ""
"§0 looks like a §1 matrix. Reminder for §2: §3 is\n"
"the set §4. Indeces start here at §5 and not §6. §7 is the matrix which\n"
"has at position §8 the entry §9 and else zero. §10s are abbreviations for "
"case §11.\n"
"§12 is entry of matrix §13 at position §14. Goal can be seen as scalar "
"multiplication akin to\n"
"\n"
"§15\n"
"\n"
"Begin with §16.\n"
msgstr ""
"**你**：不管是什么东西在这儿留下了痕迹——我感觉它挺喜欢矩阵的。总之，§0 看起来"
"很像 §1 矩阵。我就是想不起来 §2 是啥了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§3 是集合 §4。所以这里的行、列索引是从 §5 开始，而不是从 §6。还有 "
"§7 我正好认识：它是在位置 §8 处取值为 §9、其他地方全是 0 的矩阵。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那这些 §10s 就只是 §11 这种情况的简写咯？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：看起来是这样。而且 §12 就是矩阵 §13 在位置 §14 的那个条目。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：啊，懂了。所以这里不是矩阵乘积，只是标量乘法。大概像……\n"
"\n"
"你在纸上乱写：\n"
"\n"
"§15\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那这就又……显然了！？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。我觉得你从 §16 开始，后面就会自己顺下去。\n"

#. §0: `E.mul_of_ne`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L02_EBasis
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L02: save result as §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我也把这个 §0 存一下，以防万一。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L02_EBasis
msgid "Intro Robotswana L02"
msgstr ""
"没过多久，你们发现了两张非常相似的纸条，上面同样写满了难以辨认的字迹，几乎全"
"都被划掉了。\n"
"不过每张纸上的第一行还勉强能辨认出来。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L02_EBasis
msgid "Looks like matrix multiplication"
msgstr "**你**：这看起来就是矩阵乘法。应该也没错。"

#. §0: `simp`
#. §1: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L02_EBasis
msgid "Try §0 with §1"
msgstr "**司南**：但别忘了，§0 需要你明确告诉它使用假设 §1！"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L03
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L03"
msgstr ""
"**你**：现在我倒是很好奇，到底是谁把这些纸条弄丢了或者扔在这儿的。走吧，我们"
"继续。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L03
msgid "Seems to be correct"
msgstr "**你**：看起来是对的。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L04_MatrixEqSum
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L04"
msgstr ""
"你决定沿着一串特别显眼的足迹走。\n"
"司南跟在你后面，走着走着，还顺手从地上捡起了一张羊皮纸。"

#. §0: `E i j`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L04_MatrixEqSum
msgid "Explain statement w.r.t. §0 and use former results"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这看起来就是在说，这些 §0 构成了矩阵空间的一组生成元。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你肯定马上就能用上我们已经得到的那些结果！"

#. §0: `(A i j) • E i j`
#. §1: `Matrix.smul_ebasis`
#. §2: `rw […]`
#. §3: `simp […]`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L04_MatrixEqSum
msgid ""
"Expression §0 can be simplified with §1.\n"
"§2 can not be used under a sum. §3 can work.\n"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：表达式 §0 你肯定能用 §1 化简吧。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以用 §2？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不，在求和号下面那样不行。不过 §3 倒是有希望。\n"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L04_MatrixEqSum
msgid "Intro Robotswana L04"
msgstr ""
"你们来到一处地方，那里有一大片正方形草地被踩得稀烂。\n"
"足迹横七竖八，朝着不同方向延伸。\n"
"\n"
"你们有点没头绪地搜了一圈，找到了各种各样的羊皮纸碎片。\n"
"大多数是空白的或者已经看不清了，但有一张你还能辨认出来。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L04_MatrixEqSum
msgid "Repeat proof from first level"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：行吧，你也可以直接把第一张羊皮纸上的证明再做一遍。\n"
"来吧，熟能生巧。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：行了行了，我又没有你那种机械脑子。"

#. §0: `apply matrix_eq_sum_single`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L04_MatrixEqSum
msgid "Try to use §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：对了！按现在这个写法，我在我的库里见过这个命题。这正是 §0。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：太好了！那我们就不用在这上面浪费时间了。"

#. §0: $(n × n)$
#. §1: $A$
#. §2: $\\mathbb{R}$
#. §3: $$A = \\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}\\sum_{j=0}^{n-1} A_{ij} \\cdot E(i, j)$$
#. §4: `matrix_eq_sum_single`
#. §5: $(m × n)$
#. §6: $R$
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L04_MatrixEqSum
msgid ""
"[Doc.Theorem] Matrix.matrix_eq_sum_ebasis\n"
"every §0 matrix §1 over §2 an be expressed as\n"
"§3\n"
"more generally, use §4 for §5 matrices over any §6"
msgstr ""
"任意实 §0 矩阵 §2 都可以写成\n"
"§3。\n"
"\n"
"一般维度和系数类型的矩阵，见 §4。"

#. §0: `sum_congr`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Again employ §0"
msgstr "**司南**：那你大概又该用 §0 了。"

#. §0: `1 «{i}» «{x}»`
#. §1: `Matrix.one_apply`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Apply definition §0 by §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那我现在要怎么展开 §0 的定义？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1！"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L05"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我感觉我们是在追踪一个对矩阵对角线感兴趣的人……不过我开始有点渴了！"

#. §0: `1 «{i}» «{i}»`
#. §1: `1 • _`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Explain simplification of §0 and §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：谢谢，这很有帮助！这一步应该很简单：对单个元素求和，而这里 §0 又是 "
"1，而且 §1 也能化简！"

#. §0: `1 «{i}» «{x}»`
#. §1: `if «{i}» = «{x}» then _ else _`
#. §2: `«{i}» = «{x}»`
#. §3: `«{i}» ≠ «{x}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Explain that §0 is defined as §1 and that either §2 or §3 is needed"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：反过来会更有用，因为 §0 被定义成了 §1！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你说得对，我马上就需要 §2 或者 §3。让我改一下。"

#. §0: `«{h₂}»`
#. §1: `«{i}» ≠ «{x}»`
#. §2: `have h₃ : «{i}» ≠ «{x}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Explain that §0 states §1. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：但这种情况我该怎么做？§0 或多或少是在说 §1。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，但也不完全是。你先用 §2 把你想要的假设写出来，然后简单证明一下"
"吧！"

#. §0: `1`
#. §1: `1 «{i}» j`
#. §2: `j ≠ «{i}»`
#. §3: `j = «{i}»`
#. §4: `have h : {«{i}»} ⊆ univ`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Explain §0 and values of §1 for all §2 i.e. §3. Try §4"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0 在这里是单位矩阵，对吧？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那 §1 对所有 §2 都是零啊。所以除了 §3 对应的那一项之外，其他所有求和"
"项都会消掉。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：是这样吗？那让我想想……你能先证明一下 §4 吗？"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Explanation of equal sums"
msgstr "**你**：我觉得这两个求和是一样的，因为每一项求和项都一样。"

#. §0: `1`
#. §1: `matrix_eq_sum_ebasis`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Intro Robotswana L05: §0 indicates unit matrix. Begin with §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：给我看看，你手里是什么？是关于单位矩阵的吗？能放进我们的收藏吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对——最右边那个 §0 在这里就是单位矩阵。我觉得你可以直接从 §1 开"
"始。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我在想，我们是不是把什么重要的东西落在广场上了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：无所谓啦，我们已经走出挺远一段了。先试试这个吧！"

#. §0: `sum_subset`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Now §0 can be applied"
msgstr "**司南**：很好。现在你就可以用 §0 了。"

#. §0: `«{h₂}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Try to simplify §0."
msgstr "**你**：我首先会看看 §0 能不能化简。"

#. §0: `rw`
#. §1: `if_neg`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Try §0 and §1"
msgstr "**司南**：既然这是错的，你就可以用 §0 和 §1 继续推进。"

#. §0: `matrix_eq_sum_ebasis`
#. §1: `matrix_eq_sum_single`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Try §0 not §1"
msgstr "**司南**：不，不是 §0，而是 §1。"

# GPT: Mehrdeutig war hier v.a. das eingedeutschte/Codewort „§3e§4riten“ (= „rewriten“) und der Tippfehler „Gleichheitszeigen“; ich habe „Gleichheitszeichen“ als „等号“ verstanden und „rewriten“ als technischen Lean-Ausdruck stehen gelassen.
#. §0: `matrix_eq_sum_ebasis`
#. §1: `1`
#. §2: `matrix_eq_sum_ebasis 1`
#. §3: `r`
#. §4: `w`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid ""
"Try §0 on §1 with §2 to §3e§4rite\n"
"goal."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：就像我刚才说的，我觉得你可以直接从 §0 开始，把它用在等号右边的单位"
"矩阵 §1 上。也就是说，你可以用等式 §2 来重写目标 也就是§3§4。"

#. §0: `symm`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Try §0 to fix skewed order"
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，现在顺序反了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：想想 §0！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：对哦，我们之前在那个玩传送带的怪人那里就已经用过这个了。"

#. §0: `funext r s`
#. §1: $(r,s)$
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "Try §0 to focus on position §1."
msgstr ""
"**你**：然后呢？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：用 §0 的话，你可以把注意力集中到矩阵在 §1 位置的那个条目上。"

# GPT: „§0 kann man immer versuchen …“ lässt sich auch als „Man kann immer §0 versuchen …“ lesen; ich habe die näher am Original stehende Satzstellung mit vorangestelltem §0 gewählt.
#. §0: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L05_EBasisDiagSum
msgid "§0 is always available"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 总是可以先试试……"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L06_EBasisEqOnDiag
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L06"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我觉得，“交换子被消去”这个假设，我们先就这么带着用吧。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：很好。 我是不是已经说过，我开始有点口渴了？"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `E i i`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L06_EBasisEqOnDiag
msgid "Explain §0 with §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：换句话说：如果 §0 会消去交换子，那它在所有 §1 上的取值都相等。对"
"吗？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我们来看看！"

#. §0: $$
#. [A, B] = AB - BA
#. $$
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L06_EBasisEqOnDiag
msgid ""
"Intro Robotswana L06: Introduce nihiliated cummotator\n"
"§0"
msgstr ""
"顺着足迹走，你们来到一棵大树前。树荫下，你们发现了一个一动不动的东西：\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：哦，看，一个交换子！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：它看起来已经坏得很厉害了。我觉得它是渴死的。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：再看，树上还写着东西。"

#. §0: `E i k = (E i j) * (E j k)`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L06_EBasisEqOnDiag
msgid "Remind former results with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我们不是在某张纸条上见过 §0 吗？"

#. §0: `«{h₁}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L06_EBasisEqOnDiag
msgid "Remind use of §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你做这一大堆，不就是为了用 §0 吗？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：啊对，没错！"

#. §0: `«{h₁}»`
#. §1: `A * B`
#. §2: `f (E i i) = f (A * B) = f (E j j)`
#. §3: `trans f (A * B)`
#. §4: `f (E i i) = f (A * B)`
#. §5: `f (A * B) = f (E j j)`
#. §6: `«{h₁}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L06_EBasisEqOnDiag
msgid ""
"Start with §0. Find §1 with §2. Try §3 to get §4 and §5 and see if §6 "
"applicable"
msgstr ""
"**你**：可我该拿我们的假设 §0 怎么办？\n"
"我得先弄出一个乘法才行。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你得想出一个矩阵乘积 §1，使得 §2 成立。\n"
"然后你就可以写 §3，把它拆成两个目标——§4 和 §5——这样 §6 也许就能用上了。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L07_EBasisZeroOffDiag
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L07"
msgstr "这些足迹看起来新鲜多了。你们继续沿着足迹前进。"

#. §0: `unfold E`
#. §1: `simp`
#. §2: `E`
#. §3: `simp [E]`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L07_EBasisZeroOffDiag
msgid "Try §0 or §1 with §2 via §3"
msgstr "**司南**：别忘了 §0，或者让 §1 用 §2 的定义（§3）。"

#. §0: `«{h₁}»`
#. §1: `E i j`
#. §2: `E i j * E j j`
#. §3: `E.mul_of_ne`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L07_EBasisZeroOffDiag
msgid "Use §0 by writing §1 as §2. Remind §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：那我们在这里怎么用 §0 呢？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：要不这次把 §1 写成乘积 §2？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：为什么要这么写？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：因为在这个乘积里把因子对调一下，我会得到零！\n"
"我们不是已经见过了吗，§3 之类的。"

#. §0: `trans f (E i j * E j j)`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L07_EBasisZeroOffDiag
msgid "[Hint plnk] Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：随你吧。你最好试试 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L07_EBasisZeroOffDiag
msgid "[Robotswana.L07] Hint 1: Try commutating"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你现在是想在这里交换一下吗？\n"
"**你**：没错！"

#. §0: `h₁`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L07_EBasisZeroOffDiag
msgid "[Robotswana.L07] Hint 2: Try rewriting with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：哦。这看起来不对。"

#. §0: `E i j`
#. §1: `E i j`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L07_EBasisZeroOffDiag
msgid ""
"intro Robotswana L07: Introduce new consideration for §0: do not consider §1 "
"with i ≠ j"
msgstr ""
"就在树旁边，你又找到一张纸条，上面大大地划掉了 §0。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：大概是说：带 i ≠ j 的 §1 我们不关心。"

#. §0: $$
#. \\begin{aligned}
#. f(A)
#. &= f\\left( \\sum_{i,j} A_{i,j} \\cdot E_{i,j} \\right) \\ %(new line)
#. &= \\sum_{i,j} A_{i,j} \\cdot f(E_{i,j})   \\ %(new line)
#. &= \\sum_{i} A_{i,i} \\cdot f(E_{i,i})
#. \\end{aligned}
#. $$
#. §1: `A`
#. §2: `f`
#. §3: `E i j`
#. §4: `i ≠ j`
#. §5: `A`
#. §6: `f A`
#. §7: `A`
#. §8: `nth_rw 1 [ ... ]`
#. §9: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid ""
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"Write §1 as sum of base matrices. Use linearity to make §2 disappear in §3 "
"with §4.\n"
"Rewrite first §5 in §6 as sum of base matrices, but not the later §7. Try "
"§8\n"
"which works like §9.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"**你**：这又是什么……？\n"
"\n"
"你随手写了几笔。\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"**你**：嗯，这样也许行。我把 §1 写成基矩阵的线性组合，然后用线性性，最后用"
"到：当 §4 时，§2 在 §3 上的值为0。\n"
"所以我大概应该先把 §6 里的第一个 §5 展开成线性组合，而不是右边后面那个 §7。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**（*远处*）：§8！跟 §9 一样用。\n"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L08"
msgstr ""
"**你**：终于！\n"
"\n"
"司南递给你一瓶水。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你这是从哪里变出来的？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：第 17 招。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那你又找到足迹了吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：找到了，跟我来！我刚才在那边看到点东西。"

#. §0: `by_cases`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Employ §0"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 就是那个，没错！"

#. §0: `matrix_eq_sum_ebasis A`
#. §1: `nth_rw 1`
#. §2: `rw`
#. §3: `rw [matrix_eq_sum_ebasis A]`
#. §4: `A`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Explain why to use §0 with §1 instead of §2. §3 replaces both §4"
msgstr ""
"**你**（*喊着*）：你什么意思？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**（*也在喊*）：你肯定是想用 §0，但要用 §1 而不是 §2。§3 会把两个 §4 都"
"替换掉。"

#. §0: `if_neg «{h₂}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Here try §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：……然后这里是 §0。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我知道啦。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Intro Robotswana L08"
msgstr ""
"你们又找到一条线索，但一激动就跟丢了足迹。\n"
"你这会已经很渴了。\n"
"司南在附近继续搜寻时，你累得坐下，在火辣辣的太阳底下有点发懵地盯着那片羊皮纸"
"碎片。"

#. §0: `«{i}» = «{j}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Prove by cases for §0"
msgstr "**你**：然后现在对 §0 做分类讨论……"

#. §0: `f (E i j)`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "See that §0 is zero"
msgstr "**你**：§0 不就是零嘛，我们不是已经知道了吗！"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Simplify"
msgstr "**你**：啊对，拿不准就先化简。"

#. §0: `trans`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Solve second half of §0 operation"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我还以为这就结束了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：差不多了，上面还有 §0 那一步的后半段。这一半特别简单。"

#. §0: `zero_on_offDiag_ebasis`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "This was called §0"
msgstr "**司南**：而那个就叫 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try again"
msgstr "**你**：要不再来一遍？"

#. §0: `apply congr_arg`
#. §1: `ext`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try using §0 and §1"
msgstr "**司南**：和等于求和……可以用 §0、§1 来处理。"

#. §0: `map_sum`
#. §1: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try §0 via §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**（*不知从哪里*）：这听起来像 §0。我不觉得我们在巴比伦见过这个，你是在"
"瞎想。不过 §1 肯定知道这个引理。"

#. §0: `if_pos «{h₂}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try §0."
msgstr "**司南**：这里 §0 很有用。"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `E i j`
#. §2: `i≠j`
#. §3: `trans ∑ i, ∑ j, if i = j then (A i j) * f (E i j) else 0`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Use disappearing §0 in §1 with §2. Try §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你现在做到哪一步了？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我还得想办法用上这个事实：当 §2 时，§0 在 §1 上的值为0。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那不如先做下面这个中间步骤：\n"
"\n"
"§3"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid ""
"[Doc.Theorem] map_sum\n"
"Linear mapping, or 'additive' mappings in general, can be exchanged with a "
"sum."
msgstr "线性映射（或者更一般的“加性”映射）可以移入求和号内。"

#. §0: `IN_HINT 1`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "§0 Use linearity"
msgstr ""
"**你**（*心里想*）：现在用线性性……千万别想水……巴比伦那的水可真不少……我刚才做"
"到哪儿了？"

#. §0: `rw`
#. §1: `nth_rw`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L08_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "§0 is a bad idea here. Try §1."
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，§0 确实是个馊主意。 \n"
"这看起来太复杂了。让我试试 §1。"

#. §0: `«{n}»`
#. §1: $$
#. \\begin{aligned}
#. n \\cdot f(E_{i i})
#. &= \\sum_j f(E_{i i}) \\ %(new line)
#. &= \\sum_j f(E_{j j}) \\ %(new line)
#. &= f(1) \\ %(new line)
#. &= n
#. \\end{aligned}
#. $$
#. §2: `f E i i`
#. §3: `f E j j`
#. §4: `i`
#. §5: `j`
#. §6: `«{n}»`
#. §7: ```
#. suffices h : n * f (E i i) = n * 1
#. ```
#. §8: `mul_eq_mul_left_iff`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid ""
"\n"
"§0-th multiplication of the equation can be calculated with the former "
"results as:\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"Keep in mind that §2 and §3 are equal for arbitrary §4 and §5. Use fact "
"that\n"
"multiplications with §6 are injective. Try\n"
"§7\n"
"and then continue with §8.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"你想了一会儿，在纸上乱涂乱画。 \n"
"过了一阵：\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我有个主意！方程的 §0 倍我可以用之前的结果这样计算： \n"
"§1\n"
"关键点是，我们已经知道，对任意的 §4 和 §5，§2 和 §3 是相等的。所以在求和里它"
"们可以互换。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：嗯嗯。总之你是想先利用“乘以 §6 是单射”这件事？我们以前是不是有个引"
"理来着？嗯 …\n"
"司南想了一会儿。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我会先这么试：\n"
"§7\n"
"然后再用 §8 继续。\n"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L09"
msgstr "**你**：好。我们小心点靠近。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Intro Robotswana L09"
msgstr ""
"再往前不到五十米，你们来到一个小土坡上。司南指着远处的一个点。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：看，它就在那儿！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那*是*什么？？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不知道。但我感觉这些纸条像是在给它做某种“档案”……你看，这里还有一"
"张。我觉得这张是在说它有多大。"

#. §0: `«{h}» : «{n}» = 0`
#. §1: `obtain «{h}» | «{h}» := «{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Observe §0 seperatly. Prove by cases with §1"
msgstr "**司南**：啊对，§0 这个情况我们得单独处理。那就用 §1 来分类讨论吧"

#. §0: `«{h}» : «{n}» = 0`
#. §1: `«{i}» : Fin «{n}»`
#. §2: `«{i}»`
#. §3: `Fin 0`
#. §4: `simp [«{h}»] at «{i}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Put §0 into §1 to show triviality because there is no §2 in §3. Try §4"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：然后你大概想把 §0 代入 §1，这样就能发现这个命题是平凡的，因为在 §3 "
"里根本不存在 §2。这里可以用 §4 来做这个代入。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Return to topic at hand"
msgstr "**司南**：行吧。那现在回到正题。"

#. §0: `«{f}» (∑ x, E x x)`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Show statement via §0"
msgstr "**你**：然后我想通过中间等式 §0 来证明这个等式。"

#. §0: `rw [«{h₂}»]`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try out using §0"
msgstr "**司南**：试试 §0。"

#. §0: `simp [E]`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：这次你直接再用 §0 就行。"

#. §0: `trans`
#. §1: `trans ∑ j : Fin «{n}», f (E i i)`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try §0 several times. Start with §1"
msgstr "**司南**：如果我没理解错的话，你现在想多次使用 §0，第一步是 §1。"

#. §0: `IsEmpty.false`
#. §1: `M`
#. §2: `∀ (m : M), False`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Try §0. It states for the empty set §1 that §2"
msgstr "**司南**：接下来可能会用到的引理是 §0，它说明：对空集 §1，有 §2。"

#. §0: `eq_sum_apply_diag_ebasis`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "Use the result §0"
msgstr "**司南**：你刚才想用的那个结果叫 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "[Hint dkmw] Remind of previous result"
msgstr "**你**：这个我们之前在路上已经见过了。"

#. §0: `eq_on_diag_ebasis`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "[Hint fzwc] Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我的硬盘记录这一条是 §0。"

#. §0: `trans «{f}» (∑ j : Fin «{n}», E «{i}» «{i}»)`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "[Hint yvqm] Try §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：哦，这可不是你刚才记下来的那个。不过也许也能行。下一步试试 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "[Hint ztqn] Remind of previous result"
msgstr "**司南**：这个我们已经见过了。"

#. §0: `apply congr_arg`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "[Robotswana.L09] Hint 1: §0 is mathematically wrong"
msgstr "**你**：不对，这在数学上就是错的！"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "[Robotswana.L09] Hint: pull function into sum 1"
msgstr "**你**：接下来我们把函数移进求和里。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "[Robotswana.L09] Hint: pull function into sum 2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：又来 `congr`-`ext`？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：不，得先把函数移进求和里，不然不行。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "again"
msgstr "**你**：再来！"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `ℕ`
#. §2: `ℝ`
#. §3: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L09_EvalOnEBasis
msgid "§0 is an implicid embedding of  §1 in §2.  Try §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：箭头 §0 是从 §1 到 §2 的一个隐式嵌入。比如你可以用 §3 消掉它。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L10"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：确实。你说得对。\n"
"\n"
"你们满心欢喜地观察着这个显然是这颗星球上独一无二的生物。\n"
"\n"
"你们走近时，特蕾西似乎注意到了你们。但她似乎完全不受你们打扰。"

#. §0: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Explain that each §0 has stated properties"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这里再把所有性质汇总一遍。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也就是说，你觉得特蕾西有这些性质？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：对。我觉得就是这样。任何具有这些性质的映射 §0，在所有矩阵上的表现都和"
"特蕾西一模一样。所以它*就是*特蕾西！"

#. §0: `trace`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Intro Robotswana L10: Introduce §0"
msgstr ""
"你们慢慢地潜行靠近。\n"
"\n"
"**你**（**低声**）：我觉得你说得对。这些纸条像是一份档案！而且它们把眼前这个"
"家伙描述得明明白白！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你什么意思？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你看嘛，它的大小、它对交换子的偏爱，还有其他那些特征——靠这些就能把它"
"唯一确定出来！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这你得跟我讲清楚点。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我试试。在Lean语里，“迹”有名字吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：当然有，就叫 §0。有些形式哲学家还亲切地叫它特蕾西。\n"
"\n"
"你拿起一片羊皮纸碎片，在背面写了起来。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Observe equality"
msgstr "**司南**：按定义两边就是相等的！"

#. §0: `f (E i i) = 1`
#. §1: `one_on_diag_ebasis`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Remind former result for §0. Try §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我们刚才不是已经确定 §0 成立了吗！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：查资料我最在行！那是 §1。"

#. §0: `rw [eq_sum_apply_diag_ebasis]`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Remind missed argument with §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这个证明目标是从哪儿来的？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：最开始你用 §0 的时候，大概漏掉了这个参数。现在可以补上。"

#. §0: `f «{A}»`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Rewrite §0 as sum of basis elements"
msgstr "**你**：然后我们把 §0 写成基元素的和。"

#. §0: `ext`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L10_Characterize
msgid "Use §0!"
msgstr "**司南**：§0!"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L11_Linearity
msgid "Conclusion Robotswana L11"
msgstr ""
"最后你们动身踏上返程。\n"
"你们立刻就迷路了，但特蕾西显然跟了上来，带着你们穿过草原，回到你们的飞船。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L11_Linearity
msgid "Explain statement"
msgstr "**你**：这显然是在讲矩阵迹的线性性。"

#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L11_Linearity
msgid "Intro Robotswana L11"
msgstr ""
"你们隔着一点距离停下时，特蕾西朝你们跑过来，开始玩耍。\n"
"她兴致勃勃地抛给你们各种各样的问题和项，你们则试着尽快把它们组合起来。"

#. §0: `card_fin`
#. §1: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Robotswana.L11_Linearity
msgid "[Hint xnqr] Try §0 | §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：最后这一步可以用 §0。当然，其实也可以全都用 §1 来做，不过我开始喜欢"
"一步一步做了。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand
msgid "Intro Samarkand"
msgstr ""
"远处出现了一颗色彩斑斓的行星。等你们靠近了，才发现它表面的大部分区域都装饰着"
"精致的几何图案。不过也有一些没装饰的地方，纯白一片。你们就在其中一块白色斑点"
"上着陆。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"**你**：哈喽，这里有人吗？\n"
"\n"
"行星表面像一颗完美的球体。你们朝各个方向望去都是地平线。一个人影也没有。你们"
"正想转身离开，却发现了什么。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：司南，你看那边，那个星球有个鼓包！\n"
"\n"
"结果发现，这个“鼓包”是一只小乌龟，它躺在图案边缘附近的彩色地面上。你们小心翼"
"翼地踏上有图案的区域。颜料看起来已经干了。\n"
"\n"
"**阿拉普卡**：你们好呀，过来吧！真好，我也能有访客了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你在这儿干什么呢，一个人孤零零的？\n"
"\n"
"**阿拉普卡**：我在做一件大型艺术品。我会一直躺在这里，直到我的腹甲把地面的图"
"案“印”上去。然后我就爬到那块还缺这一段图案的地方，再躺在那里很久，把图案转印"
"到白色的行星表面上。这很花时间。所以我很需要有人陪我聊聊天。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那敢情好。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand
msgid "Samarkand"
msgstr "撒马尔罕"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L01_ImagePreimage
msgid "Conclusion Samarkand L01"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：不错。"

#. §0: `intro b`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L01_ImagePreimage
msgid "Explain inclusion. Try §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：要证明一个包含关系，你从左边集合任取一个元素，然后证明它属于右边集"
"合。所以先从 §0 开始吧。"

#. §0: `f : A → B`
#. §1: `S`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: ```
#. f '' S = {f a | a ∈ S}
#. = {b | ∃ a ∈ S, f a = b}
#. ```
#. §4: `f`
#. §5: `T`
#. §6: `B`
#. §7: ```
#. f ⁻¹' T = { a | f a ∈ T}
#. ```
#. §8: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L01_ImagePreimage
msgid ""
"Explain statement: given §0 for subset §1 of §2\n"
"§3\n"
"is the image over §4. For subset §5 of §6\n"
"§7\n"
"is the pre-image over §8,\n"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我觉得我得给你解释一下这里的符号。\n"
"这里明确给定了一个映射 §0。\n"
"对 §2 的一个子集 §1 而言，\n"
"§3\n"
"是它在 §4 下的像。\n"
"而对 §6 的一个子集 §5 而言，\n"
"§7\n"
"是它在 §8 下的原像。\n"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L01_ImagePreimage
msgid "Intro Samarkand L01"
msgstr ""
"**阿拉普卡**：还有一些事情我已经想了很久了。也许你们能帮帮我。比如说：……\n"
"\n"
"她给你们口述了一条命题。司南把它写了下来。"

#. §0: `«{hb}»`
#. §1: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L01_ImagePreimage
msgid "Transform §0 by using §1"
msgstr "**司南**：要把假设 §0 变成更基础的表达式，你可以用一下 §1。"

#. §0: `image`
#. §1: `''`
#. §2: `image f`
#. §3: `A`
#. §4: `B`
#. §5: ```
#. image f = fun S ↦ f '' S
#. ```
#. §6: `image f`
#. §7: `f ''`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L02_ImageMap
msgid ""
"Can not use §0 instead of §1.\n"
"Explain that §2 is mapping from §3 to §4 i.e.\n"
"§5\n"
".You can express §6 by §7 but not vica versa"
msgstr ""
"**你**：啊哈！所以如果我不喜欢 §1 这种“蝇点”一样的小符号，也可以直接写 §0？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不行，不能这么写。你仔细看就会发现，这里的 §2 是一个映射。\n"
"它的输入是集合 §3 的一个子集，输出是集合 §4 中对应的像集，也就是\n"
"§5"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L02_ImageMap
msgid "Conclusions Samarkand L02"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：好看，好看。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L02_ImageMap
msgid "Intro Samarkand L02"
msgstr "阿拉普卡又给你们口述了一道问题。"

#. §0: `funext`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L02_ImageMap
msgid "Remind §0"
msgstr "**司南**：这里要证明两个映射相等。你还记得 §0 吗？"

#. §0: `ext`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L02_ImageMap
msgid "Show equality of sets by §0"
msgstr "**司南**：现在要证明两个集合相等——别忘了那个关键词：§0。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L02_ImageMap
msgid "This can be simplified"
msgstr "**司南**：这个肯定可以很容易化简……"

#. §0: `funext S`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L02_ImageMap
msgid "[Hint gwrm] Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：哦，不。看起来太复杂了。你还是把 §0 明写出来吧。"

#. §0: `ext`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L03_SurjectiveRange
msgid "Again show equality of sets by using §0"
msgstr "**司南**：这不又是要证明集合相等吗？那就用 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L03_SurjectiveRange
msgid "Conclusion Samarkand L03"
msgstr ""
"**阿拉普卡**：也挺好。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你该不会把整个星球都画满了吧？\n"
"\n"
"**阿拉普卡**：没有。这是几代人的问题。最早的图案元素是我曾曾曾曾……祖父定下来"
"的。我都不太确定要往回数多少代。更别说最初的原始图案是从哪来的。"

#. §0: `range f`
#. §1: `f`
#. §2: ```
#. range f = {f a | a : A}
#. = {  b | ∃ a, f a = b}
#. ```
#. §3: `f '' univ`
#. §4: `mem_range`
#. §5: ```
#. x ∈ range f ↔ ∃ a, f a = b
#. ```
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L03_SurjectiveRange
msgid ""
"Explain §0 w.r.t. §1 as\n"
"§2\n"
"and its equivalent §3. Mention §4:\n"
"§5\n"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这里的 §0 是 §1 的整个像集：\n"
"§2\n"
"所以这本质上只是 §3 的另一种写法。\n"
"要处理这个记号，§4 很有用：\n"
"§5\n"

#. §0: `constructor`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L03_SurjectiveRange
msgid "Try to start with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我会先从 §0 开始。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L04_SurjectiveImagePreimage
msgid "Conclusion Samarkand L04"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：你们真是帮了大忙！"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L04_SurjectiveImagePreimage
msgid "Intro Samarkand L04"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：你们或许也能帮我看看这个吗？"

#. §0: `image_preimage_subset`
#. §1: ```
#. f '' (f ⁻¹' T) ⊆ T
#. ```
#. §2: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L04_SurjectiveImagePreimage
msgid ""
"Remind §0 i.e.\n"
"§1\n"
"and additional assumption that §2 surjectiv"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我们刚才不是已经有过这个了吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没有。刚才我们只有包含关系 §0：\n"
"§1\n"
"现在要证明的是相等，这里的已知条件是映射 §2 是满射。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L05_InjectiveFibre
msgid "Conclusion Samarkand L05"
msgstr "阿拉普卡还是一动不动地躺着，不过她看起来很开心。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L05_InjectiveFibre
msgid "Intro Samarkand L05"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：我还有一个关于单射映射的问题。"

#. §0: `∃! a`
#. §1: `a`
#. §2: `use a`
#. §3: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L05_InjectiveFibre
msgid "Try §0 to construct §1, Try §2 and §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：对于 §0，我先构造出我想用的元素 §1……\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：……然后你用 §2 和 §3。没错。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L06_PreimageNonempty
msgid "Conclusion Samarkand L06"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：你们说得对。我自己也该想到的。"

#. §0: `b`
#. §1: `b`
#. §2: `eq_empty_iff_forall_notMem`
#. §3: `unfold Ne`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L06_PreimageNonempty
msgid ""
"Explain that §0 is not empty iff §1 has pre-image. Remind of §2 that can be "
"used after §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：这大概是说：§0 的纤维非空，当且仅当 §1 有一个原像。又是相当显然。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，除了记号问题。不过幸好我们已经证明了 §2。要用它，你只需要把不等"
"号展开，比如直接用 §3。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L06_PreimageNonempty
msgid "Intro Samarkand L06"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：那这个呢？"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L07_LeftInvPreimage
msgid "Conclusion Samarkand L07"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：哇！你们真的太厉害了。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L07_LeftInvPreimage
msgid "Got to think about it..."
msgstr "**你**：让我想想……"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L07_LeftInvPreimage
msgid "Intro Samarkand L07"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：不过我现在还有一道真的很难的问题。"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L08_Preimage_Injective
msgid "Conlsuion Samarkand L08"
msgstr ""
"**阿拉普卡**：太棒了！我激动得简直想跳起来。但那当然不行。那样图案就乱了。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你还要这样待多久？\n"
"\n"
"**阿拉普卡**：我还要在这里待三年、22天、7小时和35分钟。\n"
"\n"
"：\n"
"**司南**：哦哦……\n"
"\n"
"**你**:那你怎么知道之后要去哪里，才能让图案对得上？\n"
"\n"
"**阿拉普卡**：啊！\n"
"\n"
"阿拉普卡的脸上绽开了一个大大的笑容。\n"
"\n"
"**阿拉普卡**：这就是艺术啦！"

#. §0: `preimage f`
#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L08_Preimage_Injective
msgid "Explain surcetivity by §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：一个映射是满射，当且仅当由它诱导出的取原像映射 §0 是单射。这个映射"
"会返回一个子集在原映射下的原像。真是这样吗？\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我觉得对。我以前见过。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那就走起！"

#: Game.Levels.Samarkand.L08_Preimage_Injective
msgid "Intro Samarkand L08"
msgstr "**阿拉普卡**：那你们能不能也帮我看看这个猜想呢？"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn
msgid "Intro Saturn"
msgstr ""
"你们本来根本没打算飞向这颗星球。但你们有点走神了。而在宇宙里可不能心不在焉，"
"尤其是你还不熟悉这个宇宙的时候。现在你们已经飞得太近了，引力太强，而你们的再"
"生引擎正处在再生模式。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：这颗星球上的橙色酱汁是什么鬼？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：看起来像是有毒。或者很烫。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：或者两者都有。我真的不想在那儿降落！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我也不想，我已经在尽力了。你看，这里已经有多少垃圾在绕着星球转了！"
"我们现在能做的最好的事，就是顺着这股流飞。"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn
msgid "Saturn"
msgstr "土星"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L01_Rewrite_equality
msgid "Conclusion Saturn L01"
msgstr "你们收到了一个 👍。"

#. §0: `=`
#. §1: `↔`
#. §2: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L01_Rewrite_equality
msgid "Explain that §0 and §1 with §2 can be used as in Implis"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我感觉这个之前见过。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对！这看起来很像我们在 *蕴涵* 上已经做过的一道问题。只不过这里写的"
"是数的等式，而不是“当且仅当”的陈述！但本质上没啥区别。你几乎可以把 §0 和 §1 "
"跟 §2 一样来用。"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L01_Rewrite_equality
msgid "Intro Saturn L01"
msgstr "突然，你们收到一条无线电消息。"

#. §0: `←`
#. §1: `\\l`
#. §2: `rw [← hₓ]`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L01_Rewrite_equality
msgid "Remind of rewrite via §0 as §1. Try §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：反方向改写，是怎么写的来着？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§2，其中 §0 写作 §1。"

#. §0: `rw [hₓ]`
#. §1: `rw [← hₓ]`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L01_Rewrite_equality
msgid "Try if §0 and §1 can be used as in Implis"
msgstr ""
"**你**：所以这里我也可以用 §0 和 §1？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：你试试看？"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L02_Ring_add_pow_two
msgid "Conclusion Saturn L02: §0 could have been used as well"
msgstr ""
"你们收到了一个👍。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不过你其实也可以直接用 §0。"

#. §0: `binomi`
#. §1: `add_pow_two`
#. §2: `rw [add_pow_two]`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L02_Ring_add_pow_two
msgid "Explain misfit of §0. Try §1 via §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：我们这是进了匿名中学数学家互助会吗？这不就是把各项重新排列一下直接算"
"出来嘛。要不我们回复 §0？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不，这个宇宙里这个等式当然叫 §1，因为在公式里先出现“+”，然后才"
"是“^2”。所以你可以用 §2。之后左边就会和右边一模一样，你就搞定了。"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L02_Ring_add_pow_two
msgid "Intro Saturn L02"
msgstr "下一条无线电消息看起来有点不一样。"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L03_mul_comm
msgid "Conclusion Saturn L03"
msgstr "又一个👍。"

#. §0: `P`
#. §1: `P`
#. §2: `Fin 2`
#. §3: `ℚ`
#. §4: `Fin 2`
#. §5: $\\{0,1\\}$
#. §6: `X 0`
#. §7: `X 1`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L03_mul_comm
msgid ""
"Explain §0: §1 is a 'multivariate polynome' with variables indexed by §2 "
"and\n"
"coefficients in §3.\n"
"Explain §4 as the set of elements §5 that lead to the variables §6 and §7"
msgstr ""
"**你**：咦，§0 在这里到底是个什么怪东西？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1 是一个“多元多项式”，变量依次用 §2 编号，系数在 §3 里。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那 §4 是啥？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：带两个元素的标准集合——§5。所以变量就叫 §6 和 §7。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：不过其实这些都无所谓吧？多项式环不是交换的吗！\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错。"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L03_mul_comm
msgid "Intro Saturn L03"
msgstr "又一条无线电消息。"

#. §0: `ℕ`
#. §1: `ℕ`
#. §2: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L04_mul_assoc
msgid ""
"Conclusion Saturn L04: coefficients were in §0. Polynomes with coefficients "
"in §1\n"
"are not considered rings. §2 does also work on half rings."
msgstr ""
"又一个👍。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：但等等，这次系数不是在§0里吗！这根本不是个环，而且系数在 §1 里的多项"
"式也不构成环。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：也许吧。 但 §2 甚至对所谓的半环也管用。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：哦哦……\n"
"\n"
"那位匿名者想通过无线电问问你们：是准备好进入最终挑战了，还是更想再绕他的星球"
"转几圈。\n"
"\n"
"“准备好了。”司南用无线电回道。"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L04_mul_assoc
msgid "Intro Saturn L04"
msgstr "又一条无线电消息。"

#. §0: `mul_assoc`
#. §1: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L04_mul_assoc
msgid "Try §0 or again §1"
msgstr "**司南**：这里你可以用 §0。或者*再次*用 §1……"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L05_Ring
msgid "Conclusion Saturn L05"
msgstr ""
"“通过了”，匿名电台员就这么简短地回了一句。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：我觉得推进器现在已经恢复得差不多了。赶紧溜！"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza
msgid "Intro Spinoza"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我觉得那是斯宾诺莎，一颗极少见的 QED 型小行星。快点，我们得稍微赶一"
"赶，不然就错过它了。\n"
"\n"
"半小时后你们着陆了。斯宾诺莎看起来不太宜居。它的整个表面都覆盖着细细的红色沙"
"粒。一个孤零零的形式哲学家在等你们，他自我介绍说叫本尼迪克特。\n"
"\n"
"**本尼迪克特**：很高兴你们来了！我已经等你们很久了！\n"
"\n"
"**你**：你也有几个很紧急的问题……？\n"
"\n"
"**本尼迪克特**：哎呀不，我早过了那个年纪。不过我能想象你们在蕴涵和量词上过得"
"怎么样。相信我，在其他行星上也不会好多少。但我也许能给你们做点准备。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：我们就不能干脆留在这儿，稍微休息一下吗？\n"
"\n"
"本尼迪克特摇了摇头。\n"
"\n"
"**本尼迪克特**：不行。斯宾诺莎容不下三个居民。而且你们很快就得继续走，不然路"
"就太远了。我们每 400 年才会路过这些行星一次。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza
msgid "Spinoza"
msgstr "斯宾诺莎"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L01_Have
msgid "Conclusion Spinoza L01"
msgstr "**本尼迪克特**：看起来不错！"

#. §0: `contradiction`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L01_Have
msgid "If to assumptions contradict each other use §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：两条假设互相矛盾的时候，该怎么做来着？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§0。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L01_Have
msgid "Intro Spinoza L01"
msgstr "**本尼迪克特**：来，你们看。这是我为你们准备的。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L01_Have
msgid "Prove the assumption before using it"
msgstr ""
"**你**：啥？我现在就直接假设它是对的了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不，你当然得先把它证明出来，然后才能拿来用。"

#. §0: `∧`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L01_Have
msgid "Try to split §0"
msgstr "**你**：那我先把这个“与”（§0）拆开吧。"

#. §0: `have`
#. §1: `have g : ¬ B`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L01_Have
msgid "Try §0 in form of §1"
msgstr ""
"**你**：然后……\n"
"\n"
"**本尼迪克特**：……你应该先准备一个合适的中间结果。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对！再试试 §0 吧。更准确地说：§1！"

#. §0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L01_Have
msgid "§0 should help"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 应该能帮上忙。"

#. §0: `have`
#. §1: `suffices`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L02_Suffices
msgid ""
"Conclusion Spinoza L02: The use of §0 or §1 is up to personal preference."
msgstr ""
"**本尼迪克特**：我就是这个意思。你们以后用 §0 还是 §1，纯属个人偏好。关键是，"
"你们得知道怎样通过一个个小步骤，逐渐完成遥远的目标。"

#. §0: `«{g}»`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L02_Suffices
msgid "End proof with assumption that §0 is true"
msgstr "**司南**：所以在这里，你要在假设 §0 为真的前提下完成证明。"

#. §0: `have`
#. §1: `suffices`
#. §2: `suffices g : ¬B`
#. §3: `g`
#. §4: `g`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L02_Suffices
msgid ""
"Instead of §0, §1 can be used. After §2, you have to show how to\n"
"prove goal by §3 before proving §4 itself."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我懂他什么意思了！除了 §0，你也可以用 §1。效果完全一样，只不过两个"
"目标的顺序对调了。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以写下 §2 后，我得先说明如何用 §3 完成证明，然后再证明 §4？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错！"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L02_Suffices
msgid "Intro Spinoza L02"
msgstr ""
"**本尼迪克特**：你们当然也可以先证明主结果，再证明中间结果。这道题和刚才那道"
"很相似，你们可以试试这种做法。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L02_Suffices
msgid "Prove intermediate result"
msgstr "**司南**：然后你在这里证明这个中间结果。"

#. §0: `«{h}» : «{A}»`
#. §1: `suffices`
#. §2: `suffices k : B`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L03_ByContra
msgid "Apply contradiction with §0 via §1 with §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在你有了一个假设 §0，然后你得从中推出一个矛盾。\n"
"\n"
"你可以用 §1 指定想要推出的矛盾，比如 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L03_ByContra
msgid "Conclusion Spinoza L03"
msgstr "**本尼迪克特**：我看出来了，你们学得真快！"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L03_ByContra
msgid "Derive intermediate result that lead to the conclusion"
msgstr "**司南**：现在你只需要推出那个产生矛盾的中间结果就行了。"

#. §0: `¬`
#. §1: `contradiction`
#. §2: `by_contra h`
#. §3: `contradiction`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L03_ByContra
msgid ""
"Explain §0 in goal. Perform proof by §1 by stating with §2 and\n"
"concluding with §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：Goal 里出现一个 §0，通常意味着你想使用反证法。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我怎么做？用 §1 吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：用 §2 开始反证法。然后用 §3 收尾。"

#. §0: `«{B}»`
#. §1: `¬«{B}»`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L03_ByContra
msgid "Finish proof by stating contradiction between §0 and §1"
msgstr "**你**：啊，那我现在就可以直接说，假设 §0 和 §1 互相矛盾。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L03_ByContra
msgid "Intro Spinoza L03"
msgstr "**本尼迪克特**：这里还有一种变体。"

#. §0: `not_imp_not`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L04_ByContra
msgid "Intro Spinoza L04: introduce contraposition equivalence with §0"
msgstr ""
"**本尼迪克特**：我还有一道关于奇数平方的好问题要给你们。不过在那之前，你们最"
"好先证明这里这个等价。我觉得你们甚至给它起了个名字：*逆否等价*，之类的。在"
"Lean语里，我们就把这个等价直接叫 §0。是不是更一目了然？"

#. §0: $A ⇒ B$
#. §1: $¬B ⇒ ¬A$
#. §2: `not_imp_not`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L04_ByContra
msgid "Often to prove §0, §1 can be proven as well. Here this is called §2."
msgstr ""
"**你**：嗯，这个我确实以前见过。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对啊，你当然见过。数学家不是老这么干嘛。要是他们对 §0 没思路，就改"
"去证明 §1。我倒是觉得这与其叫*逆否命题*，不如叫*绕个大圈反着来*。不过在这里它"
"当然叫 §2。"

#. §0: `suffices g : B`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L04_ByContra
msgid "Provoce contradiction by using §0"
msgstr "**司南**：我会再用 §0 来导出一个矛盾。"

#. §0: `constructor`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L04_ByContra
msgid "Start trying with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：先从 §0 开始吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L04_ByContra
msgid "Use proof by contradiction"
msgstr "**司南**：我觉得这里也该从反证法开始。"

#. §0: `suffices g : ¬ A`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L04_ByContra
msgid "§0 would be a good option"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 看起来是个不错的选择。"

#. §0: `contrapose`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L05_Contrapose
msgid "Apply contraposition lemma simply by §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：那现在我可以用这个逆否引理吗？它叫啥来着？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：其实你也可以直接写 §0。"

#. §0: `even_square`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L05_Contrapose
msgid "Apply lemma §0"
msgstr "**你**：这看起来已经很不错了。现在我终于可以用之前那个引理 §0 了！"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L05_Contrapose
msgid "Conclusion Spinoza L05"
msgstr "**本尼迪克特**：太棒了！我觉得你们现在已经挺有底气了。"

#. §0: `by_contra`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L05_Contrapose
msgid "Intro Spinoza L05. prove without §0"
msgstr ""
"**本尼迪克特**：好，这就是我刚才说的问题。试着做一个*直接*证明，不用 §0。"

#. §0: `even_square`
#. §1: `Odd (n^2) → Odd n`
#. §2: `Even n → Even (n^2)`
#. §3: `→`
#. §4: `revert`
#. §5: `revert «{h}»`
#. §6: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L05_Contrapose
msgid ""
"Refer back to §0 as §1 is equivalent in contrapoition to §2.\n"
"Explain that lack of  §3 can be dealt with §4 via §5 for §6."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：我建议把它归结到我们在量词上已经证明过的引理 §0。这里基本上写的就"
"是 §1。而在逆否命题之下，这等价于 §2。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：对。从后面绕到前面来……不过等等，现在那儿根本没有 §3 啊。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：记得 §4 吗？用 §5 你可以把假设 §6 移到目标中，作为蕴涵的前提。"

#. §0: `not_odd_iff_even`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L05_Contrapose
msgid "§0 might help here"
msgstr "**司南**：也许现在 §0 能帮上忙？"

#. §0: `suffices d : ¬ Odd (n ^ 2)`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L06_Summary
msgid "Conclude with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：那就 §0。"

#. §0: `have`
#. §1: `suffices`
#. §2: `by_contra`
#. §3: `contradiction`
#. §4: `contrapose`
#. §5: `revert`
#. §6: `contrapose`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L06_Summary
msgid ""
"Conclusion Spinoza L06: overview of planet's contents:\n"
"§0, §1, §2, §3, §4, §5 (useful when applying\n"
"§6 afterwards)."
msgstr ""
"**司南**：太棒了！下面是本尼迪克特教给我们的内容概览。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"| **策略**      | **用途**                                              |\n"
"|:----------------|:-------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| §0              |  引入并证明一个中间结"
"论                                     |\n"
"| §1              |  先假设一个中间结论足以完成目标，再证明这个中间结"
"论                                     |\n"
"| §2              |  开始反证法                                       |\n"
"| §3              |  从已知矛盾中完成证"
"明                                       |\n"
"| §4              |  将目标转化为逆否命"
"题                                             |\n"
"| §5              |  将假设移回目标，以便之后使用 "
"§6                                |\n"
" "

#. §0: `Odd (n ^ 2)`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L06_Summary
msgid "Derive contradiction for §0"
msgstr "**司南**：现在我会导出一个与 §0 矛盾的结论。"

#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L06_Summary
msgid "Intro Spinoza L06"
msgstr ""
"**你**：但上一道问题，我们不也完全可以用反证法来证明吗？\n"
"\n"
"**本尼迪克特**：当然可以。我只是觉得再来一个反证法会很无聊。不过你们也可以再"
"试一次这道问题。来，我把它交给你们带在路上做。不过现在，你们该赶紧出发！"

#. §0: `by_contra g`
#: Game.Levels.Spinoza.L06_Summary
msgid "This time start with §0"
msgstr ""
"安全脱离了小行星的引力场后，你们又开始研究手头的问题。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：好，那这次我们从 §0 开始！"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta
msgid "Intro Vieta"
msgstr ""
"喂，有人吗？你们降落在一片荒原上。放眼望去，一个人影都没有。\n"
"\n"
"突然，一支箭嗖地一下从你头顶正上方掠过。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：找掩护！\n"
"\n"
"你们立刻趴倒在地。你们正想爬回飞船，这时一个男人从一棵枯死的树后走了出来，友"
"好地向你们挥手。于是你们就朝他爬了过去。\n"
"\n"
"**韦达**：别这么害羞嘛，两位！我叫韦达。欢迎！放心站起来吧，现在安全得很。\n"
"\n"
"你们小心翼翼地站起身来，结果又有一支箭嗖地一下从你们身边擦过。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：您在这儿怎么待得下去？\n"
"\n"
"**韦达**：嗯，我学会了总在正确的时间站在正确的地方。别担心。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta
msgid "Vieta"
msgstr "韦达"

#. §0: `→`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L01_FunctionNotation
msgid "Conclusion Vieta L01: explain ambiguity of §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：话说，§0 刚才不还是个蕴涵吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，没错。在这里，映射和蕴涵用的是同一个符号。"

#. §0: `f`
#. §1: `ℤ`
#. §2: `ℕ`
#. §3: `f n`
#. §4: $f(n)$
#. §5: `f (n)`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L01_FunctionNotation
msgid ""
"Explain §0 as mapping from §1 to §2:\n"
"§3 is notation for §4. If you want to use brackets it has to be §5.\n"
msgstr ""
"**你**：看起来 §0 是一个从 §1 到 §2 的映射。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对，正是这样。§3 是 §4 的记号。不过在Lean语里通常会把括号省掉。要是"
"你想加括号，就一定要在括号前面加空格——像这样：§5。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：好的，我记住了。不过既然这个映射在这里只取 ℕ 里的值，那其实也没什么要"
"证明的吧。\n"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L01_FunctionNotation
msgid "Intro Vieta L01"
msgstr ""
"**韦达**：来，我给你们看点东西……\n"
"\n"
"他递给你一张纸。"

#. §0: `fun (x : ℤ) ↦ x ^ 2`
#. §1: $x↦x^2$
#. §2: `f : ℤ → ℤ := …`
#. §3: $$
#. \\begin{aligned}
#. f\\colon \\mathbb{ℤ} &\\to \\mathbb{ℤ} \\ %(new line)
#. x &\\mapsto x ^ 2
#. \\end{aligned}
#. $$
#. §4: $2^2=4$
#. §5: `rfl`
#. §6: `simp [«{f}»]`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L02_Function
msgid ""
"Explain anonymous function §0 as mapping §1.\n"
"Only §2 the anon. function would receive a name. The goal is for\n"
"§3\n"
"to show that §4.\n"
"You can try §5 or §6\n"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：啊哈，这就更有意思了。这里的 §0 是一个“匿名函数”，也就是映射 §1。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那它哪里匿名了？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：就是说它一开始没有名字。只有通过 §2，它才得到一个名字。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：哦——所以总体来说，我们有下面这个映射，对吧？\n"
"\n"
"§3\n"
"\n"
"所以我要证明 §4？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我这里怎么做？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：Lean 能看穿大多数映射规则，所以这里用 §5 应该就够了。或者你也可以"
"用 §6 显式代入定义。\n"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L02_Function
msgid "Intro Vieta L02"
msgstr ""
"又有一支箭嗖地飞过。\n"
"但韦达还是若无其事地把下一张纸递给你们。"

#. §0: `«{f}»`
#. §1: `use`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L03_Let
msgid "If §0 correctly defind try §1"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：如果你构造出来的 §0 是正确的，就可以用 §1 把它用上，剩下的不等式证"
"明应该很简单。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L03_Let
msgid "Intro Vieta L03"
msgstr "又飞来一支箭。又来了一道题。"

#. §0: `∃`
#. §1: `use …`
#. §2: `let f : ℤ → ℤ := fun …`
#. §3: `↦`
#. §4: `\\maps`
#. §5: `\\mapsto`
#. §6: `=>`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L03_Let
msgid ""
"Tackle  §0 either with §1 or define mapping §2 as before.\n"
"Remind that §3 is either §4 or §5 ro can be replyced by §6"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：跟往常一样，你可以用 §1 来处理 §0。或者你也可以先用 §2 定义一个你想"
"用的映射，就像你刚刚看到的那样。顺便说一下，箭头 §3 你写成 §4 或 §5 都行。不"
"过你也可以用 §6 代替。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L03_Let
msgid "Try simplification"
msgstr "**你**：这到底会化简成什么呢？"

#. §0: `g ∘ «{f}»`
#. §1: `\\comp`
#. §2: `let g : ℤ → ℤ := fun x ↦ _`
#. §3: `use fun (x : ℤ) ↦ _`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L04_Let
msgid "Composition §0 can be written with §1. Try §2 or §3"
msgstr ""
"**你**：§0 是映射的复合吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错！可以用 §1 来写。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：那我在这里就又可以用 §2 定义一个映射？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对。或者你也可以直接写 §3。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L04_Let
msgid "Intro Vieta L04"
msgstr ""
"**韦达**：现在我们得往这边挪一小段。\n"
"\n"
"他小心地把你们往旁边推了几米。片刻之后，就在你们刚才站的地方，三支箭落了下"
"来，插在地上。\n"
"\n"
"**韦达**：别紧张，我对这里很熟悉。来，我还有更多问题给你们。"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `«{f}»`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L04_Let
msgid "Try §0 as it sees through defintion §1"
msgstr "**司南**：§0 能看穿像 §1 这样的局部定义，所以你可以直接用它。"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `«{f}»`
#. §2: `«{g}»`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L04_Let
msgid "Try §0, as it sees through definitions §1 and §2"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：§0 能看穿像 §1 和 §2 这样的局部定义。\n"
"所以你可以直接用这个策略。"

#. §0: `(g ∘ «{f}») x`
#. §1: `g («{f}» x)`
#. §2: `simp`
#. §3: `rw [comp_apply]`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L04_Let
msgid "[Hint bpwn] Explain §0 defined as §1. Try §2 | §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：按定义，§0 就是 §1。§2 也知道这个引理，不过这里你就直接用 §3 来做"
"吧。"

#. §0: `use «{g}»`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L04_Let
msgid "[Hint bsjn] Try §0"
msgstr "**司南**：现在你可以用 §0 把它用上。"

#. §0: `(«{g}» ∘ «{f}») x`
#. §1: `«{g}» («{f}» x)`
#. §2: `simp`
#. §3: `rw [comp_apply]`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L04_Let
msgid "[Hint kzmq] Explain §0 defined as §1. Try §2 | §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：按定义，§0 就是 §1。§2 也知道这个引理，不过这里你就直接用 §3 来做"
"吧。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L05_Funext
msgid "Intro Vieta L05"
msgstr ""
"韦达小心翼翼地环顾四周，但最后还是站在原地。\n"
"他镇定地把下一张纸递给你们。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L05_Funext
msgid "Remind: §0 sees through local definitions"
msgstr "**司南**：提醒一下，§0 能看穿局部定义。"

# GPT: „Abbildungen“ kann je nach Kontext auch als „Funktionen“ übersetzt werden; wegen des Glossars und des mathematischen Kontexts habe ich mich für „映射“ entschieden. Außerdem habe ich das Auslassungszeichen als Unicode-„…. “ gesetzt wie gewünscht.
#. §0: `funext`
#. §1: `funext x`
#. §2: `x`
#. §3: `f = g`
#. §4: `f x = g x`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L05_Funext
msgid ""
"Try §0. Explain §1 as taking arbitrary §2 and changing goal from §3 to §4"
msgstr ""
"**你**：按定义来说，两个映射相等，不就是当它们作用到每个元素上都得到同样的值"
"吗…… \n"
"\n"
"**司南**：这个原则对应的策略，我这里也有：§0。用 §1，你选一个任意的 §2，然后"
"把目标从 §3 改成 §4。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "Intro Vieta L06"
msgstr ""
"**韦达**：我们还是再走一段吧。往这边！\n"
"\n"
"他急匆匆地走开，你们也尽可能快地跟上。等你们赶到他最终停下来的地方时，你已经"
"累得完全喘不过气了。韦达笑了。\n"
"\n"
"**韦达**：纯粹是以防万一！我得照看好我的访客嘛。像你们这样的访客我可不常"
"有！\n"
"\n"
"他把下一张纸递给你们。"

#. §0: `if_pos`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "Remind of negation for §0"
msgstr "**你**：啊，那§0的否定肯定是……"

#. §0: `(g ∘ f) «{x}»`
#. §1: `g (f «{x}»)`
#. §2: `simp`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "Rewrite §0 to §1 via §2"
msgstr ""
"**你**：啊，那我现在可以先把 §0 改写成 §1？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：用 §2 就行。"

#. §0: `funext x`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "Show swappability if mapping by using §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在我们有两个映射，其中一个是分段定义的。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：所以我要证明这两个映射可交换？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：没错，最好用 §0 先取一个任意元素，然后对这个元素证明等式。"

#. §0: `by_cases h : 0 ≤ «{x}»`
#. §1: `0 ≤ «{x}»`
#. §2: `0 > «{x}»`
#. §3: `0 ≤ «{x}»`
#. §4: `¬(0 ≤ «{x}»)`
#. §5: `not_le`
#. §6: `¬(0 ≤ «{x}»)`
#. §7: `0 > «{x}»`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid ""
"Try §0 for resulting cases §1 and §2 i.e. §3 and §4.\n"
"Could switch via §5 between §6 and §7"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：现在你就可以做分类讨论了，§0。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：这样我就得到 §1 和 §2 两种情况？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：对！或者更准确地说是 §3 和 §4。这不完全一样，不过可以用引理 §5 在 "
"§6 和 §7 之间切换。"

#. §0: `rw [if_pos «{h}»]`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "Try §0 to reduce if-then-else"
msgstr "**司南**：现在你可以用 §0 把 if-then-else 化简掉。"

#. §0: `simp [f, g]`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "Use definitions via §0"
msgstr ""
"**你**：看来我还是得用一下定义。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：那就用 §0 吧！"

#. §0: `if_neg`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "Use the negation §0"
msgstr "**司南**：§0，正是！"

#. §0: `simp [f, g]`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L06_Piecewise
msgid "[Vieta] Try §0 (again)"
msgstr "**司南**：再来一次 §0。"

#. §0: `g`
#. §1: `use`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L07_Extend
msgid "Insert §0 via §1"
msgstr "**司南**：现在你用 §1 把你的 §0 给出来，看看你的定义是不是对的。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L07_Extend
msgid "Intro Vieta L07"
msgstr ""
"你们远远地听到战斗的声音。\n"
"韦达看起来依然一点也不慌。\n"
"他又给了你们一道题。"

#. §0: `if 0 ≤ n then ... else ...`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L07_Extend
msgid "Try piecewise function with §0"
msgstr "**司南**：你可以用 §0 定义一个分段函数。"

#. §0: `toNat`
#. §1: `n : ℤ`
#. §2: `n.toNat : ℕ`
#. §3: `(-1).toNat`
#. §4: `n ≥ 0`
#. §5: `n.toNat`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L07_Extend
msgid ""
"Try §0. Explain, given §1 then §2 is the same number interpreted as a "
"natural number.\n"
"Remind that §3 undefined as §4 for §5"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这里你大概需要 §0：给定一个整数 §1，§2 就是同一个数，只不过把它当作"
"自然数来看。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：啊？那比如说 §3 呢？？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：不知道啊。我当然是说：*如果 §4 成立*，那 §5 仍然是“同一个”数。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L08_CongrArg
msgid "Intro Vieta L08"
msgstr "战斗的声音越来越近。韦达又给了你们两张纸。"

#. §0: `congr_arg`
#. §1: `x = y`
#. §2: `f x = f y`
#. §3: `apply congr_arg`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L08_CongrArg
msgid "Try §0. If §1, then §2 when using §3"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：哦，这正是 §0 的用武之地。要是你已经知道 §1，那用 §3 就能得到 §2。"

#. §0: `congr_fun`
#. §1: `h : f = g`
#. §2: `apply congr_fun at h`
#. §3: `h : ∀ x, f x = g x`
#. §4: `rw [h]`
#. §5: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L09_CongrFun
msgid ""
"Try §0. Given assumption §1 rewrite it via §2 to §3.\n"
"§4 not applicable to more complex §5"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：这也是 §0 的用武之地。如果你有一个假设 §1，可以用 §2 把它改写成 "
"§3。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：可是我这里不能更简单地直接用 §4 吗？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：行吧，在这个简单例子里确实可以。但如果 §5 是个更复杂的表达式，而且"
"并没有以完全相同的形式出现在目标里，那就不行了。按我刚才说的试试看。"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L10_Surjective
msgid "Conclusion Vieta L10"
msgstr "**韦达**：太棒了！不过现在得赶紧离开这里。往这边走。我带你们回飞船。"

#. §0: `succ`
#. §1: `succ : ℕ → ℕ`
#. §2: `n ↦ n + 1`
#. §3: `f`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L10_Surjective
msgid ""
"Explain §0 as mapping §1 i.e. §2. Explain goal of showing §3 surjective."
msgstr ""
"**你**：这里的 §0 是什么？\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：§1 是把一个自然数映射到它的 *successor*，也就是它的后继的映射。换句"
"话说：§2。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：啊，懂了。如果我没看错的话，这里本质上是要证明 §3 是满射。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：看起来是这样！"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L10_Surjective
msgid "Intro Vieta L10"
msgstr ""
"战斗的声音现在听起来已经近得吓人了。你们清清楚楚地听见炮声。然后又有一支箭嗖"
"地从你们身边飞过。\n"
"\n"
"**你**：呃，我们是不是该……\n"
"\n"
"**韦达**：别担心，再做一道题的时间还是有的。"

#. §0: `ℕ`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L10_Surjective
msgid "Remind of induction as mapping goes to §0"
msgstr ""
"**司南**：你看，这个映射的到达域是 §0！\n"
"\n"
"你挑了挑眉。\n"
"\n"
"**司南**：可能跟归纳有关吧。我就随口一说。"

#. §0: `congr_fun`
#. §1: `«{hs}»`
#. §2: `∀ x, («{f}» ∘ «{g}») x = (succ ∘ «{f}»)`
#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L10_Surjective
msgid "Try §0 to rewrite §1 to §2"
msgstr "**司南**：你要不要用 §0 把假设 §1 改写成 §2？"

#: GameServer.RpcHandlers
msgid "intermediate goal solved! 🎉"
msgstr "– 中间目标证明完成！ –"

#: GameServer.RpcHandlers
msgid "level completed with warnings… 🎭"
msgstr "– 关卡完成！但不完全是按预想的方式 –"

#: GameServer.RpcHandlers
msgid "level completed! 🎉"
msgstr "– 关卡完成！ –"
